duct Companies: ₹20L–₹45L+ PA', 'Internships at Red Hat, Zoho, Intel, Samsung, Nvidia, Qualcomm, CDAC. Example projects: Linux Shell, Kernel Modules, Thread Scheduling Simulator, Deadlock Avoidance Tools. Apply via Internshala, GitHub, HackerEarth.', 'Trainee OS Programmer → System Engineer → Linux Kernel Developer → Embedded Systems Expert → DevOps / Platform Engineering → CTO / Architect', 'RHCSA (Red Hat), Linux Foundation Certified SysAdmin, CompTIA Linux+, NPTEL OS Certificate, Coursera OS (Georgia Tech), Google IT Support (Linux Component)');
