('Engineering', 'Computer Science / IT', 'Data Structures & Algorithms (DSA)', 'IIT Bombay, IIT Delhi, IIT Kanpur, IIT Kharagpur, IIT Madras, IIIT Hyderabad, IIIT Delhi, IIIT Allahabad, NIT Trichy, NIT Warangal, NIT Surathkal, BITS Pilani, BITS Hyderabad, BITS Goa, DTU, NSUT, VIT Vellore, SRM University, MIT Pune', 'Data Structures, Algorithms, Design & Analysis of Algorithms, Discrete Mathematics, Programming in C++, Java, Python, Competitive Programming', 'Data Structures and Algorithms Made Easy - Narasimha Karumanchi, Introduction to Algorithms - Cormen (CLRS), Cracking the Coding Interview - Gayle Laakmann, Competitive Programming - Halim Brothers, The Algorithm Design Manual - Steven Skiena, Elements of Programming Interviews - Adnan Aziz', 'NPTEL - DSA & Programming by IITs; Coursera - Algorithms by Stanford; Udemy - DSA Bootcamps in C++/Java; GeeksforGeeks - DSA Self-Paced; Scaler Academy - DSA Career Track; Coding Ninjas - DSA in C++/Java; Codeforces EDU - Topic Practice', 'Apna College - https://www.youtube.com/c/ApnaCollegeOfficial, CodeWithHarry - https://www.youtube.com/c/CodeWithHarry, Take U Forward - https://www.youtube.com/c/takeUforward, Love Babbar - https://www.youtube.com/c/LoveBabbar1, Gate Smashers - https://www.youtube.com/c/GateSmasher, Jenny Lectures - https://www.youtube.com/c/JennyslecturesCSITNETJRF, KnowledgeGate - https://www.youtube.com/c/KnowledgeGate', 'https://www.geeksforgeeks.org, https://leetcode.com, https://codeforces.com, https://www.hackerrank.com, https://www.interviewbit.com, https://atcoder.jp, https://cs50.harvard.edu', 'Top recruiters like Google, Microsoft, Amazon, Flipkart, Adobe, and startups prioritize DSA knowledge. Strong DSA skills are key for coding interviews and product-based placements. Colleges provide DSA-specific training and support.', 'Software Developer, Backend Developer, Competitive Programmer, Algorithm Engineer, Coding Instructor, System Design Engineer', 'Very high demand in tech product companies, startups, and service firms requiring problem-solving roles. Also essential for competitive programming and research coding positions.', 'Fresher: ₹6L–₹18L PA; 2–3 Years: ₹12L–₹30L PA; 5+ Years: ₹25L–₹60L+ PA; FAANG+: ₹35L–₹1Cr+ CTC', 'Internshala, HackerEarth, LinkedIn, Google Summer of Code; Companies like Microsoft, Amazon, Zoho, Adobe, TCS Digital; Projects: Online Judge, Code Visualizer, Pathfinding Algorithm Tools, Leetcode Tracker', 'Learner → Programmer → Software Developer → SDE II/III → Tech Lead → Engineering Manager → CTO / Product Builder', 'Google Kickstart Certificate, Meta Hacker Cup, NPTEL DSA Certificate, LeetCode 100 Days Badge, Coursera Algorithms Certificate, Scaler / Coding Ninjas Completion Badge, Codeforces Max Rating Proof'),
('Engineering', 'Computer Science / IT', 'Git', 'IIT Bombay, IIT Delhi, IIT Kanpur, IIT Kharagpur, IIT Madras, IIIT Hyderabad, IIIT Bangalore, IIIT Allahabad, NIT Trichy, NIT Warangal, NIT Surathkal, BITS Pilani, BITS Goa, BITS Hyderabad, DTU, NSUT Delhi, VIT Vellore, MIT Pune', 'Software Engineering, Operating Systems, Computer Networks, Project Management, DevOps and Automation Tools, Distributed Systems', 'Pro Git - Scott Chacon and Ben Straub, Version Control with Git - Jon Loeliger, Git Pocket Guide - Richard E. Silverman', 'Git & GitHub – Udacity, Version Control with Git – Coursera (Atlassian), Git Complete – Udemy, Git Fundamentals – CS50 DevOps Track, Codecademy – Learn Git, GitHub Learning Lab, freeCodeCamp – Git & GitHub', 'freeCodeCamp - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RGOj5yH7evk, CodeWithHarry - https://www.youtube.com/c/CodeWithHarry, Apna College - https://www.youtube.com/c/ApnaCollegeOfficial, The Net Ninja - https://www.youtube.com/c/TheNetNinja, Tech with Tim - https://www.youtube.com/c/TechWithTim', 'https://git-scm.com, https://docs.github.com/, https://www.atlassian.com/git, https://www.freecodecamp.org, https://learngitbranching.js.org/', 'Git is an essential skill for software and DevOps roles. It is a must for coding interviews, collaborative projects, and automation pipelines. Most tech companies expect familiarity with Git and GitHub. Used in all modern software teams.', 'Software Developer, DevOps Engineer, QA Automation Engineer, Data Engineer, AI/ML Engineer, Version Control Manager', 'Extremely high demand in product-based, open-source, and DevOps-focused roles. Mandatory for most developer jobs, even entry-level.', 'Fresher: ₹4L–₹10L PA; 2–3 Years Exp: ₹8L–₹18L PA; 5+ Years Exp: ₹18L–₹35L+ PA; FAANG/MNCs: ₹25L–₹70L+ CTC', 'Internships at GitHub Campus Expert, Atlassian, Microsoft Student Ambassadors. Apply via LinkedIn, HackerEarth, Devfolio. Projects include GitHub Action Bots, Open Source PR Systems, Multi-dev CLI tools.', 'Git Learner → Contributor → Software Developer / DevOps → Senior Engineer → DevOps Architect / Engineering Manager → CTO', 'GitHub Learning Lab Certificate, Coursera Git Certificate (Atlassian), freeCodeCamp Git Certificate, GitLab DevOps Certification, Red Hat DevOps with Git, Microsoft Learn Git Badge, Codecademy Git Track Completion'),
('Engineering', 'Chemical Engineering', 'Process Simulation (Aspen HYSYS)', 'IIT Bombay, IIT Delhi, IIT Madras, IIT Kanpur, IIT Kharagpur, Institute of Chemical Technology Mumbai, NIT Trichy, NIT Warangal, BITS Pilani, Jadavpur University Kolkata', 'Chemical Reaction Engineering, Heat & Mass Transfer, Thermodynamics, Fluid Mechanics, Process Dynamics and Control, Chemical Process Calculation, Mechanical Operations, Process Equipment Design', 'Chemical Engineering Design by Sinnott & Towler, Unit Operations of Chemical Engineering by McCabe Smith & Harriott, Elements of Chemical Reaction Engineering by H. Scott Fogler, Introduction to Chemical Engineering Thermodynamics by Smith & Van Ness, Transport Processes and Separation Process Principles by Geankoplis', 'Aspen HYSYS: Process Simulation - Udemy, NPTEL Chemical Engineering Courses - NPTEL, Process Design with Aspen - Coursera, Process Simulation with Aspen Plus - LearnChemE.org', 'LearnChemE - https://www.youtube.com/c/LearnChemE, Chemical Engineering Guy - https://www.youtube.com/c/ChemicalEngineeringGuy, NPTEL IIT Lectures - https://www.youtube.com/user/nptelhrd, AspenTech Learning - https://www.youtube.com/user/AspenTechInc, The Chemical Engineer - https://www.youtube.com/@IChemE', 'https://www.learncheme.com/, https://nptel.ac.in/, https://www.aspentech.com/, https://www.coursera.org/browse/engineering/chemical-engineering, https://www.edx.org/learn/chemical-engineering', 'Top recruiters include Reliance Industries, ONGC, HPCL, GAIL, IOCL, Shell, Schlumberger, UPL, BASF. Roles include Process Engineer, Simulation Engineer, Production Engineer, Process Design Engineer, HSE Engineer.', 'Process Engineer, Simulation Engineer, Production Engineer, Process Design Engineer, HSE Engineer', 'High demand in oil & gas, petrochemical, energy, and pharma sectors. Opportunities in public and private sectors as well as international positions.', 'Entry Level: ₹4–7 LPA, Mid-Level (2–5 yrs): ₹8–15 LPA, Senior Level (5+ yrs): ₹15–25 LPA, International: ₹30–60 LPA', 'Internships at IOCL, GAIL, HPCL, BPCL, Tata Chemicals, L&T. In-plant training at refineries or fertilizer plants. Simulation and design projects are common.', 'Graduate Engineer Trainee → Process Engineer → Senior Process Engineer → Lead Simulation Specialist → Project Manager → R&D Head or Plant Head', 'Aspen HYSYS Certification, Six Sigma (Green Belt), Safety & HAZOP Studies, Process Control using MATLAB/Simulink, Data Analytics for Engineers'),
('Engineering', 'Chemical Engineering', 'Heat Transfer', 'IIT Bombay, IIT Madras, IIT Kharagpur, IIT Kanpur, IIT Delhi, ICT Mumbai, NIT Trichy, NIT Rourkela, BITS Pilani, Jadavpur University', 'Heat Transfer, Chemical Thermodynamics, Transport Phenomena, Fluid Mechanics, Mechanical Operations, Process Equipment Design, Computational Methods in Chemical Engineering', 'Heat and Mass Transfer by Yunus Cengel, Process Heat Transfer by D.Q. Kern, Transport Processes and Separation Process Principles by Geankoplis, Chemical Engineering Vol 1 & 2 by Coulson and Richardson, Introduction to Chemical Engineering Thermodynamics by Smith & Van Ness', 'Heat Transfer - NPTEL, Fundamentals of Heat Transfer - Coursera, Heat Exchanger Design - Udemy, Interactive Modules - LearnChemE', 'LearnChemE - https://www.youtube.com/c/LearnChemE, NPTEL HRD - https://www.youtube.com/user/nptelhrd, Chemical Engineering Guy - https://www.youtube.com/c/ChemicalEngineeringGuy, The Organic Chemistry Tutor - https://www.youtube.com/@theorganicchemistrytutor', 'https://www.learncheme.com/, https://nptel.ac.in/, https://www.coursera.org/, https://www.edx.org/, https://www.engineeringtoolbox.com/', 'Recruiters include ONGC, IOCL, GAIL, Reliance, BPCL, Tata Chemicals, L&T offering Process, Thermal, and Simulation Engineer roles.', 'Process Engineer, Thermal Engineer, Plant Engineer, Simulation Analyst, R&D Engineer', 'Heat Transfer professionals are in high demand in power, petrochemical, and green energy sectors. International roles are increasing in sustainability-related industries.', 'Fresher: ₹4–6 LPA, Mid-Level: ₹7–12 LPA, Senior: ₹15–20+ LPA, Abroad: ₹30–50+ LPA', 'Internships available at IOCL, GAIL, L&T, BHEL, Tata Chemicals. Includes design, inspection, energy audit, simulation.', 'Graduate Trainee → Heat Transfer Engineer → Senior Engineer → Project Manager → Energy Consultant', 'HTRI Software Training, ANSYS Fluent Certification, BEE Energy Management Certificate, Heat Exchanger Design Course, Safety & HAZOP Certification'),
('Engineering', 'Chemical Engineering', 'Lab Skills', 'IIT Bombay, IIT Madras, IIT Delhi, ICT Mumbai, IIT Kanpur, IIT Kharagpur, NIT Trichy, NIT Rourkela, BITS Pilani, Jadavpur University', 'Chemical Process Lab, Instrumentation and Control, Analytical Chemistry, Organic and Inorganic Lab Practices, Reaction Engineering, Chemical Safety & Hazards, Environmental Chemistry Lab, Physical Chemistry', 'Vogel’s Quantitative Chemical Analysis by G.H. Jeffery, Analytical Chemistry by Gary D. Christian, Laboratory Manual in Chemical Engineering by S. Ghosal, Instrumental Methods of Analysis by Willard and Merritt, Chemical Process Principles by Hougen & Watson', 'Analytical Chemistry Lab - NPTEL, Introduction to Laboratory Methods - Coursera, Lab Safety & Instrument Handling - Udemy, Basic Analytical Chemistry - edX', 'LearnChemE - https://www.youtube.com/c/LearnChemE, NPTEL HRD - https://www.youtube.com/user/nptelhrd, Chemical Engineering Guy - https://www.youtube.com/c/ChemicalEngineeringGuy, Lab Safety Institute - https://www.youtube.com/@labsafetyinstitute, MIT OCW - https://www.youtube.com/c/mitocw', 'https://www.learncheme.com/, https://nptel.ac.in/, https://www.coursera.org/, https://www.sciencelab.com/, http://chemcollective.org/', 'Recruiters include Sun Pharma, Cipla, Reliance, UPL, HUL, and ONGC labs. Roles offered include QC/QA Chemist, Lab Technician, Process Chemist, Analytical Scientist.', 'QC/QA Chemist, Lab Technician, Process Chemist, Analytical Scientist, Research Associate', 'Lab skills are in high demand in pharma, chemical testing, and biotech sectors. Opportunities are growing rapidly in industrial quality and safety testing labs.', 'Fresher: ₹3.5–5.5 LPA, Mid-Level: ₹6–10 LPA, Senior: ₹12–18 LPA, Abroad: ₹25–45+ LPA', 'Internships in pharma and chemical labs like Sun Pharma, Lupin, IOCL labs, GAIL, and National Chemical Laboratory (NCL). Focused on lab practice, documentation, and compliance training.', 'Lab Assistant → QC/QA Chemist → Senior Analyst → Lab Supervisor → R&D Manager or Consultant', 'GLP Certification, Analytical Chemistry Course, OSHA Lab Safety, Spectroscopy (UV, IR, NMR), HPLC/GC Instrumentation Certification'),
('Engineering', 'Aerospace Engineering', 'CAD (CATIA, ANSYS)', 'IIT Bombay, IIT Kanpur, IIT Madras, IIT Kharagpur, IIT Hyderabad, IIST Trivandrum, BITS Pilani, Manipal Institute of Technology, Amrita School of Engineering, MIT Anna University Chennai', 'Aerodynamics, Aircraft Structures, Propulsion Systems, Flight Mechanics, Avionics, Aerospace Materials, Computational Fluid Dynamics, Finite Element Methods, Aircraft Design Lab', 'Aircraft Structures for Engineering Students by T.H.G. Megson, Fundamentals of Aerodynamics by John D. Anderson, Introduction to Flight by John D. Anderson, CATIA V5 Workbook by Richard Cozzens, Finite Element Method for Engineers by Kenneth H. Huebner, Theoretical Aerodynamics by L. M. Milne-Thomson', 'Aerospace Propulsion - NPTEL, CAD and Engineering Design - Coursera, CATIA V5/V6 for Beginners - Udemy, ANSYS Mechanical FEA - Udemy, Aerospace Structure and Design - edX', 'LearnCAx - https://www.youtube.com/user/learncax, CAD CAM Tutorials - https://www.youtube.com/c/CADCAMTutorial, ANSYS How To - https://www.youtube.com/c/ANSYSHowTo, NPTEL HRD - https://www.youtube.com/user/nptelhrd, AeroVlog - https://www.youtube.com/@aerovlog', 'https://nptel.ac.in/, https://www.learncax.com/, https://www.coursera.org/, https://courses.ansys.com/, https://www.edx.org/, https://grabcad.com/', 'Top recruiters include HAL, ISRO, DRDO, Boeing, Airbus, Tata Aerospace, Mahindra Aerospace. Positions include CAD Engineer, Design Engineer, FEA Analyst, Aerospace Simulation Engineer.', 'CAD Engineer, Design Engineer, FEA Analyst, Aerospace Simulation Engineer, Aerostructures Designer', 'Growing demand in defense, civil aviation, UAV, and space sector. Startups in aerospace tech and R&D are hiring actively.', 'Fresher: ₹4.5–7 LPA, Mid-Level: ₹8–15 LPA, Senior: ₹18–30 LPA, Abroad: ₹30–60+ LPA', 'Internships at ISRO, HAL, DRDO, Mahindra Aerospace, Tata Advanced Systems, Rolls Royce India, and L&T. Focused on simulation, CAD design, structural modeling.', 'Design Intern → CAD Engineer → Senior FEA Engineer → Aerospace Project Manager → Aerospace Consultant / R&D Lead', 'CATIA Certification, ANSYS Mechanical Certification, SolidWorks Certification, FEM/CFD Training, NPTEL Aerospace Certificates, Siemens NX Certification'),
('Engineering', 'Aerospace Engineering', 'Aerodynamics', 'IIT Bombay, IIT Kanpur, IIT Madras, IIT Kharagpur, IIST Trivandrum, BITS Pilani, Amrita School of Engineering, Manipal Institute of Technology, MIT Anna University Chennai, SRM Institute of Science and Technology', 'Fluid Mechanics, Aerodynamics I II III, Compressible Flows, Boundary Layer Theory, Computational Fluid Dynamics, Wind Tunnel Techniques, Flight Dynamics, Aircraft Propulsion, Avionics and Control Systems', 'Fundamentals of Aerodynamics by John D. Anderson, Introduction to Flight by John D. Anderson, Modern Compressible Flow by John D. Anderson, Boundary Layer Theory by Hermann Schlichting, Gas Dynamics by E. Rathakrishnan, Aerodynamics for Engineers by Bertin & Smith', 'Aerodynamics - NPTEL, Compressible Flow - NPTEL, Introduction to Aerodynamics - Coursera, Fundamentals of Flight - edX, Applied Aerodynamics using CFD - Udemy, Aerodynamics - MIT OCW', 'LearnChemE - https://www.youtube.com/c/LearnChemE, NPTEL HRD - https://www.youtube.com/user/nptelhrd, Engineering Explained - https://www.youtube.com/user/EngineeringExplained, AeroVlog - https://www.youtube.com/@aerovlog, MIT OCW - https://www.youtube.com/c/mitocw', 'https://nptel.ac.in, https://ocw.mit.edu, https://www.grc.nasa.gov, https://www.coursera.org, https://www.edx.org', 'Top recruiters include HAL, ISRO, DRDO, Boeing, Airbus, Tata Aerospace, Mahindra Aerospace. Positions include Aerodynamics Engineer, CFD Analyst, Flight Test Engineer.', 'Aerodynamics Engineer, CFD Analyst, Flight Test Engineer, Research Associate, Wind Tunnel Engineer', 'Aerodynamics specialists are in demand across aerospace R&D, UAV companies, and space programs. Great scope in both public and private sectors.', 'Fresher: ₹4.5–7 LPA, Mid-Level: ₹8–14 LPA, Senior: ₹15–25 LPA, Abroad: ₹30–60+ LPA', 'Internships available at ISRO, HAL, DRDO, CSIR-NAL, Tata Aerospace, L&T. Activities include CFD modeling, simulation, experimental aero testing.', 'Aerodynamics Intern → CFD Engineer → Senior Aerodynamicist → Project Lead → R&D Scientist / Consultant', 'CFD with ANSYS or OpenFOAM, CATIA/SolidWorks, NPTEL Aerodynamics, MATLAB for Aero, Wind Tunnel Certification, XFLR5/XFOIL usage'),
('Engineering', 'Aerospace Engineering', 'Flight Simulation', 'IIT Kanpur, IIT Madras, IIT Bombay, IIST Trivandrum, IIT Kharagpur, BITS Pilani, MIT Anna University, Amrita School of Engineering, Manipal Institute of Technology, SRM Institute of Science and Technology', 'Flight Mechanics, Aircraft Stability and Control, Flight Dynamics, Control Systems, Avionics, Simulation Modeling, CFD, Aerodynamics, Aircraft Systems Lab', 'Flight Stability and Automatic Control by Robert C. Nelson, Aircraft Control and Simulation by Stevens & Lewis, Flight Dynamics Principles by M.V. Cook, Introduction to Aircraft Flight Mechanics by Thomas Yechout, MATLAB/Simulink for Flight Control Systems by Thomas Beuhler', 'Flight Dynamics - NPTEL, Aerospace Control Systems - NPTEL, Modeling and Control of Aerospace Systems - Coursera, Flight Mechanics - ISAE Supaero, Aerospace Engineering - MITx, Flight Simulation using MATLAB - Udemy', 'NASA Aeronautics - https://www.youtube.com/@NASAaero, FlightGear Project - https://www.youtube.com/@FlightGearProject, NPTEL HRD - https://www.youtube.com/user/nptelhrd, Engineering Explained - https://www.youtube.com/@EngineeringExplained, Pilot Training System - https://www.youtube.com/@pilottrainingsystem', 'https://nptel.ac.in, https://ocw.mit.edu, https://flightgear.org, https://www.mathworks.com, https://x-plane.com', 'Recruiters include ISRO, DRDO, HAL, Airbus, Boeing, Honeywell, Thales, Tata Advanced Systems. Roles include Simulation Engineer, Flight Test Engineer, Avionics Simulation Specialist.', 'Flight Simulation Engineer, Control Systems Engineer, Test & Evaluation Engineer, Flight Test Instrumentation Engineer', 'Growing opportunities in both defense and civil aviation sectors. Simulation professionals are needed in training, design, and R&D units.', 'Fresher: ₹4.5–7 LPA, Mid-Level: ₹8–14 LPA, Senior: ₹15–25 LPA, Abroad: ₹35–60+ LPA', 'Internships offered at DRDO (ADE), HAL, Boeing, ISRO, Thales, and IIT Flight Labs. Focused on simulation, control system integration, and data testing.', 'Simulation Intern → Simulation Engineer → Senior Flight Control Engineer → System Architect → R&D Simulation Consultant', 'MATLAB Simulink Aerospace Certificate, X-Plane SDK, UAV Simulation Certification, NPTEL Control Systems, Python for Flight Modeling, LabVIEW for Aerospace'),
('Engineering', 'Mechatronics', 'Arduino', 'IIT Patna, VIT Vellore, SRM Institute of Science and Technology, Amrita School of Engineering, MIT Manipal, BITS Pilani Hyderabad, SASTRA University, PSG College of Technology, Kumaraguru College of Technology, NIIT University', 'Embedded Systems, Microcontrollers and Applications, Mechatronic Systems Design, Sensors and Instrumentation, Robotics and Control, Signal Processing, Electrical Machines, Industrial Automation', 'Exploring Arduino by Jeremy Blum, Arduino Cookbook by Michael Margolis, Embedded Systems with Arduino by James Floyd Kelly, Mechatronics by W. Bolton, Getting Started with Arduino by Massimo Banzi', 'Mechatronics and Microcontrollers - NPTEL, Interfacing with Arduino - Coursera, Embedded Systems with Arduino - edX, Mastering Arduino - Udemy, MIT OCW Mechatronics', 'Paul McWhorter - https://www.youtube.com/c/PaulMcWhorter, GreatScott! - https://www.youtube.com/c/greatscottlab, Programming Electronics Academy - https://www.youtube.com/c/ProgrammingElectronicsAcademy, DroneBot Workshop - https://www.youtube.com/c/DroneBotWorkshop, Arduino Official - https://www.youtube.com/user/arduinoteam', 'https://www.arduino.cc, https://circuitdigest.com, https://maker.pro, https://instructables.com, https://learn.sparkfun.com', 'Recruiters include Bosch, Siemens, ABB, Honeywell, L&T, TCS Innovation Labs, HCL, Fanuc, Tata ELXSI. Roles include Embedded Developer, IoT Engineer, Automation Engineer.', 'Embedded Developer, Automation Engineer, IoT System Engineer, Robotics Developer, Control System Designer', 'Growing demand in industrial automation, IoT, and smart device industries. High startup and R&D potential in India and abroad.', 'Fresher: ₹3.5–6 LPA, Mid-Level: ₹7–12 LPA, Senior: ₹15–22+ LPA, Freelance: ₹1–10+ LPA, Abroad: ₹25–50+ LPA', 'Internships available at Bosch, DRDO, Siemens, Tech Mahindra, ABB. Focused on Arduino-based systems, embedded hardware interfacing, automation design.', 'Intern → Embedded Developer → Automation Engineer → Lead Architect → R&D Head / Consultant', 'Arduino Fundamentals Certificate, Embedded Systems (Coursera/edX), IoT Arduino Certification, Automation with Arduino – Udemy, Embedded C Programming, Industrial Robotics'),
('Engineering', 'Mechatronics', 'Raspberry Pi', 'IIT Patna, VIT Vellore, SRM Institute of Science and Technology, MIT Manipal, Amrita School of Engineering, BITS Pilani Hyderabad, PSG College of Technology, Kumaraguru College of Technology, SASTRA University, KLE Technological University', 'Embedded Linux Systems, IoT and Smart Systems, Python Programming, Sensors and Actuators, Mechatronics Systems Integration, Microcontroller Architecture, AI/ML on Embedded Devices, Control Systems', 'Raspberry Pi Cookbook by Simon Monk, Programming the Raspberry Pi by Simon Monk, Exploring Raspberry Pi by Derek Molloy, Python Programming for Raspberry Pi by Tim Cox, Internet of Things with Raspberry Pi by Rajesh Singh', 'Mechatronics and IoT - NPTEL, Raspberry Pi and Python - Coursera, Full Stack Raspberry Pi Development - Udemy, Embedded Linux with Pi - edX, Build Raspberry Pi Computer - FutureLearn', 'Techiesms - https://www.youtube.com/c/Techiesms, Raspberry Pi Foundation - https://www.youtube.com/user/raspberrypi, Learn Electronics - https://www.youtube.com/c/LearnElectronics, Paul McWhorter - https://www.youtube.com/c/PaulMcWhorter, ProgrammingKnowledge - https://www.youtube.com/c/ProgrammingKnowledge', 'https://www.raspberrypi.org, https://circuitdigest.com, https://maker.pro, https://randomnerdtutorials.com, https://projects.raspberrypi.org', 'Placement opportunities in Bosch, Siemens, Wipro IoT, Tata Elxsi, DRDO, and automation startups. Roles include Embedded Linux Developer, IoT App Developer, Raspberry Pi System Integrator.', 'Embedded Linux Developer, IoT Application Developer, Hardware Interface Engineer, Python IoT Engineer, Raspberry Pi Developer', 'High demand in IoT, automation, smart devices, and robotics startups. Strong freelancing and maker community support.', 'Fresher: ₹4–7 LPA, Mid: ₹8–14 LPA, Senior: ₹15–25+ LPA, Freelance: ₹1–10+ LPA, Abroad: ₹30–60+ LPA', 'Internships available at Bosch, DRDO, Tata Elxsi, MSME labs, L&T Smart World. Projects involve IoT data logging, GPIO control, and AI edge deployment.', 'Intern → IoT Developer → Embedded Systems Lead → Smart Systems Architect → Product Head / AIoT Consultant', 'Raspberry Pi Foundation Certificate, Embedded Linux (Coursera/edX), IoT Edge Computing (FutureLearn), Python for Embedded (Udemy), NPTEL Certified, TensorFlow Lite on Pi'),
('Engineering', 'Mechatronics', 'Robotics', 'IIT Kanpur, IIT Bombay, IIT Hyderabad, BITS Pilani, SRM Institute of Science and Technology, VIT Vellore, MIT Manipal, PSG College of Technology, Amrita School of Engineering, IIIT Hyderabad', 'Robotics and Automation, Control Systems, Embedded Systems, Mechatronics System Design, Machine Learning for Robotics, Robot Dynamics and Kinematics, Signal Processing, Artificial Intelligence, Industrial Automation', 'Introduction to Robotics by John J. Craig, Robotics by Siciliano & Sciavicco, Learning ROS for Robotics Programming by Aaron Martinez, ROS for Beginners by Lentin Joseph, Modern Robotics by Kevin Lynch & Frank Park', 'Robotics - NPTEL, Modern Robotics - Coursera, Robotics MicroMasters - edX, ROS Programming - Udemy, MIT Underactuated Robotics - OCW', 'Robotics Today - https://www.youtube.com/@RoboticsToday, Paul McWhorter - https://www.youtube.com/c/PaulMcWhorter, NPTEL HRD - https://www.youtube.com/user/nptelhrd, The Construct - https://www.youtube.com/c/TheConstructPlayground, MIT OCW - https://www.youtube.com/c/mitocw', 'https://nptel.ac.in, https://www.ros.org, https://ocw.mit.edu, https://theconstructsim.com, https://www.robotshop.com', 'Top recruiters: ABB, Fanuc, Tata, Mahindra, TCS, DRDO, ISRO. Roles include Robotics Engineer, ROS Developer, Embedded Robotics Developer.', 'Robotics Engineer, ROS Developer, Embedded Systems Engineer, Automation Developer, R&D Engineer, Robotics Consultant', 'High growth in autonomous tech, smart factories, drone robotics, healthcare robotics. Global demand rising.', 'Fresher: ₹4–7 LPA, Mid-Level: ₹8–14 LPA, Senior: ₹15–25+ LPA, Abroad: ₹30–60+ LPA', 'Internships at ABB Robotics, DRDO, Bosch, Siemens, Tata ELXSI, Mahindra R&D. Focus on robot design, automation, sensor integration.', 'Intern → Robotics Developer → Robotics Engineer → Robotics Architect → R&D Consultant / Robotics Director', 'NPTEL Robotics Certificate, ROS Programming (The Construct/Udemy), Embedded C Programming, AI for Robotics (Coursera), Python + OpenCV for Robotics, Robotics Simulation with Gazebo'),
