n Architect → R&D Consultant / Industry 4.0 Specialist', 'NPTEL Control Systems Certificate, MATLAB Simulink Associate – MathWorks, PID & SCADA Automation – Udemy, Allen Bradley PLC Certificate, Siemens Automation Certificate, Control of Mobile Robots – Coursera'),
