('Engineering', 'Biotechnology', 'Lab Techniques (PCR, ELISA)', 'IISc Bangalore, JNU Delhi, IIT Delhi, IIT Madras, IIT Kharagpur, BHU, Amity Institute of Biotechnology, Manipal School of Life Sciences, VIT Vellore, SRM Institute', 'Molecular Biology, Immunology, Microbiology, Biochemistry, Genetic Engineering, Analytical Techniques, Recombinant DNA Technology, Cell Culture, Clinical Research Techniques', 'Molecular Biology of the Cell by Alberts, Principles of Biochemistry by Wilson & Walker, PCR Technology by Erlich, ELISA Protocols – Molecular Biology Series, Molecular Biotechnology by Glick', 'DNA Sequencing – Coursera, Biochemistry – edX, Genetic Engineering – NPTEL, Diagnostic Biotech – FutureLearn, LabXchange PCR/ELISA Labs', 'Shomu’s Biology - https://www.youtube.com/user/TheFunsuman, BioTechniques Journal - https://www.youtube.com/@BioTechniques, NPTEL Biotechnology - https://www.youtube.com/c/nptelhrd, Leah4Sci - https://www.youtube.com/c/Leah4sci, Raja Biotech - https://www.youtube.com/@RajaBiotech', 'https://www.labxchange.org, https://www.thermofisher.com, https://www.protocol-online.org, https://www.addgene.org, https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov', 'Placement in Biocon, Serum Institute, Thermo Fisher, Lupin, Bharat Biotech, R&D and Quality roles. High preference for candidates with strong lab skill certification.', 'Lab Technician, Research Assistant, QC Analyst, Molecular Biologist, Clinical Trial Associate', 'Growing demand in diagnostic labs, biopharma QC, R&D labs. Post-COVID testing infrastructure boosted job opportunities for skilled lab technicians.', 'Fresher: ₹3–6 LPA, Mid-Level: ₹6–10 LPA, Senior: ₹12–18+ LPA, Abroad: ₹25–50+ LPA', 'Internships in Biocon, Bharat Biotech, IIT Biotech Labs, Thermo Fisher. Focus: PCR assay setup, ELISA plate testing, molecular diagnostics, quality control.', 'Intern → Lab Assistant → QC/Research Analyst → Molecular Biologist → Biotech Lead / R&D Scientist', 'LabXchange PCR Certification, NSDC Biotech Lab Technician, Co