('Science', 'Mathematics', 'R Programming', 'ISI Kolkata, CMI Chennai, IIT Kanpur, IIT Bombay, IISc Bangalore, University of Hyderabad, Delhi University, TIFR Mumbai, BHU Varanasi', 'Probability, Statistics, Regression Analysis, Time Series, Linear Algebra, Numerical Methods, R Programming, Statistical Computing', 'The Art of R Programming – Matloff, R for Data Science – Wickham, Applied Stats in R – Dalpiaz, Intro to Statistical Learning – Hastie, Hands-on Programming with R – Grolemund', 'NPTEL – Data Analysis with R, Coursera – R Programming JHU, edX – Intro to R (Microsoft), Udemy – R for Data Science, DataCamp – R Programmer Track', 'StatQuest – https://www.youtube.com/@statquest, Marin Stats – https://www.youtube.com/@MarinStatsLectures, CodeBasics – https://www.youtube.com/@codebasics, Simplilearn R – https://www.youtube.com/@simplilearn, freeCodeCamp R – https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_V8eKsto3Ug', 'https://r4ds.had.co.nz, https://cran.r-project.org, https://datacamp.com, https://nptel.ac.in, https://towardsdatascience.com', 'Placements available in analytics firms, policy research units, research labs, finance companies, healthcare analysis – especially for students skilled in R and statistics.', 'Data Analyst, R Developer, Statistician, Quant Researcher, Epidemiology Analyst, Financial Risk Analyst', 'Strong growth in research-oriented and analytical roles. Preferred in policy research, bioinformatics, epidemiology, government statistics, and AI modeling.', 'Fresher Analyst: ₹4–8 LPA, R Programmer: ₹5–10 LPA, Quantitative Analyst: ₹8–15 LPA, Senior Data Scientist: ₹12–25+ LPA, Abroad Research Roles: ₹30–60+ LPA', 'Internships at ISI, DRDO, TCS Analytics, Public Health Labs; experience in data cleaning, modeling, R Shiny dashboard, report automation', 'Intern → Data Analyst → Statistician → Quant Analyst → Principal Scientist / Policy Research Head', 'DataCamp R Track, Coursera R Certification, NPTEL Data Analysis, edX Intro to R, RStudio Shiny Developer Certification'),
('Science', 'Mathematics', 'LaTeX', 'ISI Kolkata, CMI Chennai, IIT Kanpur, IIT Bombay, IISc Bangalore, DU (St. Stephen\'s), BHU Varanasi, Presidency University, University of Hyderabad, TIFR', 'Real Analysis, Linear Algebra, Abstract Algebra, Number Theory, Mathematical Logic, Differential Equations, Probability and Statistics, Discrete Mathematics', 'The Not So Short Intro to LaTeX – Oetiker, LaTeX: A Document Preparation System – Lamport, Guide to LaTeX – Kopka, More Math into LaTeX – Grätzer, Mathematics Into Type – Swanson', 'Overleaf LaTeX Tutorials, Coursera – LaTeX Scientific Writing, NPTEL Technical Writing, Udemy LaTeX Courses, FreeCodeCamp LaTeX Guide', 'OverleafHQ – https://www.youtube.com/@OverleafHQ, Michelle Krummel – https://www.youtube.com/@MichelleKrummel, LearnLaTeX – https://www.youtube.com/@LearnLatex, Chandrahas Sir – https://www.youtube.com/@ChandrahasSir', 'https://overleaf.com, https://latex-project.org, https://tex.stackexchange.com, https://ctan.org, https://detexify.kirelabs.org', 'Placements in research labs, academic publishing, ed-tech, government R&D, and technical writing. LaTeX skill preferred for scholars, mathematicians, and publication editors.', 'Mathematical Content Creator, Scientific Editor, Research Assistant, Technical Writer, Academic Editor, Research Scholar', 'Strong in academia, research organizations, education technology, and publication houses. Preferred for PhD, documentation, and content-based mathematical jobs.', 'Fresher: ₹3–6 LPA, Content Developer: ₹6–10 LPA, Research Scholar: ₹6–12+ LPA, International Roles: ₹20–60+ LPA', 'Internships at Springer, Elsevier, DRDO, Overleaf Community, Government Math Research Labs. Work in typesetting, documentation, research formatting.', 'Intern → LaTeX Editor → Research Assistant → Documentation Lead → Postdoc / Academic Researcher', 'Overleaf LaTeX Certification, Coursera LaTeX Scientific Writing, Springer Workshop Certificate, Udemy LaTeX Mastery Badge'),
('Science', 'Mathematics', 'Data Analysis', 'ISI Kolkata, CMI Chennai, IIT Bombay, IIT Kanpur, IISc Bangalore, University of Hyderabad, DU (Hindu, St. Stephen\'s), BHU, Presidency University, Ashoka University', 'Probability and Statistics, Linear Algebra, Regression Analysis, Time Series Forecasting, Machine Learning Basics, Real Analysis, Optimization, Data Cleaning and Wrangling', 'Intro to Probability – Sheldon Ross, Practical Statistics for Data Scientists, All of Statistics – Larry Wasserman, Applied Linear Statistical Models, Python for Data Analysis – Wes McKinney', 'NPTEL – Data Science for Engineers, Coursera – Data Science (JHU), edX – Data Analysis (Harvard), DataCamp Analyst Track, Udemy Data Analyst Bootcamp', 'StatQuest – https://www.youtube.com/@statquest, Codebasics – https://www.youtube.com/@codebasics, Krish Naik – https://www.youtube.com/@krishnaik06, Ken Jee – https://www.youtube.com/@KenJee1, Simplilearn – https://www.youtube.com/@simplilearn', 'https://www.datacamp.com, https://www.kaggle.com/learn, https://www.analyticsvidhya.com, https://towardsdatascience.com, https://nptel.ac.in', 'Excellent placement in analytics, banking, ed-tech, government research, and tech startups. Preferred candidates have strong Python/R and statistical knowledge.', 'Data Analyst, Statistician, Research Analyst, Business Intelligence Analyst, Junior Data Scientist', 'High demand across finance, healthcare, marketing, research, and public policy. Strong prospects even for fresh graduates with portfolio projects.', 'Fresher: ₹4–6 LPA, Experienced Analyst: ₹10–15 LPA, Data Scientist: ₹15–25+ LPA', 'ISI, DRDO, NITI Aayog, HSBC, Deloitte, Cognizant – internships in data analysis, statistical computing, and report generation', 'Intern → Data Analyst → Senior Analyst → Analytics Manager → Head of Data Science / CDO', 'Coursera IBM Data Science, edX Harvard Data Science, Google Data Analytics, Tableau Certification, NPTEL Data Science'),
('Science', 'Zoology / Botany', 'Taxonomy Tools', 'IISc Bangalore, DU (Botany/Zoology), BHU Varanasi, Madras Christian College, Presidency University, St. Xavier\'s Mumbai/Kolkata, Kerala Agricultural University, Panjab University, Jiwaji University, Osmania University', 'Systematics and Taxonomy, Evolutionary Biology, Ecology, Biodiversity, Biogeography, Cell Biology, Molecular Biology, Genetics', 'Plant Systematics – Gurcharan Singh, Zoology – R.L. Kotpal, Taxonomy of Vascular Plants – George Lawrence, Principles of Animal Taxonomy – G.G. Simpson, Manual of Plant Taxonomy – E. Lawrence', 'NPTEL – Biodiversity & Taxonomy, Coursera – Ecology and Evolution, edX – Environmental Studies, FutureLearn – Taxonomy Skills, GBIF eLearning', 'Nature Spy – https://www.youtube.com/@NatureSpy, BioMan Biology – https://www.youtube.com/@biomanbiology, Untamed Science – https://www.youtube.com/@untamedscience, Study Lovers Bio – https://www.youtube.com/@studyloversbio', 'https://gbif.org, https://iucnredlist.org, https://inaturalist.org, https://ncbi.nlm.nih.gov, https://botanicgardens.org', 'Placements in biodiversity institutes, academic research, ecological consulting, and NGOs. Preferred candidates have good field knowledge and specimen handling experience.', 'Field Biologist, Taxonomist, Research Assistant, Biodiversity Scientist, Project Coordinator, Academic Faculty', 'Moderate demand in biodiversity research, taxonomy projects, eco-restoration planning, and DNA barcoding programs', 'Fresher: ₹3–5 LPA, Project Staff: ₹6–10 LPA, Govt. Scientist: ₹8–12+ LPA, Academic/Research Lead: ₹12–20+ LPA', 'Internships available at ZSI, BSI, BNHS, WII, state biodiversity boards. Work involves species documentation, ecological surveys, and taxonomic identification', 'Intern → Taxonomist → Research Scientist → Project Leader → Biodiversity Department Head', 'GBIF eLearning Certificate, DNA Barcoding Training, GIS and RS Certification, WII Field Training, NPTEL Taxonomy Certificate'),
('Science', 'Zoology / Botany', 'Specimen Collection', 'IISc Bangalore, BHU Varanasi, University of Delhi, Presidency University, St. Xavier\'s College Mumbai/Kolkata, Kerala Agricultural University, Panjab University, Osmania University, Madras Christian College', 'Systematic Botany, Animal Taxonomy, Ecology, Field Biology, Conservation Biology, Genetics, Evolution, Plant/Animal Physiology', 'Field Biology and Ecology – R.L. Smith, Plant Systematics – Gurcharan Singh, Zoology – R.L. Kotpal, Animal Taxonomy – G.G. Simpson, Handbook of Field Techniques – Ernest G. Neal', 'NPTEL – Biodiversity & Conservation, Coursera – Ecology & Evolution (Duke), edX – Environmental Biology, FutureLearn – Species Identification, WII Field Methods MOOC', 'WII – https://www.youtube.com/@wii_official, Nature Spy – https://www.youtube.com/@NatureSpy, BioMan Biology – https://www.youtube.com/@biomanbiology, Study Lovers Bio – https://www.youtube.com/@studyloversbio', 'https://gbif.org, https://iucnredlist.org, https://inaturalist.org, https://bnhs.org, https://envfor.nic.in', 'Research-based placements in wildlife surveys, ecological restoration projects, biodiversity missions, forest departments. Good for postgraduates and trained collectors.', 'Field Biologist, Project Assistant, Taxonomist, Research Assistant, Junior Scientist', 'Strong in conservation and biodiversity sectors, especially with field experience and ecological certifications.', 'Fresher: ₹3–5 LPA, Research Assistant: ₹6–9 LPA, Project Scientist: ₹10–15 LPA, Academic/Govt. Scientist: ₹12–20+ LPA', 'Internships at ZSI, BSI, BNHS, SACON, WII – focus on field collection, biodiversity mapping, herbarium work', 'Intern → Field Biologist → Researcher → Project Scientist → Senior Scientist / Director', 'GBIF Data Certificate, WII Field Training, DNA Barcoding Workshop, GIS Certificate, NPTEL Biodiversity'),
('Science', 'Zoology / Botany', 'Field Survey', 'IISc Bangalore, Wildlife Institute of India, ZSI Kolkata, BSI Kolkata, BHU, DU, Presidency University Kolkata, Kerala Agricultural University, Madras Christian College, St. Xavier\'s Mumbai', 'Ecology, Biodiversity, Systematics, Field Biology, Environmental Science, Biogeography, Remote Sensing, Taxonomy, Statistics', 'Field Biology and Ecology – R.L. Smith, Manual of Field Techniques – B.K. Sharma, Wildlife Ecology – Eric G. Bolen, Plant Systematics – Gurcharan Singh, Zoology – R.L. Kotpal', 'NPTEL – Biodiversity and Taxonomy, WII Wildlife Techniques, Coursera – Ecology Ecosystem Dynamics, edX – Field Ecology, FutureLearn – Mapping Skills', 'WII – https://www.youtube.com/@wii_official, Nature Spy – https://www.youtube.com/@NatureSpy, BBC Earth – https://www.youtube.com/@BBCEarth, Study Lovers – https://www.youtube.com/@studyloversbio', 'https://gbif.org, https://bnhs.org, https://inaturalist.org, https://moef.gov.in, https://envirothon.org', 'Good placements in ecological research, field biodiversity missions, and NGOs. Required: field experience, GPS knowledge, and strong ecology base.', 'Field Biologist, Ecological Surveyor, GIS Analyst, Environmental Consultant, Research Assistant', 'High demand in biodiversity monitoring, wildlife conservation, and EIA consulting with interdisciplinary skills.', 'Fresher: ₹3–5 LPA, Mid-Level: ₹6–9 LPA, Senior Consultant: ₹10–18+ LPA, Academic/Govt. Scientist: ₹12–20+ LPA', 'Internships at WII, ZSI, BSI, SACON, BNHS; NGOs like WWF-India, ATREE; work includes species survey, GIS mapping, biodiversity inventory', 'Intern → Field Biologist → Project Scientist → Senior Consultant/Researcher → Professor / Department Head', 'NPTEL Ecology, WII Wildlife Techniques, GBIF Data, ISRO GIS Course, EIA Training Certificate'),
('Science', 'Microbiology', 'Staining Techniques', 'AIIMS Delhi, University of Delhi, Madurai Kamaraj University, JMI Delhi, Panjab University, Amity University, St. Xavier\'s College Mumbai/Kolkata, Presidency University Kolkata, Fergusson College Pune, Osmania University', 'General Microbiology, Bacteriology, Immunology, Molecular Biology, Instrumentation, Medical Microbiology, Industrial Microbiology', 'Microbiology Lab Manual – Cappuccino, Prescott’s Microbiology, Fundamentals of Microbiology – Pommerville, Techniques in Microbiology – Frazier, Manual of Practical Microbiology – Aneja', 'NPTEL – Microbiology Basics, Coursera – Micro Lab Techniques, edX – Molecular Biology, SWAYAM – Microbial Genetics, YouTube MOOC – Practical Micro', 'Microbiology with Sumi, NPTEL Microbiology, Easy Learning Microbiology, MEDSimplified, Dr. Najeeb Lectures', 'https://microbeonline.com, https://asm.org, https://ncbi.nlm.nih.gov, https://swayam.gov.in, https://labtestsonline.org', 'Placements available in hospitals, diagnostics labs, pharma companies, and research centers with core lab skills in staining and microscopy.', 'Lab Technician, Clinical Microbiologist, QC Analyst, JRF/Research Assistant, QA Executive, Microbiology Scientist', 'Strong demand in clinical diagnostics, pharma labs, hospital labs, and biotechnological R&D. Advanced microscopy and staining knowledge is a major plus.', 'Fresher: ₹3–4.5 LPA, Research Assistant: ₹5–7 LPA, Clinical Microbiologist: ₹7–12 LPA, Senior Scientist: ₹15+ LPA', 'Internships at AIIMS, Biocon, Zydus, Cipla, Serum Institute – focus on staining techniques, microbial diagnosis, QC processes', 'Intern → Lab Tech → Microbiologist → Senior Scientist → Lab Director / Professor', 'NPTEL Biosafety, Coursera Micro Lab, WHO Biosafety, ISO 17025, AIIMS Workshop Certificate'),
('Science', 'Microbiology', 'Culture Maintenance', 'AIIMS Delhi, University of Delhi, JNU Delhi, Madurai Kamaraj University, JMI Delhi, Panjab University, St. Xavier\'s Mumbai/Kolkata, Presidency University Kolkata, Fergusson College Pune, Osmania University', 'Microbial Physiology, Culture Techniques, Bacteriology, Virology, Immunology, Medical & Industrial Microbiology, Lab Instrumentation, Biosafety', 'Cappuccino Lab Manual, Prescott’s Microbiology, Fundamentals of Microbiology – Pommerville, Techniques in Microbiology – Frazier, Aneja’s Practical Microbiology', 'NPTEL Micro Lab Techniques, Coursera – Culture Techniques, edX – Microbial Methods, SWAYAM – Microbial Techniques, WHO Lab Safety', 'Microbiology with Sumi, NPTEL HRD, Easy Learning Microbiology, Labpedia Academy, MEDSimplified', 'https://microbeonline.com, https://asm.org, https://labtestsonline.org, https://ncbi.nlm.nih.gov, https://swayam.gov.in', 'Strong placement in diagnostic, pharmaceutical, food, and R&D labs; preferred candidates skilled in aseptic handling and long-term culture maintenance.', 'Lab Technician, Microbiologist, QA/QC Analyst, Research Assistant, Fermentation Technician', 'High demand across healthcare, pharmaceuticals, food industries, vaccine production and research labs. Culture handling skill is a core requirement.', 'Fresher: ₹2.5–4.5 LPA, Mid-level: ₹6–8 LPA, Experienced Scientist: ₹10–20+ LPA', 'Internships at AIIMS, Serum Institute, Biocon, Panacea Biotec, Zydus Cadila – focusing on media prep, culture maintenance, contamination control', 'Intern → Junior Microbiologist → Lab Manager → Scientist → R&D Lead / Professor', 'NPTEL Certification, WHO Lab Biosafety, ISO 17025, Coursera Micro Lab Techniques, AIIMS Practical Workshops'),
('Science', 'Microbiology', 'Autoclave Use', 'AIIMS Delhi, University of Delhi, Madurai Kamaraj University, JNU Delhi, Jamia Millia Islamia, Panjab University, St. Xavier\'s Mumbai/Kolkata, Presidency University Kolkata, Fergusson College Pune, Osmania University Hyderabad', 'General Microbiology, Lab Techniques, Biosafety & Waste Management, Medical & Industrial Microbiology, Instrumentation, Environmental Microbiology', 'Cappuccino Lab Manual, Prescott’s Microbiology, Fundamentals of Microbiology – Pommerville, Techniques in Microbiology – Frazier, Aneja’s Microbiological Methods', 'NPTEL Micro Techniques, Coursera – Lab Practices, WHO – Infection Control, edX – Lab Management, SWAYAM – Environmental Micro', 'Microbiology with Sumi, NPTEL HRD, Labpedia Academy, Easy Learning Microbiology, MEDSimplified', 'https://microbeonline.com, https://asm.org, https://labtestsonline.org, https://ncbi.nlm.nih.gov, https://swayam.gov.in', 'Colleges provide placement in QA/QC labs, pharma and diagnostics companies, and hospital sterilization departments. Autoclave proficiency is considered a core technical requirement.', 'Lab Technician, Microbiology Analyst, QA/QC Executive, Hospital Infection Control Technician, Research Assistant', 'High demand in labs, hospitals, pharma, diagnostics, and food sectors where sterilization and biosafety are critical.', 'Fresher: ₹2.5–4 LPA, Mid: ₹6–8 LPA, Experienced: ₹10–20+ LPA', 'Internships available at AIIMS, Biocon, Zydus, Serum Institute for culture prep, sterilization management, and lab QA', 'Intern → Technician → QA Analyst → Lab Manager → Microbiologist / Scientist', 'NPTEL Certification, WHO Lab Sterilization, ISO 17025 QA Training, AIIMS Lab Handling Certificate, Coursera Advanced Lab Practices'),
('Science', 'Biochemistry', 'Enzyme Assays', 'AIIMS Delhi, University of Delhi, JNU Delhi, BHU, IISc Bengaluru, Osmania University, Panjab University, St. Xavier\'s Mumbai, Fergusson College Pune, JMI Delhi', 'Enzymology, Biochemical Techniques, Metabolism, Molecular Biology, Protein Chemistry, Instrumentation, Research Methodology', 'Lehninger Principles of Biochemistry – Nelson & Cox, Biochemistry – Stryer, Biochemical Calculations – Segel, Practical Biochemistry – Plummer, Enzymes – Palmer', 'NPTEL Enzyme Technology, Coursera – Biochem Harvard, edX Enzyme Kinetics, SWAYAM Molecular Enzymology, Udemy – Practical Assay Techniques', 'NPTEL HRD, Biology at Ease, Learn Biochem, Labpedia Academy, Shomu’s Biology', 'https://biochemden.com, https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov, https://sciencelearn.org.nz, https://protocols.io, https://swayam.gov.in', 'Placement in pharma, biotech, and R&D sectors; strong preference for enzyme assay expertise for QA and R&D teams', 'Research Associate, QC Analyst, Biochemist, Scientist R&D, Lab Instructor', 'Excellent demand in research, diagnostics, pharmaceuticals, and academic labs. Enzyme assay experts are central to QA and development teams.', 'Fresher: ₹3.5–6 LPA, Mid: ₹8–12 LPA, Senior R&D: ₹15–25+ LPA', 'Internships at Biocon, Serum Institute, Panacea Biotec, Dr. Reddy\'s, AIIMS – covering wet-lab enzymology, assay development, drug-screening', 'Trainee → RA → QC Analyst / Biochemist → Scientist → Group Leader / Director', 'NPTEL Enzyme Tech, WHO Biosafety, Coursera Enzyme Assays, AIIMS Biochem Practical, ISO 17025 Certification');
INSERT INTO `career_recommendation` (`field`, `domain`, `technical_skill`, `best_colleges`, `core_subjects`, `recommended_books`, `online_courses`, `youtube_channels`, `websites`, `placement_info`, `job_roles`, `job_status`, `salary_info`, `training_internship`, `career_path`, `certifications`) VALUES
('Science', 'Biochemistry', 'Western Blotting', 'AIIMS Delhi, University of Delhi, JNU Delhi, BHU, IISc Bengaluru, Osmania University, Panjab University, St. Xavier\'s Mumbai, Fergusson College Pune, Jamia Millia Islamia', 'Protein Chemistry, Molecular Biology, Biochemical Techniques, Immunology, Genetic Engineering, Instrumentation, Cell Signaling', 'Lehninger Biochemistry – Nelson & Cox, Molecular Cloning – Sambrook, Immunoblotting – Austen, Essential Cell Biology – Alberts, Protein Blotting – Kurien', 'NPTEL Biochemistry Labs, Coursera Western Blot by Thermo, edX Molecular Biology, SWAYAM Molecular Diagnostics, Udemy – SDS PAGE to Blotting', 'Addgene, Shomu\'s Biology, BioRender Learning, Labpedia Academy, NPTEL HRD', 'https://addgene.org/protocols/western-blot/, https://bio-rad.com, https://thermofisher.com, https://protocols.io, https://swayam.gov.in', 'Placement opportunities include roles in research labs, pharma R&D, biotech validation departments, and pathology labs. Proficiency in Western blotting is highly valued in proteomics.', 'Research Assistant, Lab Technician, Biochemist, R&D Scientist, QA Executive', 'Western blotting is in high demand in cancer research, infectious disease diagnostics, and therapeutic validation in India and abroad.', 'Fresher: ₹3.5–6 LPA, Mid-level: ₹8–10 LPA, Senior: ₹15–20+ LPA', 'Internships at Biocon, Thermo Fisher, Dr. Reddy\'s, AIIMS, ILS Bhubaneswar – SDS-PAGE, immunodetection, chemiluminescence, troubleshooting', 'Trainee → Research Assistant → Scientist → Project Head → Lab Director', 'NPTEL Certification, Coursera Western Blotting (Thermo), WHO Lab Safety, ICMR Molecular Training, ISO 13485 Biotech Lab Certification'),
('Science', 'Biochemistry', 'DNA Isolation', 'AIIMS Delhi, JNU Delhi, University of Delhi, BHU, IISc Bengaluru, Osmania University, St. Xavier\'s College Mumbai, Jamia Millia Islamia, Fergusson College Pune, Panjab University', 'Molecular Biology, Biochemistry, Cell Biology, Genetics, Nucleic Acid Techniques, Gene Cloning, Analytical Biology', 'Lehninger Principles – Nelson & Cox, Molecular Cloning – Sambrook, DNA Science – Micklos, Cell Biology – Alberts, Gene Manipulation – Primrose', 'NPTEL Molecular Lab, Coursera DNA Isolation, edX Biotech Lab Skills, SWAYAM Molecular Bio, Udemy DNA Extraction', 'Shomu\'s Biology, Biology at Ease, Labpedia Academy, iBiology Techniques, NPTEL HRD', 'https://addgene.org, https://protocols.io, https://thermofisher.com, https://bitesizebio.com, https://swayam.gov.in', 'Placement offered in biotech companies, molecular labs, forensic departments, and research centers. DNA isolation is a gateway to genomics.', 'Research Assistant, Molecular Biologist, Lab Technician, DNA Analyst, Bioinformatician', 'DNA isolation is essential in R&D, diagnostics, agriculture biotech, and medical research. Strong opportunities in India and abroad.', 'Fresher: ₹3.5–6 LPA, Mid-level: ₹7–10 LPA, Senior: ₹12–18+ LPA', 'Internships at Biocon, Thermo Fisher, Mapmygenome, AIIMS, ILS Bhubaneswar – training in DNA extraction, QC, PCR, gel electrophoresis', 'Trainee → Lab Assistant → Molecular Biologist → Scientist → Team Leader', 'NPTEL Certification, Coursera DNA Isolation, ICMR Training, Thermo Fisher Certified Workshop, ISO 15189 Lab Safety & Standards'),
('Science', 'Environmental Science', 'GIS (Geographic Information System)', 'IIRS Dehradun, JNU Delhi, IIT Bombay CESE, University of Delhi, TISS Mumbai, BHU, Pondicherry University, Amity University, AMU, Anna University', 'Remote Sensing, GIS, Environmental Pollution Control, Ecology, EIA, Environmental Laws, Climate Science', 'GIS by DeMers, Remote Sensing by Richards, Environmental Science by Cunningham, GIS Principles by Burrough, Barrett’s Remote Sensing', 'NPTEL GIS, IIRS ISRO, Coursera GIS Specialization, Esri ArcGIS Pro, SWAYAM Environmental GIS', 'ISRO Official, Geospatial World, Learn GIS, NPTEL HRD, NASA EarthData', 'https://bhuvan.nrsc.gov.in, https://earthdata.nasa.gov, https://gisgeography.com, https://iirs.gov.in, https://esri.in', 'Placement opportunities in consultancy firms, smart city planning, NGOs, and government GIS cells', 'GIS Analyst, Remote Sensing Expert, Environmental Scientist, Project Consultant', 'Increasing demand due to environmental crisis monitoring, disaster planning, and urban analytics', 'Fresher: ₹3–5.5 LPA, Mid: ₹7–10 LPA, Experienced: ₹12–18+ LPA', 'ISRO IIRS, TERI, CPCB, WWF, State Pollution Control Boards – GIS and RS project internships', 'Trainee → Analyst → Consultant → Project Manager → Strategy Director', 'ISRO GIS Certificate, Esri ArcGIS Certified, NPTEL Remote Sensing, Coursera GIS, Autodesk GIS Integration'),
('Science', 'Environmental Science', 'Remote Sensing', '[\"Indian Institute of Remote Sensing (IIRS), Dehradun\", \"IIT Bombay\", \"IIT Kharagpur\", \"Jawaharlal Nehru University (JNU), New Delhi\", \"Banaras Hindu University (BHU), Varanasi\", \"University of Delhi\", \"Anna University, Chennai\", \"Forest Research Institute (FRI), Dehradun\", \"Osmania University, Hyderabad\", \"Indian Institute of Science (IISc), Bangalore\"]', 'Fundamentals of Remote Sensing, Environmental Science and Ecology, Geographic Information Systems (GIS), Image Processing Techniques, Digital Photogrammetry, Climate Change and Environmental Monitoring, Data Analysis & Modeling, Environmental Impact Assessment', '[\"Remote Sensing and Image Interpretation – Lillesand, Kiefer & Chipman\", \"Fundamentals of Remote Sensing – George Joseph\", \"Introduction to Environmental Remote Sensing – Andrew Green\", \"GIS and Remote Sensing: Applications in Environmental Studies – S.K. Saha\", \"Principles of Geographic Information Systems – Peter A. Burrough & Rachael A. McDonnell\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"IIRS\",\"course\":\"Introduction to Remote Sensing\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"GIS and Remote Sensing Specialization - University of California, Davis\"},{\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Remote Sensing and GIS Fundamentals\"},{\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\",\"course\":\"Earth Observation from Space: The Optical View\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Geospatial and Environmental Analysis - University of California, Davis\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Indian Institute of Remote Sensing (IIRS)\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/IIRSOfficial\"},{\"title\":\"GIS & Remote Sensing Tutorials by GeoAwesomeness\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/geoawesomeness\"},{\"title\":\"ESRI India\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/EsriIndia\"},{\"title\":\"Remote Sensing Tutorials by GIS Geography\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzT8ZZPTk1Z0cRlM9eEBtVg\"},{\"title\":\"NASA Earth Observatory\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/NASAEarthObservatory\"}]', '[\"https://iirs.gov.in/\", \"https://www.nrsc.gov.in/\", \"https://www.isro.gov.in/earth-observation\", \"https://www.gisdevelopment.net/\", \"https://earthdata.nasa.gov/\", \"https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/environmental-science-and-policy\"]', 'Good placement records in IIRS, IITs, JNU with opportunities in government agencies like ISRO, NRSC, environmental consulting firms and private GIS companies.', 'Remote Sensing Analyst, GIS Technician, Environmental Data Analyst, GIS Specialist, Environmental Consultant, Research Associate, Project Manager, Senior Scientist, Remote Sensing Expert, Policy Advisor', 'Growing demand in environmental monitoring, disaster management, urban planning, agriculture, forestry, climate research; strong presence in government and private sectors.', '{\"starting\":\"₹3,00,000 - ₹5,00,000 per annum\",\"mid_level\":\"₹5,00,000 - ₹8,00,000 per annum\",\"experienced\":\"₹8,00,000 - ₹15,00,000+ per annum\"}', 'Internships available at ISRO’s IIRS, NRSC, Space Applications Centres, Forest Research Institutes, private GIS firms with focus on satellite data processing and GIS software.', 'Entry Level: Remote Sensing Analyst, GIS Technician, Environmental Data Analyst; Mid Level: GIS Specialist, Environmental Consultant, Research Associate; Senior Level: Project Manager, Senior Scientist, Remote Sensing Expert, Policy Advisor; Academia/Research: Lecturer, Research Scientist', 'Certificates from IIRS/ISRO on Remote Sensing & GIS, Esri Technical Certification, Coursera/edX/Udemy online course certificates, specialized courses on Climate Change and Environmental Impact Assessment'),
('Science', 'Environmental Science', 'Pollution Monitoring Instruments', '[\"Indian Institute of Technology (IIT), Kharagpur\", \"Jawaharlal Nehru University (JNU), New Delhi\", \"University of Delhi, Delhi\", \"IIT Bombay\", \"Banaras Hindu University (BHU), Varanasi\", \"National Institute of Environmental Health Sciences, Bhopal\", \"Anna University, Chennai\", \"Forest Research Institute (FRI), Dehradun\", \"Amity University, Noida\", \"Tata Institute of Social Sciences (TISS), Mumbai\"]', 'Environmental Pollution and Control Technologies, Instrumentation and Measurement Techniques, Air, Water, and Soil Quality Analysis, Environmental Chemistry and Microbiology, Analytical Techniques in Environmental Science, Sampling Methods and Data Analysis, Environmental Toxicology, Environmental Impact Assessment', '[\"Environmental Instrumentation and Analysis – Roman M. Pallas\", \"Air Quality Monitoring and Control Strategy – R.K. Trivedi\", \"Environmental Pollution Monitoring – F.W. Fifield & P.J. Haines\", \"Handbook of Environmental Analysis – Pradyot Patnaik\", \"Environmental Monitoring and Characterization – Janick Artiola, Ian L. Pepper, Mark L. Brusseau\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Environmental Monitoring\"},{\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Air Pollution – Monitoring, Modelling, Health\"},{\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Environmental Instrumentation\"},{\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\",\"course\":\"Water Quality Monitoring\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Basics of Pollution Control Instruments\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Environmental Monitoring by NPTEL\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLbMVogVj5nJSb2ZLdf9lf9i6GPlgP2sXL\"},{\"title\":\"EnviroMentor\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/EnviroMentor\"},{\"title\":\"Learn Pollution Monitoring Instruments\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpTqD2v1MF5H6RkJO9KgkRA\"},{\"title\":\"Environmental Science Tutorials\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Environmental