('Science', 'Earth Science / Geology', 'Mineral Identification', '[\"Indian Institute of Science (IISc), Bangalore\", \"Indian Institute of Technology (IIT), Kharagpur\", \"Indian School of Mines (IIT Dhanbad)\", \"Banaras Hindu University (BHU), Varanasi\", \"University of Delhi, Delhi\", \"Jawaharlal Nehru University (JNU), New Delhi\", \"University of Calcutta, Kolkata\", \"University of Madras, Chennai\", \"University of Mumbai, Mumbai\", \"Birbal Sahni Institute of Palaeosciences, Lucknow\"]', 'Mineralogy, Petrology, Optical Mineralogy, Geochemistry, Crystallography, Geophysics, Analytical Techniques in Mineral Identification, Economic Geology, Environmental Geology', '[\"Manual of Mineralogy – Cornelis Klein & Barbara Dutrow\", \"Introduction to Mineralogy – William D. Nesse\", \"Optical Mineralogy – Cornelis Klein\", \"Mineralogy – Dexter Perkins\", \"Economic Mineral Deposits – Walter L. Pohl\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Mineralogy and Petrology\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Introduction to Mineralogy\"},{\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Geology and Mineral Exploration\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Optical Mineralogy Basics\"},{\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\",\"course\":\"Geochemistry and Mineral Identification\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Geology Hub\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/GeologyHub\"},{\"title\":\"Earth Science Tutorials\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/EarthScienceTutorials\"},{\"title\":\"Mineralogy and Petrology Lectures\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/MineralogyPetrology\"},{\"title\":\"The Geology Channel\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/TheGeologyChannel\"},{\"title\":\"NPTEL Geology Lectures\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/nptelhrd\"}]', '[\"https://www.gsi.gov.in/\", \"https://www.iitism.ac.in/\", \"http://www.minerals.net/\", \"https://www.mindat.org/\", \"https://www.usgs.gov/mission-areas/mineral-resources\"]', 'Good placements in mining companies, mineral exploration firms, research institutions, and government agencies like GSI and ISM; industrial internships and fieldwork experience enhance employability.', 'Mineralogist Trainee, Junior Geologist, Mineral Analyst, Exploration Geologist, Senior Geologist, Mineral Resource Manager, Consultant, Lecturer, Research Scientist', 'Consistent demand for mineralogists in mining, exploration, environmental geology, and academia; opportunities in public sector units, private mining firms, and geological research labs.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2,50,000 to ₹4,50,000 per annum\",\"mid_level\":\"₹4,50,000 to ₹7,00,000 per annum\",\"experienced\":\"₹7,00,000 to ₹12,00,000+ per annum\"}', 'Internships at GSI, ISM, mining companies, and geological survey labs; hands-on training in mineral identification techniques, sample preparation, and field surveys.', 'Entry Level: Mineralogist Trainee, Junior Geologist; Mid Level: Mineral Analyst, Exploration Geologist; Senior Level: Senior Geologist, Mineral Resource Manager, Consultant; Academia/Research: Lecturer, Research Scientist', 'Certificate courses in Mineralogy and Petrology from reputed institutes; training in XRD, SEM, and other analytical instruments; online certifications from NPTEL, Coursera, and edX'),
('Commerce', 'Accounting / Finance', 'Tally ERP', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"St. Xavier\'s College, Mumbai\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Narsee Monjee College of Commerce and Economics, Mumbai\", \"Symbiosis College of Arts and Commerce, Pune\", \"Hansraj College, Delhi University\", \"Presidency College, Chennai\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\", \"Banaras Hindu University (BHU), Varanasi\"]', 'Financial Accounting, Cost Accounting, Taxation, Business Law, Auditing, Management Accounting, Economics, Tally ERP and Business Applications, Company Law, Banking and Insurance', '[\"Tally ERP 9 Training Guide – Asok K. Nadhani\", \"Accounting Made Easy – Rajesh Agarwal\", \"Elements of Cost Accounting – M.N. Arora\", \"Practical Guide to GST in Tally ERP 9 – Taxmann\", \"Principles of Accounting – Maheshwari & Maheshwari\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Tally ERP 9 with GST\"},{\"platform\":\"Tally Solutions\",\"course\":\"Tally Prime Complete Course\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Accounting and Bookkeeping Basics\"},{\"platform\":\"NIELIT\",\"course\":\"GST with Tally ERP\"},{\"platform\":\"Skillshare\",\"course\":\"Accounting in Tally Prime\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Tally Solutions\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/TallySolutions\"},{\"title\":\"Accounts Guruji\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AccountsGuruji\"},{\"title\":\"Tally Adda\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/TallyAdda\"},{\"title\":\"Accounting Master\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AccountingMaster\"},{\"title\":\"Learn with Sumit\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/LearnWithSumit\"}]', '[\"https://tallysolutions.com/\", \"https://www.caclubindia.com/\", \"https://learn.tallysolutions.com/\", \"https://www.accountingcoach.com/\", \"https://cleartax.in/\"]', 'Tally ERP is highly valued in SMEs, CA firms, BPOs, and accounting consultancies. B.Com programs often include recruitment for Accounts Executive, Tally Operator, and Junior Accountant roles. Tally certification improves placement rates significantly.', 'Tally Accountant, Junior Accounts Executive, GST Return Filer, Payroll Executive, Audit Assistant, Finance Executive, MIS Executive, Back Office Accounting Staff, Freelancer for Small Businesses', 'High demand in small to mid-sized businesses, CA firms, and startups. Growing use of Tally Prime creates strong demand in GST and e-Invoicing support roles.', '{\"starting\":\"₹1.8 LPA – ₹3 LPA\",\"mid_level\":\"₹3.5 LPA – ₹6.5 LPA\",\"experienced\":\"₹6.5 LPA – ₹12 LPA+\"}', 'Internships offered by Tally Academy, ICA Edu Skills, NIIT, Aptech. CA firms offer seasonal internships focused on accounting and GST filing. Hands-on experience with Tally Prime and tax returns is highly valued.', 'Entry Level: Tally Operator, Junior Accountant; Mid-Level: GST Expert, Accounts Manager; Senior Level: Finance Manager, Tax Consultant; Entrepreneur: Freelance Accountant; Higher Studies: CA, CMA, MBA (Finance)', 'Tally Essentials Certification (Tally Solutions), Certified GST Practitioner (NACIN), NIELIT Tally ERP Certification, Accounting & Taxation Certification (ICA Edu Skills), Coursera/Udemy certifications for accounting tools'),
('Commerce', 'Accounting / Finance', 'Advanced Excel', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"St. Xavier\'s College, Mumbai\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Narsee Monjee College of Commerce and Economics, Mumbai\", \"Hansraj College, Delhi University\", \"Symbiosis College of Arts and Commerce, Pune\", \"Presidency College, Chennai\", \"St. Joseph\'s College of Commerce, Bangalore\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\"]', 'Financial Accounting, Management Accounting, Business Statistics, Corporate Finance, Taxation, Cost Accounting, Business Analytics, Spreadsheet Modelling, MIS, Advanced Excel Applications in Accounting', '[\"Microsoft Excel Data Analysis and Business Modeling – Wayne Winston\", \"Excel 2021 Bible – Michael Alexander & Dick Kusleika\", \"Financial Modeling in Excel – Danielle Stein Fairhurst\", \"Excel for Accountants – Conrad Carlberg\", \"Advanced Excel for Productivity – Nathan George\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Excel Skills for Business\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Advanced Excel with VBA\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Excel to MySQL: Analytics Techniques\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Excel from Beginner to Advanced\"},{\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Excel Dashboard & Financial Modeling\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Leila Gharani\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/LeilaGharani\"},{\"title\":\"ExcelIsFun\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/ExcelIsFun\"},{\"title\":\"MyOnlineTrainingHub\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/MyOnlineTrainingHub\"},{\"title\":\"Excel Campus\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/ExcelCampus\"},{\"title\":\"PK: An Excel Expert\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/PKAnExcelExpert\"}]', '[\"https://exceljet.net/\", \"https://chandoo.org/\", \"https://trumpexcel.com/\", \"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/excel\", \"https://edu.gcfglobal.org/en/excel/\"]', 'Commerce colleges provide placement opportunities in finance, accounting, MIS, and analyst roles. Companies like EY, Deloitte, TCS, and Genpact recruit heavily for Excel-skilled candidates.', 'MIS Executive, Financial Analyst, Data Analyst, Business Intelligence Associate, Budget Analyst, Accountant (with automation), Excel Trainer, Audit Associate, Operations Analyst', 'High demand across finance, IT, logistics, BPO, and corporate sectors. Excel remains a vital tool in reporting and financial analysis.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2.4 LPA – ₹4 LPA\",\"mid_level\":\"₹4.5 LPA – ₹7 LPA\",\"experienced\":\"₹7 LPA – ₹12+ LPA\"}', 'Internships available at KPMG, Deloitte, Grant Thornton, WNS, and many mid-sized firms. MIS training centers and CA firms offer 3–6 month hands-on training in Excel-based reporting.', 'Entry-Level: MIS Executive, Jr. Financial Analyst; Mid-Level: Data Analyst, Financial Analyst, Team Lead; Senior-Level: Senior Analyst, BI Manager, Finance Manager; Specialization: Excel Automation Consultant, Dashboard Specialist, Trainer', 'Microsoft Office Specialist (MOS) Excel Certification, NSE Certified Excel for Finance, Coursera/LinkedIn Excel Certifications, VBA & Macros Certification, Udemy Advanced Excel Course'),
('Commerce', 'Accounting / Finance', 'SAP', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Mumbai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Narsee Monjee College, Mumbai\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Symbiosis College of Arts and Commerce, Pune\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\", \"University of Mumbai\", \"Delhi University (Hansraj, Hindu, Ramjas)\", \"ICFAI Business School\"]', 'Financial Accounting, Cost Accounting, Business Finance, Taxation, MIS, ERP Systems, SAP FI/CO Modules, Corporate Law, Financial Reporting', '[\"Discover SAP ERP Financials – Venki Krishnamoorthy\", \"Configuring SAP ERP Financials and Controlling – Peter Jones\", \"SAP FI Certification Guide – Stuart Lee\", \"SAP S/4HANA Financial Accounting Certification Guide – Stefanie Hornung\", \"SAP Controlling Configuration Guide – John von Aspen\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"SAP FICO Training\"},{\"platform\":\"Michael Management\",\"course\":\"SAP S/4HANA Finance Certification Course\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"ERP Financials in SAP\"},{\"platform\":\"Simplilearn\",\"course\":\"SAP Accounting Tutorials\"},{\"platform\":\"TCS iON\",\"course\":\"SAP FICO Training\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Michael Management\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/MichaelManagement\"},{\"title\":\"SAP Training and Certification\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/SAPTrainings\"},{\"title\":\"Guru99 SAP Tutorials\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Guru99\"},{\"title\":\"TechnoFunctional Academy\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/TechnoFunctionalAcademy\"},{\"title\":\"Ravi SAP FICO\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/SapFicoTrainingRavi\"}]', '[\"https://training.sap.com/\", \"https://open.sap.com/\", \"https://www.michaelmanagement.com/\", \"https://www.guru99.com/sap-training.html\", \"https://www.saponlinetutorials.com/\"]', 'Many commerce colleges have ERP/SAP training labs or partnerships. SAP FICO-trained students get placed in TCS, Infosys, Wipro, Capgemini, Accenture, and Deloitte. Practical knowledge and SAP certification significantly improve placement rates.', 'SAP FICO Consultant, Financial Analyst with SAP, Accounts Executive (SAP-enabled), ERP Support Analyst, Business Process Analyst – Finance, Controlling Analyst, SAP End User, SAP Support Trainee', 'High demand in IT, consulting, manufacturing, and MNC finance departments. Growing use of S/4HANA and ERP automation ensures consistent job opportunities.', '{\"starting\":\"₹3.5 – ₹5.5 LPA\",\"mid_level\":\"₹6 – ₹10 LPA\",\"experienced\":\"₹12 – ₹20+ LPA\"}', 'Internships available in TCS, Infosys, Deloitte, Wipro, and SAP-authorized training centers like NIIT, ICA Edu Skills, Atos, and Aptech. Real-time project internships available for SAP FICO configuration and support.', 'Entry Level: SAP End User / Junior FICO Consultant; Mid-Level: SAP Functional Analyst / Business Analyst; Senior-Level: Senior SAP Consultant / Project Lead; Top-Level: ERP Architect / Finance Automation Consultant', 'SAP Certified Application Associate – Financial Accounting with SAP S/4HANA, SAP Certified Application Associate – Management Accounting (CO), ERP Consultant Certificate (SAP-authorized centers), Microsoft Excel + SAP ERP Combo Certification, Financial Analyst with SAP (Great Learning / Simplilearn)'),
('Commerce', 'Accounting / Finance', 'QuickBooks', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Mumbai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Narsee Monjee College, Mumbai\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Hansraj College, Delhi University\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\", \"Presidency College, Chennai\", \"Fergusson College, Pune\", \"Symbiosis College of Arts and Commerce, Pune\"]', 'Financial Accounting, Management Accounting, Business Law, Business Statistics, Taxation, Cost Accounting, Accounting Software Tools, Payroll and Compliance', '[\"QuickBooks 2023 All-in-One For Dummies – Stephen L. Nelson\", \"Bookkeeping and Accounting All-in-One – Lita Epstein\", \"Practical Bookkeeping with QuickBooks Online – Crystalynn Shelton\", \"Mastering QuickBooks 2023 – Crystalynn Shelton\", \"QuickBooks Online For Beginners – Alicia Katz Pollock\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Intuit Academy\",\"course\":\"QuickBooks ProAdvisor Training\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"QuickBooks Online & Desktop\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"QuickBooks Online Training\"},{\"platform\":\"Skillshare\",\"course\":\"Bookkeeping with QuickBooks\"},{\"platform\":\"Intuit Academy\",\"course\":\"Free QuickBooks Learning\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Fit Small Business – QuickBooks\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/FitSmallBusiness\"},{\"title\":\"Hector Garcia CPA\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/hectorgarciacpa\"},{\"title\":\"Alicia Katz Pollock – Royalwise\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@RoyalwiseSolutions\"},{\"title\":\"QuickBooks Tutorials by Intuit\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/QuickBooks\"},{\"title\":\"BookkeepingMaster\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/BookkeepingMaster\"}]', '[\"https://quickbooks.intuit.com/in/\", \"https://quickbooks.intuit.com/learn-support/\", \"https://learnbookkeeping.org/\", \"https://www.accountingcoach.com/\", \"https://www.udemy.com/topic/quickbooks-online/\"]', 'Commerce graduates trained in QuickBooks are placed in SMEs, CA firms, and BPOs serving international clients. QuickBooks certification helps in remote and freelance roles, especially in US-based accounting firms.', 'Bookkeeper (QuickBooks Specialist), Accounting Assistant, Payroll Executive, Accounts Clerk, QuickBooks Process Executive, Remote Bookkeeping Consultant, Audit Executive, Freelancer (GST/Invoicing)', 'Moderate to high demand in small businesses, accounting consultancies, and outsourced US bookkeeping roles. High growth in freelance and cloud-based accounting jobs.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2.2 – ₹3.5 LPA\",\"mid_level\":\"₹4 – ₹6 LPA\",\"freelancer\":\"₹500 – ₹2000 per hour\"}', 'Internships available through Internshala, QuickBooks ProAdvisor program, Indian firms supporting US clients, and finance startups. Short-term QuickBooks-based internships with real client data are common.', 'Entry-Level: Bookkeeper / Jr. Accountant; Mid-Level: Payroll Analyst / Finance Executive; Senior-Level: Financial Analyst / Process Lead; Consultant: Remote Bookkeeping Expert; Growth: MBA (Finance), CPA, ACCA', 'QuickBooks ProAdvisor Certification (Intuit), Certified Bookkeeper (NACPB), Coursera Bookkeeping Specialization, Tally + QuickBooks Combo Certificate, Certified Payroll Executive'),
('Commerce', 'Marketing', 'Digital Marketing', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"NMIMS, Mumbai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Symbiosis College of Arts and Commerce, Pune\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Mumbai\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Delhi University (Hansraj, Hindu, Ramjas)\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\", \"Amity University, Noida\", \"MIT-WPU, Pune\"]', 'Principles of Marketing, Consumer Behavior, Digital Marketing, E-commerce, Advertising & Promotion, Brand Management, Data Analytics, Market Research, SEO, SEM, SMM', '[\"Digital Marketing for Dummies – Ryan Deiss\", \"Contagious – Jonah Berger\", \"Jab Jab Jab Right Hook – Gary Vaynerchuk\", \"Marketing 5.0 – Philip Kotler\", \"The Art of Digital Marketing – Ian Dodson\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Google\",\"course\":\"Fundamentals of Digital Marketing\"},{\"platform\":\"Meta\",\"course\":\"Meta Blueprint Certification\"},{\"platform\":\"HubSpot\",\"course\":\"Inbound Marketing Certification\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Digital Marketing Specialization\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"The Complete Digital Marketing Course\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Neil Patel\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/neilvkpatel\"},{\"title\":\"Simplilearn\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/Simplilearn\"},{\"title\":\"Sorav Jain – Digital Scholar\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/SoravJainOfficial\"},{\"title\":\"WS Cube Tech\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Wscubetech\"},{\"title\":\"Marketing Harry\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/MarketingHarry\"}]', '[\"https://learndigital.withgoogle.com/digitalgarage\", \"https://academy.hubspot.com/\", \"https://digitaldeepak.com/\", \"https://moz.com/\", \"https://semrush.com/academy\", \"https://blog.hootsuite.com/\"]', 'Colleges with BCom/BBA in marketing offer placement in startups, e-commerce firms, and digital agencies. Companies like Schbang, UpGrad, Wipro, Accenture, and Zoho recruit digital marketers. Freelancing roles are also growing.', 'Digital Marketing Executive, SEO/SEM Specialist, Social Media Manager, Content Strategist, Performance Marketer, Email Marketer, Marketing Analyst, Influencer Manager, Brand Executive, Freelance Marketer', 'High demand across industries, especially post-pandemic. Digital marketing skills are required by startups, agencies, e-commerce platforms, and IT firms. Remote and freelance opportunities are increasing.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2.5 – ₹4.5 LPA\",\"mid_level\":\"₹5 – ₹8 LPA\",\"experienced\":\"₹8 – ₹15+ LPA\",\"freelancer\":\"₹500 – ₹5000/hour\"}', 'Internships available on Internshala, HelloIntern, and LinkedIn. Top firms: Schbang, Webchutney, WhiteHat Jr., UpGrad, Social Beat. Google Digital Garage and HubSpot also offer simulated project-based training.', 'Intern → Digital Marketing Associate → SEO/SMM Specialist → Digital Marketing Manager → CMO / Consultant / Freelancer / Agency Owner', 'Google Digital Garage Certification, Meta Blueprint Certification, HubSpot Inbound Certificate, SEMRush Academy Certificate, Digital Scholar Internship Program, Udemy/LinkedIn Certificates with Projects');
INSERT INTO `career_recommendation` (`field`, `domain`, `technical_skill`, `best_colleges`, `core_subjects`, `recommended_books`, `online_courses`, `youtube_channels`, `websites`, `placement_info`, `job_roles`, `job_status`, `salary_info`, `training_internship`, `career_path`, `certifications`) VALUES
('Commerce', 'Marketing', 'SEO (Search Engine Optimization)', '[\"NMIMS, Mumbai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Symbiosis College of Arts and Commerce, Pune\", \"SRCC, Delhi\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Mumbai\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"MCC, Chennai\", \"Delhi University (Hansraj, Hindu, Ramjas)\", \"Amity University, Noida\", \"MIT-WPU, Pune\"]', 'Principles of Marketing, E-commerce, Digital Marketing Fundamentals, Search Engine Optimization, Web Analytics, Content Strategy, Google Tools, Marketing Strategy', '[\"The Art of SEO – Eric Enge\", \"SEO 2024 – Adam Clarke\", \"SEO All-in-One For Dummies – Bruce Clay\", \"Content Chemistry – Andy Crestodina\", \"SEO Workbook – Jason McDonald\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Google\",\"course\":\"Digital Garage – SEO Module\"},{\"platform\":\"Yoast\",\"course\":\"Yoast SEO Academy\"},{\"platform\":\"Moz\",\"course\":\"SEO Essentials Certification\"},{\"platform\":\"SEMRush\",\"course\":\"SEO Toolkit Course\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"SEO Specialization – University of California\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Complete SEO Training – Arun Nagarathanam\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Neil Patel\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/neilvkpatel\"},{\"title\":\"Backlinko\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/backlinko\"},{\"title\":\"Ahrefs\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AhrefsCom\"},{\"title\":\"Simplilearn\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/Simplilearn\"},{\"title\":\"WS Cube Tech\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Wscubetech\"}]', '[\"https://moz.com/learn/seo\", \"https://ahrefs.com/academy\", \"https://yoast.com/academy/\", \"https://www.semrush.com/academy/\", \"https://developers.google.com/search\", \"https://backlinko.com/seo-this-year\"]', 'Commerce students trained in SEO get placed in digital agencies and startups. Roles like SEO Analyst, Content Marketer, and Digital Marketing Associate are commonly offered in placements and freelancing setups.', 'SEO Executive, SEO Analyst, Technical SEO Specialist, Content Strategist, Digital Marketing Associate, SEO Copywriter, Local SEO Consultant, Link Building Expert, Freelance SEO Consultant', 'High demand in IT, media, e-commerce, SaaS, and agency setups. SEO is a foundational digital skill with growing demand in freelancing and remote jobs.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2.5 – ₹4.5 LPA\",\"mid_level\":\"₹5 – ₹8 LPA\",\"senior\":\"₹9 – ₹15+ LPA\",\"freelancer\":\"₹300 – ₹2000/hour\"}', 'Internships offered on Internshala, HelloIntern, and LinkedIn. Top firms include Schbang, Digital Scholar, SEOValley, Webenza. Live project internships available via Digital Deepak & WS Cube Tech.', 'Intern → SEO Analyst → Sr. SEO Specialist → SEO Manager → SEO Consultant → Growth Marketing Head or Agency Owner', 'Google Digital Garage – SEO Certificate, Moz SEO Essentials Certificate, SEMRush SEO Toolkit Certificate, HubSpot SEO Certification, Yoast SEO Academy Certificate, Coursera SEO Specialization, Udemy Complete SEO Course Certificate'),
('Commerce', 'Marketing', 'Google Ads (PPC)', '[\"NMIMS, Mumbai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"Symbiosis College of Arts and Commerce, Pune\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Mumbai\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\", \"Amity University, Noida\", \"Delhi University (Hansraj, Hindu, Ramjas Colleges)\", \"MIT-WPU, Pune\"]', 'Principles of Marketing, Consumer Behavior, Advertising & Promotion, Digital Marketing, Paid Media Marketing, Performance Marketing, Web Analytics, ROI Optimization', '[\"Ultimate Guide to Google Ads – Perry Marshall\", \"Google Ads Workbook – Jason McDonald\", \"Digital Marketing for Dummies – Ryan Deiss\", \"Killer Facebook Ads – Marty Weintraub\", \"Made to Stick – Chip Heath\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Google Skillshop\",\"course\":\"Google Ads Certifications\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Google Ads for Beginners – University of Colorado\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Complete Google Ads Training – Isaac Rudansky\"},{\"platform\":\"HubSpot\",\"course\":\"Paid Media & Performance Marketing\"},{\"platform\":\"Simplilearn\",\"course\":\"Advanced PPC Certification\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Surfside PPC\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/SurfsidePPC\"},{\"title\":\"MeasureSchool\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/MeasureSchool\"},{\"title\":\"Himanshu Sharma – OptimizeSmart\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@Optimizesmart\"},{\"title\":\"WS Cube Tech\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Wscubetech\"},{\"title\":\"PPC Mastery\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@ppcmastery\"}]', '[\"https://skillshop.withgoogle.com/\", \"https://ppcmastery.com/\", \"https://www.wordstream.com/\", \"https://moz.com/learn/seo/ppc\", \"https://adspresso.com/\", \"https://www.semrush.com/academy/\"]', 'Commerce students certified in Google Ads get placed in digital marketing firms, ad agencies, and e-commerce startups. Entry-level roles like PPC Executive or Ads Analyst are common. Top recruiters include Schbang, Webenza, UpGrad, and Performics.', 'Google Ads Specialist, PPC Executive, SEM Analyst, Performance Marketing Executive, Media Buyer, Paid Ads Strategist, YouTube Ads Manager, Freelance Campaign Manager', 'Very high demand across startups, ad agencies, and e-commerce firms. Google Ads experts are essential for ROI-driven marketing. Global freelancing and agency consulting are growing fast.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2.8 – ₹4.5 LPA\",\"mid_level\":\"₹5 – ₹8.5 LPA\",\"senior\":\"₹9 – ₹15+ LPA\",\"freelancer\":\"₹400 – ₹3000/hour\"}', 'Internships available via Internshala, LetsIntern, and LinkedIn. Leading companies: Schbang, Digital Deepak, iProspect, SEOValley, Performics India. Google Ads simulation training via Skillshop is also valuable.', 'Intern → Google Ads Executive → PPC Specialist → Performance Marketing Manager → Paid Ads Consultant / Media Buying Lead → Freelancer or Agency Owner', 'Google Ads Search Certification, Google Ads Display/Video/Shopping Certifications, Google Measurement Certification, SEMRush PPC Certificate, HubSpot Paid Media Certificate, Udemy PPC Certification with live projects'),
('Commerce', 'Marketing', 'CRM Tools (Customer Relationship Management)', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"NMIMS, Mumbai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Symbiosis College of Arts and Commerce, Pune\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Mumbai/Kolkata\", \"Delhi University (Hansraj, Hindu, Ramjas)\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\", \"Amity University, Noida\", \"MIT-WPU, Pune\"]', 'Principles of Marketing, Customer Relationship Management, Sales & Distribution Management, Consumer Behavior, Data Analytics, Marketing Automation, Business Communication, CRM Software, Email Marketing, Digital Marketing Basics', '[\"Customer Relationship Management – Alok Kumar Rai\", \"CRM at the Speed of Light – Paul Greenberg\", \"Salesforce CRM Admin Handbook – Paul Goodey\", \"Marketing 5.0 – Philip Kotler\", \"CRM Fundamentals – Scott Kostojohn\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Salesforce Trailhead\",\"course\":\"CRM Admin Essentials\"},{\"platform\":\"HubSpot Academy\",\"course\":\"CRM & Inbound Marketing Certification\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"CRM – University of Virginia\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Salesforce/Zoho/HubSpot CRM Essentials\"},{\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"CRM Fundamentals & Sales Tools\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Salesforce Apex Hours\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/SalesforceApexHours\"},{\"title\":\"HubSpot\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/HubSpot\"},{\"title\":\"Zoho CRM\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/ZohoCRM\"},{\"title\":\"Simplilearn\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/Simplilearn\"},{\"title\":\"WS Cube Tech\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Wscubetech\"}]', '[\"https://trailhead.salesforce.com/\", \"https://academy.hubspot.com/\", \"https://zoho.com/crm/\", \"https://freshworks.com/freshsales-crm/\", \"https://www.coursera.org/\", \"https://blog.hubspot.com/\"]', 'Students certified in CRM and automation tools are placed in B2B SaaS firms, marketing agencies, customer success teams, and CRM support roles. Firms like Zoho, Salesforce India, Razorpay, Freshworks, and UpGrad actively recruit CRM-skilled grads.', 'CRM Executive, CRM Administrator, Customer Success Associate, Marketing Automation Executive, Lead Generation Specialist, HubSpot Associate, Salesforce Admin, Email Marketing Executive, CRM Analyst', 'CRM expertise is in rising demand across SaaS, EdTech, FinTech, and E-commerce sectors. CRM tools are core to sales, marketing, and CX operations. Also high demand for CRM freelancers (HubSpot, Zoho).', '{\"starting\":\"₹3 – ₹5 LPA\",\"mid_level\":\"₹6 – ₹10 LPA\",\"senior\":\"₹10 – ₹18 LPA\",\"freelance\":\"₹25 – ₹100/hour global\"}', 'Internships available via Internshala, AngelList, LinkedIn. CRM-focused firms include Zoho, Freshworks, Webchutney, UpGrad. Skill-based internships include CRM tool setup, contact segmentation, and automation.', 'Intern → CRM Executive → CRM Admin / Specialist → Marketing Operations Manager / CRM Analyst → CRM Consultant → CX Strategist / Director of CRM Programs', 'Salesforce Administrator Certification, HubSpot CRM Certification, Zoho CRM Consultant Certificate, Freshsales CRM Training, LinkedIn CRM & Sales Tools Certificates, Udemy CRM Practice Certificates'),
('Commerce', 'HR', 'HRMS (Human Resource Management System) Software', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"NMIMS, Mumbai\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Symbiosis College of Arts & Commerce, Pune\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\", \"Amity University\", \"Delhi University (Hansraj, Hindu, Daulat Ram)\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Mumbai/Kolkata\", \"ICFAI Business School, Hyderabad\"]', 'Principles of HRM, Organizational Behavior, Talent Acquisition & Retention, Labor Law & Compliance, Performance Management, Compensation & Benefits, HR Analytics, Training & Development, HRIS / HRMS Applications, Strategic HRM', '[\"Human Resource Management – Gary Dessler\", \"HRM Text & Cases – K. Aswathappa\", \"The HR Scorecard – Dave Ulrich\", \"Performance Management – Herman Aguinis\", \"HR Analytics – Dipak Kumar Bhattacharyya\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"SAP SuccessFactors Training\"},{\"platform\":\"Simplilearn\",\"course\":\"Workday HCM Training\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"HRIS – University of Minnesota\"},{\"platform\":\"Zoho\",\"course\":\"Zoho People HR Certification\"},{\"platform\":\"Darwinbox Academy\",\"course\":\"HRMS Platform Basics\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Simplilearn\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/Simplilearn\"},{\"title\":\"Great Learning\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/GreatLearning\"},{\"title\":\"Darwinbox\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Darwinbox\"},{\"title\":\"Workology\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Workology\"},{\"title\":\"WS Cube Tech\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Wscubetech\"}]', '[\"https://successfactors.com/\", \"https://zoho.com/people\", \"https://workday.com\", \"https://darwinbox.com\", \"https://hrhelpboard.com\", \"https://hrtechnologist.com\"]', 'Students with HRMS training are hired for HR Operations, Payroll, and HR Data roles in IT firms, MNCs, and HR outsourcing companies. Popular recruiters: Zoho, Freshworks, TCS, Wipro, Deloitte, Keka, Darwinbox.', 'HRMS Analyst, HRIS Executive, Payroll and Compliance Officer, HR Data Administrator, Employee Engagement Officer, HR Operations Associate, Talent Acquisition Specialist, HR Systems Consultant', 'High demand in IT services, HR tech firms, and global corporations adopting cloud HRMS tools. HR digital transformation is a growing field, with rising freelance and remote roles.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2.8 – ₹4.5 LPA\", \"mid_level\":\"₹5.5 – ₹9 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹10 – ₹16 LPA\", \"freelance\":\"₹500 – ₹2000/hour\"}', 'Internships offered by Zoho, Darwinbox, Freshworks, Deloitte, and HR outsourcing firms. Projects include onboarding automation, payroll management, employee database setup, and analytics reporting.', 'Intern → HRMS Executive → HRMS Analyst → HRIS Manager → HR Digital Transformation Lead → Director – People Operations / HR Tech Consultant', 'SAP SuccessFactors Associate Certification, Workday HCM Certification, Zoho People Product Certification, LinkedIn Learning HRIS Courses, Darwinbox Academy Certification, Coursera HR Analytics Certification'),
('Commerce', 'HR', 'Payroll Management', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"NMIMS, Mumbai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Symbiosis School of HRM, Pune\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\", \"Amity University, Noida\", \"Delhi University (Hansraj, Hindu, Ramjas)\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Kolkata/Mumbai\", \"ICFAI Business School (IBS), Hyderabad\"]', 'Payroll Systems, Indian Labor Laws, Compensation & Benefits, Income Tax & TDS Provisions, Attendance & Leave Management, Payroll Accounting, Statutory Deductions, HR & Finance Software, Compliance Management, HR Operations', '[\"Payroll Management – Saroj Shukla\", \"Compensation Management – Richard Henderson\", \"Employee Compensation – Martocchio\", \"HR & Payroll for Beginners – Saikat Dey\", \"HR Policies & Practices in India – D.K. Bhattacharyya\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"GreytHR Academy\",\"course\":\"Payroll Certification\"},{\"platform\":\"Zoho\",\"course\":\"Zoho Payroll Certification\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Payroll Processing in India\"},{\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Payroll Management Training\"},{\"platform\":\"Simplilearn\",\"course\":\"Payroll & Labor Law Basics\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"GreytHR Academy\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@greythr\"},{\"title\":\"WS Cube Tech\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Wscubetech\"},{\"title\":\"Simplilearn HR\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/Simplilearn\"},{\"title\":\"Zoho People & Payroll\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/ZohoPeople\"},{\"title\":\"Great Learning HR Tutorials\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/GreatLearning\"}]', '[\"https://academy.greythr.com/\", \"https://zoho.com/in/payroll/\", \"https://cleartax.in/\", \"https://adp.in/\", \"https://hrhelpboard.com/\", \"https://keka.com/\"]', 'Students trained in Payroll Management are placed in HR outsourcing firms, MNCs, and HR departments of corporates. Roles include Payroll Executive, HR Ops Associate, and Compliance Analyst. Recruiters include TCS, Infosys, Keka, Zoho, ADP, GreytHR, Deloitte, and Wipro.', 'Payroll Executive, HR Operations Executive, Salary & Compliance Analyst, Compensation & Benefits Specialist, Payroll Manager, Statutory Compliance Officer, HR Shared Services Analyst, Labor Law Compliance Manager', 'There is consistent demand in HR Outsourcing, IT/BPO, and large MNCs. Payroll professionals with statutory and software expertise are highly valued. Cloud-based payroll tools are in high demand.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2.5 – ₹4.5 LPA\", \"mid_level\":\"₹5 – ₹8.5 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹9 – ₹14 LPA\", \"freelance\":\"₹500 – ₹2000/hour\"}', 'Internships are available via Internshala, Naukri Campus, and LinkedIn. Companies include GreytHR, Zoho, Keka, ADP, Infosys BPM. Tasks include salary sheet creation, tax calculation, compliance reporting, and leave management.', 'Intern → Payroll Associate → Payroll Analyst → Payroll Manager → HRBP → Head of Payroll & Compliance → Consultant', 'GreytHR Certified Payroll Professional, Zoho Payroll Certification, ADP Payroll Training, Udemy – Payroll Processing India, LinkedIn – Payroll Fundamentals, NIIT/Naukri Learning – Payroll Training'),
('Commerce', 'HR', 'Talent Acquisition Tools', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"NMIMS, Mumbai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Symbiosis Institute of Business Management (SIBM), Pune\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Kolkata / Mumbai\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\", \"Delhi University (Hansraj, Hindu, Daulat Ram)\", \"Amity University, Noida\", \"ICFAI Business School (IBS), Hyderabad\"]', 'Principles of Human Resource Management, Organizational Behavior, Recruitment & Selection, Compensation & Benefits, HR Analytics, Strategic Talent Management, Employment Law, HR Technology & Systems, Interviewing Techniques, Employer Branding', '[\"Recruitment and Selection – Gareth Roberts\", \"Hiring for Attitude – Mark Murphy\", \"Talent Acquisition and Management – Paul Sparrow\", \"The Employer Brand – Simon Barrow\", \"High-Impact Interview Questions – Victoria Hoevemeyer\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Talent Acquisition & ATS Tools\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Recruiting, Hiring & Onboarding Employees\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Talent Acquisition & Full-Cycle Recruiting\"},{\"platform\":\"Zoho Recruit Academy\",\"course\":\"Recruiter Certification\"},{\"platform\":\"Simplilearn\",\"course\":\"Recruitment Management & Sourcing\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Zoho Recruit Academy\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/ZohoRecruit\"},{\"title\":\"LinkedIn Talent Solutions\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/LinkedInTalentSolutions\"},{\"title\":\"Simplilearn HR\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/Simplilearn\"},{\"title\":\"Great Learning HR\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/GreatLearning\"},{\"title\":\"WS Cube Tech – HR\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Wscubetech\"}]', '[\"https://recruit.zoho.com/\", \"https://www.naukri.com/recruiters/rms\", \"https://www.linkedin.com/talent/\", \"https://www.greenhouse.io/\", \"https://www.workable.com/\", \"https://hrtechnologist.com/\", \"https://hrhelpboard.com/\"]', 'Students trained in talent acquisition tools are placed in corporate HR departments, recruitment agencies, HR tech companies, and MNCs. Recruiters include Zoho, TCS, Wipro, Infosys, Darwinbox, Razorpay, and Amazon.', 'Talent Acquisition Executive, Recruitment Analyst, ATS Coordinator, HR Tech Recruiter, Recruitment Operations Executive, Employer Branding Coordinator, Full-Cycle Recruiter, Recruitment Consultant', 'High demand in HR Tech firms, large corporations, and recruitment agencies. TA tools and ATS systems are now standard, and remote/freelance recruiter roles are growing globally.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2.8 – ₹4.5 LPA\", \"mid_level\":\"₹5 – ₹8.5 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹9 – ₹15 LPA\", \"freelance\":\"₹500 – ₹2000/hour\"}', 'Internships available via Internshala, Naukri Campus, and LinkedIn. Companies include Zoho Recruit, Darwinbox, Freshworks, Infosys, Razorpay, Accenture. Interns work on sourcing, resume screening, ATS usage, interview coordination.', 'Intern → Talent Acquisition Associate → Recruiter → Senior TA Specialist → TA Lead / HRBP → Head of Talent Acquisition / Global TA Manager', 'LinkedIn Talent Solutions Certification, Zoho Recruit Certification, Workable ATS Training, Oracle Taleo Training, Coursera Talent Acquisition Specialization, Udemy Full-Cycle Recruiter Certificate, HubSpot Inbound Recruiting Certification'),
('Commerce', 'Business Administration', 'MS Excel', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"NMIMS, Mumbai\", \"Symbiosis Centre for Management Studies, Pune\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Mumbai/Kolkata\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\", \"Delhi University (Hansraj, Hindu, Daulat Ram)\", \"Amity Business School\", \"ICFAI Business School (IBS)\"]', 'Principles of Management, Business Statistics, Financial Accounting, Marketing Management, Business Analytics, Financial Modeling, Operations Management, Human Resource Management, Organizational Behavior, Information Systems for Business', '[\"Excel Bible – John Walkenbach\", \"Excel for Dummies – Greg Harvey\", \"Financial Modeling in Excel – Danielle Stein Fairhurst\", \"Power Pivot and Power BI – Rob Collie\", \"Data Analysis Using Excel – Michael R. Middleton\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Excel Essentials – Microsoft\"},{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Microsoft Excel – Beginners to Advanced\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Excel Skills for Business – Macquarie University\"},{\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Analyzing Data with Excel\"},{\"platform\":\"Excel VBA – Udemy/Simplilearn\",\"course\":\"Excel VBA Programming\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Leila Gharani\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/LeilaGharani\"},{\"title\":\"ExcelIsFun\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/ExcelIsFun\"},{\"title\":\"Chandoo\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/chandoo\"},{\"title\":\"MyOnlineTrainingHub\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/MyOnlineTrainingHub\"},{\"title\":\"Learn with Sumit\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/LearnwithSumit\"}]', '[\"https://exceljet.net\", \"https://chandoo.org\", \"https://support.microsoft.com/excel\", \"https://trumpexcel.com\", \"https://myonlinetraininghub.com\", \"https://mrexcel.com\"]', 'MS Excel proficiency is highly valued in finance, admin, data analysis, HR, and reporting roles. Companies like Deloitte, TCS, Infosys, Zoho, HDFC, Wipro, and KPMG regularly hire graduates with strong Excel skills.', 'Business Analyst, MIS Executive, HR Executive, Sales/Operations Coordinator, Financial Analyst, Excel Automation Specialist, Supply Chain Analyst, Project Coordinator', 'MS Excel remains a core tool across all industries. Demand is high for professionals with advanced Excel, dashboard, and automation skills. Excel + Power BI / SQL creates higher growth opportunities.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2.5 – ₹4.5 LPA\", \"mid_level\":\"₹5 – ₹8.5 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹9 – ₹14 LPA\", \"vba_specialist\":\"₹10 – ₹20 LPA\", \"freelancer\":\"₹300 – ₹2000/hour\"}', 'Internships available at Deloitte, Capgemini, Zoho, Tata Capital, Genpact, Infosys. Tasks include Excel dashboards, sales/HR reporting, financial modeling, data analysis and automation using VBA.', 'Intern → MIS Executive → Data Analyst → Business Analyst → Excel Specialist → BI Developer → Reporting Manager / Excel Consultant', 'Microsoft Excel Specialist Certification (MOS), Excel Skills for Business – Coursera (Macquarie), Leila Gharani Excel Dashboard Certificate, LinkedIn Learning Excel Certificate, Excel VBA Certification – Udemy, edX Excel Data Analysis Certificate'),
('Commerce', 'Business Administration', 'MIS (Management Information System) Reports', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"NMIMS, Mumbai\", \"Symbiosis Centre for Management Studies, Pune\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Kolkata / Mumbai\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Delhi University Colleges (Hansraj, Hindu, Ramjas)\", \"Amity Business School, Noida\", \"ICFAI Business School (IBS), Hyderabad\", \"Madras Christian College (MCC), Chennai\"]', 'Management Information Systems, Business Analytics, Excel & Advanced Excel, Data Visualization, Accounting & Financial Reporting, Operations & Logistics, Database Management Systems, Organizational Behavior, Business Communication, Business Statistics', '[\"MIS: Management Information Systems – Kenneth C. Laudon\", \"Excel Data Analysis – Michael R. Middleton\", \"Data Visualization with Excel Dashboards – Jordan Goldmeier\", \"Business Analytics – Powell & Baker\", \"MIS for Business – O’Brien & Marakas\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"MIS Reporting & Excel Dashboards\"},{\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"MIS & Data Analytics Courses\"},{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Excel to MySQL: Analytics Techniques\"},{\"platform\":\"Simplilearn\",\"course\":\"Business Intelligence Reporting\"},{\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Data Visualization with Excel\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Learn with Sumit\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/LearnwithSumit\"},{\"title\":\"Leila Gharani\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/LeilaGharani\"},{\"title\":\"ExcelIsFun\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/ExcelIsFun\"},{\"title\":\"Yoda Learning\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/YodaLearningSolutions\"},{\"title\":\"Great Learning\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/GreatLearning\"}]', '[\"https://excelsuperstar.org\", \"https://chandoo.org\", \"https://trumpexcel.com\", \"https://exceljet.net\", \"https://support.microsoft.com/excel\", \"https://sqlzoo.net\"]', 'MIS knowledge is a strong asset in analyst, admin, operations, sales, HR, and finance roles. Companies such as Infosys, Wipro, HCL, Deloitte, Genpact, ICICI, Accenture, Reliance, and Amazon actively hire for these roles.', 'MIS Executive, Reporting Analyst, Business Analyst, Operations Executive, Data Entry + Automation Specialist, Sales/HR Coordinator, CRM Data Manager, Excel Dashboard Developer', 'MIS roles are in constant demand across departments. Excel + SQL or Power BI skills improve growth prospects. Freelance MIS consultants and dashboard creators are in demand for startups and SMEs.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2.5 – ₹4.2 LPA\", \"mid_level\":\"₹4.5 – ₹7.5 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹8 – ₹12 LPA\", \"freelancer\":\"₹400 – ₹1500/hour\"}', 'Internships available on Internshala, Naukri Campus, LinkedIn. Companies include Infosys, Zoho, Deloitte, HCL, Capgemini, and Genpact. Interns work on dashboard creation, MIS documentation, data cleaning, SQL report extraction.', 'Intern → MIS Executive → Reporting Analyst → MIS/BI Analyst → Business Analyst → MIS Consultant / Automation Specialist → Manager / Operations Head', 'Microsoft Excel Specialist (MOS), Udemy – MIS Reporting & Dashboard Expert, LinkedIn – Business Analytics with Excel, Coursera – Excel to MySQL Analytics, Google Sheets – Automation & Scripting Certificate, Great Learning – MIS Dashboard Training'),
('Commerce', 'Business Administration', 'Business Analytics', '[\"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"NMIMS, Mumbai\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Symbiosis Centre for Management Studies, Pune\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"St. Xavier’s College, Mumbai/Kolkata\", \"Delhi University (Hansraj, Hindu, Ramjas)\", \"Amity University\", \"ICFAI Business School (IBS)\", \"IIM Indore (IPM)\"]', 'Business Statistics, Data Analytics & Visualization, Database Management (SQL), Marketing/HR/Finance Analytics, Predictive Modeling, Excel & Advanced Excel, Python or R for Data Science, Machine Learning for Business, Business Communication, Operations & Supply Chain Analytics', '[\"Data Science for Business – Foster Provost\", \"Business Analytics: The Art of Modeling – Powell & Baker\", \"Competing on Analytics – Thomas Davenport\", \"Storytelling with Data – Cole Nussbaumer\", \"Python for Data Analysis – Wes McKinney\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Business Analytics Specialization – Wharton\"}, {\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Google Data Analytics Certificate\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Business Analytics with Excel, SQL, Power BI\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Business Analytics – IIMB / Harvard\"}, {\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Business Analyst Career Path\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Alex The Analyst\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AlexTheAnalyst\"}, {\"title\":\"Luke Barousse\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/LukeBarousse\"}, {\"title\":\"Simplilearn – Analytics\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Simplilearn\"}, {\"title\":\"CodeBasics\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/codebasics\"}, {\"title\":\"Great Learning\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/GreatLearning\"}]', '[\"https://www.analyticsvidhya.com\", \"https://www.kaggle.com\", \"https://towardsdatascience.com\", \"https://datacamp.com\", \"https://mavenanalytics.io\", \"https://sqlzoo.net\"]', 'Analytics graduates are hired across industries like consulting, banking, tech, logistics, and marketing. Top recruiters include KPMG, Deloitte, EY, Accenture, Mu Sigma, TCS, Genpact, Cognizant, Flipkart, Amazon.', 'Business Analyst, Data Analyst, Marketing / HR / Finance Analyst, MIS Analyst, SQL Reporting Analyst, Business Intelligence Analyst, Product Analyst, Data Visualization Consultant', 'Business Analytics roles are in extremely high demand across startups, MNCs, and product companies. Career prospects are strong in tech, fintech, health, retail, logistics, and consulting.', '{\"starting\":\"₹3.5 – ₹6 LPA\", \"mid_level\":\"₹7 – ₹12 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹12 – ₹20 LPA\", \"freelancer\":\"₹700 – ₹3000/hour\"}', 'Internships offered by TCS, Cognizant, Accenture, KPMG, Mu Sigma, Razorpay, Zoho. Interns work on dashboards, Excel/SQL-based reporting, trend forecasting, Power BI/Tableau, and data storytelling.', 'Intern → Business Analyst / Data Analyst → BI Analyst / Product Analyst → Lead Analyst → Analytics Manager → Strategy Head / Director of Analytics', 'Google Data Analytics Certificate (Coursera), Tableau / Power BI Certification, Microsoft Certified Data Analyst Associate, Coursera Business Analytics Specialization (Wharton), IBM Data Analyst Certificate, Harvard Business Analytics (edX), Excel + SQL + Python Stack Certification'),
('Commerce', 'Economics', 'Data Analysis (SPSS, R)', '[\"Delhi School of Economics\", \"Indian Statistical Institute (ISI), Kolkata\", \"St. Stephen’s College, Delhi\", \"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC), Delhi\", \"Presidency University, Kolkata\", \"Loyola College, Chennai\", \"Madras School of Economics\", \"Ashoka University, Sonipat\", \"Jadavpur University\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\"]', 'Microeconomics, Macroeconomics, Econometrics, Statistics for Economics, Public Finance, International Economics, Research Methodology, Data Science in Economics, Mathematical Economics, Environmental Economics', '[\"Introductory Econometrics – Wooldridge\", \"Econometric Analysis – William Greene\", \"The R Book – Michael Crawley\", \"Discovering Statistics Using SPSS – Andy Field\", \"Basic Econometrics – Damodar Gujarati\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Data Analysis in R for Social Scientists\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Statistical Thinking for Data Science\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Data Analysis Using R\"}, {\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"SPSS and R Training\"}, {\"platform\":\"Datacamp\",\"course\":\"R Programming & SPSS\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"MarinStatsLectures\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/marinstatslectures\"}, {\"title\":\"FreeCodeCamp – R Full Course\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_V8eKsto3Ug\"}, {\"title\":\"Andy Field – SPSS\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL343F1B60FC353D5D\"}, {\"title\":\"DataCamp YouTube\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@DataCamp\"}, {\"title\":\"Economics with R\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@daveyourd\"}]', '[\"https://www.datacamp.com\", \"https://www.r-bloggers.com\", \"https://towardsdatascience.com\", \"https://spss-tutorials.com\", \"https://www.economicshelp.org\", \"https://crantastic.org\"]', 'Students with SPSS and R skills are recruited in consulting, research, government policy, and analytics roles. Firms like Deloitte, EY, NITI Aayog, RBI, World Bank, and research NGOs hire for data-driven economics roles.', 'Economic Research Analyst, Policy Analyst, Business/Data Analyst, Research Associate, Statistician, Market Research Executive, Academic Researcher, Analytics Consultant', 'Very strong demand in government, consulting, and international development. SPSS is key for surveys; R is essential for modern econometric modeling and advanced analytics.', '{\"starting\":\"₹3.5 – ₹6 LPA\", \"mid_level\":\"₹7 – ₹12 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹13 – ₹20 LPA\", \"govt_policy\":\"₹5 – ₹9 LPA (varies by body/org)\"}', 'Internships available at NITI Aayog, RBI, Ministry of Statistics, NGOs, Deloitte, Economic Times Research. Focus on econometrics, forecasting, research writing, data handling in R/SPSS.', 'Intern → Research Assistant → Junior Data Analyst → Economic Analyst → Policy Consultant → Senior Researcher / Govt Policy Head', 'Google Data Analytics Certificate, R Programming – Coursera, SPSS Basics – IBM / Udemy, Econometrics using R – NPTEL, LinkedIn Learning – Data Analysis for Social Science, HarvardX – Data Science Series'),
('Commerce', 'Economics', 'Economic Forecasting', '[\"Indian Statistical Institute (ISI), Kolkata / Delhi\", \"Delhi School of Economics\", \"Shri Ram College of Commerce (SRCC)\", \"St. Stephen’s College\", \"Madras School of Economics\", \"Presidency University\", \"IIT Kanpur / IIT Madras\", \"Jawaharlal Nehru University (JNU)\", \"Ashoka University\", \"Christ University\"]', 'Macroeconomics, Time Series & Forecasting Techniques, Econometrics, Applied Mathematics for Economics, Financial Markets & Indicators, Public Economics & Policy, Economic Modeling & Simulations, Behavioral Economics, Quantitative Techniques, International Economics', '[\"Forecasting: Principles and Practice – Rob J Hyndman\", \"Time Series Analysis – James D. Hamilton\", \"Applied Econometric Time Series – Walter Enders\", \"The Signal and the Noise – Nate Silver\", \"Introduction to Modern Economic Growth – Daron Acemoglu\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Forecasting Models for Business & Economics\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Time Series Forecasting\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"ARIMA & Time Series Forecasting with Python/R\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Economic Indicators & Forecasting\"}, {\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Macroeconomic Forecasting Techniques\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"MarinStatsLectures\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/marinstatslectures\"}, {\"title\":\"Quantitative Economist\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@quantitativeeconomist\"}, {\"title\":\"Statistics Learning Centre\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/StatisticsLearningCentre\"}, {\"title\":\"FreeCodeCamp – Time Series\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZspR5PZemcs\"}, {\"title\":\"IMF\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/IMF\"}]', '[\"https://otexts.com/fpp3/\", \"https://www.r-bloggers.com\", \"https://imf.org/en/Data\", \"https://tradingeconomics.com\", \"https://fred.stlouisfed.org\", \"https://towardsdatascience.com\"]', 'Students with forecasting expertise are placed in policy think tanks, central banks, consulting firms, and financial organizations. Employers include RBI, NITI Aayog, CRISIL, EY, Moody’s, World Bank projects, and rating agencies.', 'Economic Forecaster, Econometrician, Policy Advisor, Research Economist, Financial Market Analyst, Government Research Officer, Quantitative Modeler, Data Scientist (Economics focus)', 'High demand across public and private sectors including financial markets, government policy, multilateral development agencies, and research firms.', '{\"starting\":\"₹4 – ₹7 LPA\", \"mid_level\":\"₹8 – ₹15 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹16 – ₹25+ LPA\", \"govt\":\"₹7 – ₹12 LPA\"}', 'Internships available at RBI, Ministry of Finance, NITI Aayog, CRISIL, ICRA, EY, PwC, IMF projects, PRS Legislative Research. Work includes modeling inflation, forecasting trends, and macroeconomic report writing.', 'Intern → Research Associate → Economist → Policy Consultant → Economic Analyst → Lead Analyst → Forecasting Head / Strategy Advisor → IMF / World Bank Economist', 'Coursera Forecasting Models, IMF Forecasting Certificate, Harvard Economics on edX, R Programming (Datacamp), Time Series Forecasting (NPTEL), LinkedIn Learning Forecasting, Python for Time Series (Udemy)'),
('Commerce', 'International Business', 'Foreign Exchange Tools', '[\"Indian Institute of Foreign Trade (IIFT)\", \"Symbiosis Institute of International Business (SIIB)\", \"IIMs\", \"SPJIMR\", \"JBIMS\", \"Christ University\", \"Amity International Business School\", \"Delhi University - MIB\", \"K J Somaiya Institute\", \"IMI Delhi\"]', 'International Finance, Foreign Exchange Management, Global Economics, Currency Derivatives, Export-Import Procedures, Risk Management in International Trade, Trade Policies & WTO Regulations, Financial Derivatives, Treasury Management, Forex Market Operations', '[\"Multinational Financial Management – Alan Shapiro\", \"Foreign Exchange: A Practical Guide – Tim Weithers\", \"International Financial Management – P.G. Apte\", \"Currency Trading for Dummies – Brian Dolan\", \"Options, Futures & Other Derivatives – John C. Hull\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Currency Risk Management\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"International Finance by IIMBx\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Forex Trading for Beginners\"}, {\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Foreign Exchange Fundamentals\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Global Financial Markets\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Trading 212\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@Trading212\"}, {\"title\":\"Rayner Teo\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/RaynerTeo\"}, {\"title\":\"Bloomberg Markets\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@markets\"}, {\"title\":\"The Plain Bagel\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/ThePlainBagel\"}, {\"title\":\"Market Wizards\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@MarketWizardsIndia\"}]', '[\"https://www.investopedia.com\", \"https://www.tradingview.com\", \"https://www.oanda.com\", \"https://www.babypips.com\", \"https://www.rbi.org.in\", \"https://www.fedai.org.in\"]', 'Top B-Schools place students in banks, export houses, finance firms, and MNCs. Companies like HSBC, HDFC, CitiBank, EXIM Bank, Deloitte, Maersk, and FedEx hire graduates for forex and international trade roles.', 'Foreign Exchange Dealer, Treasury Analyst, Currency Risk Analyst, Trade Compliance Officer, Forex Trader, Trade Finance Officer, Global Supply Chain Risk Analyst, Treasury Sales Manager, Export-Import Analyst', 'Strong demand in banking, international trade, logistics, and finance. Forex roles are increasing with globalization and currency volatility. Regulatory and compliance-based hiring is growing.', '{\"starting\":\"₹4 – ₹7 LPA\", \"mid_level\":\"₹8 – ₹14 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹15 – ₹30+ LPA\", \"self_employed\":\"Varies based on profitability\"}', 'Internships available at RBI, ICICI Bank, Maersk, DHL, EXIM Bank, and logistics firms. Hands-on training in forex dealing, treasury operations, international payments, and compliance reporting.', 'Intern → FX Dealer / Analyst → Forex Risk Manager / Trade Officer → Treasury Head / Director Global Trade → International Business Consultant', 'Certified Treasury Professional (CTP), NISM Currency Derivatives Certificate, Forex Market Professional (NSE), Trade Finance Certificate (IIBF), Bloomberg Terminal Training, Export-Import Management (MSME), Coursera International Business – University of London'),
('Commerce', 'International Business', 'Global Market Analysis', '[\"Indian Institute of Foreign Trade (IIFT)\", \"IIM Ahmedabad\", \"Symbiosis Institute of International Business (SIIB)\", \"SP Jain Institute of Management\", \"IMI Delhi\", \"Jamnalal Bajaj Institute of Management Studies\", \"Christ University\", \"Amity International Business School\", \"K J Somaiya Institute of Management\", \"Delhi University - MIB\"]', 'International Marketing, Global Business Strategy, Global Supply Chain, Cross-Cultural Management, Trade Analytics, Strategic Management, Financial Markets & Investments, Business Intelligence, Global Macroeconomics, Data Analytics for International Markets', '[\"International Marketing – Philip Cateora\", \"Global Business Today – Charles W.L. Hill\", \"Market Entry Strategies – Paul Beamish\", \"The Global Entrepreneur – James F. Foley\", \"Business Analytics – U Dinesh Kumar\", \"Blue Ocean Strategy – Kim & Mauborgne\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"International Business Essentials\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Global Strategic Management – HEC Paris\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Business Analytics\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Market Research for Startups\"}, {\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Global Marketing Trends\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Valuetainment\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Valuetainment\"}, {\"title\":\"Economics Explained\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/EconomicsExplained\"}, {\"title\":\"WION Business\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@WION\"}, {\"title\":\"World Economic Forum\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/WorldEconomicForum\"}, {\"title\":\"Statista\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@Statista\"}]', '[\"https://www.statista.com\", \"https://www.imf.org\", \"https://www.tradingeconomics.com\", \"https://unctad.org\", \"https://www.worldbank.org\", \"https://data.oecd.org\", \"https://www.export.gov\", \"https://www.euromonitor.com\"]', 'Recruitments in consulting, global market research, investment firms, export houses, and international marketing. Firms like Deloitte, PwC, EXIM Bank, HSBC, HUL Global, Bain, and Amazon Global hire extensively.', 'Global Market Analyst, International Business Consultant, Trade Researcher, Country Risk Analyst, Foreign Investment Analyst, Strategy Analyst, Export Market Development Specialist, Competitive Intelligence Analyst', 'Growing demand as Indian companies expand globally. High need for market entry analysis, risk mapping, international strategy, and competitive benchmarking in export-driven businesses.', '{\"entry\":\"₹5 – ₹9 LPA\", \"mid\":\"₹10 – ₹18 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹20 – ₹35+ LPA\", \"global_roles\":\"₹25 – ₹50+ LPA\"}', 'Internships at UNCTAD, PwC, EXIM Bank, WTO India Desk, Invest India, CII, IIFT projects. Tasks include trend reports, market research, trade and FTA study, competitive mapping. Internshala and LinkedIn offer leads.', 'Intern → Market Analyst → International Business Strategist → Regional Head / Expansion Manager → Chief International Business Officer (CIBO)', 'Global Market Analysis – Coursera, International Business Strategy – HEC Paris, Export-Import Management – MSME/IIFT, Bloomberg Terminal Certification, Google Market Research, NISM International Finance Certificate'),
('Commerce', 'Entrepreneurship', 'Business Plan Tools', '[\"IIM Ahmedabad\", \"ISB Hyderabad\", \"XLRI Jamshedpur\", \"SPJIMR Mumbai\", \"NMIMS Mumbai\", \"EDI India\", \"Ashoka University\", \"FLAME University\", \"Christ University\", \"Amity Business School\"]', 'Entrepreneurship & New Venture Creation, Business Planning & Strategy, Innovation & Design Thinking, Market Research, Financial Management, Startup Legal Frameworks, Lean Startup Methodology, Digital Marketing, Product Management, Fundraising & Investor Relations', '[\"The Lean Startup – Eric Ries\", \"Zero to One – Peter Thiel\", \"Business Model Generation – Alexander Osterwalder\", \"The Startup Owner’s Manual – Steve Blank\", \"How to Write a Business Plan – Mike McKeever\", \"Start with Why – Simon Sinek\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Entrepreneurship Specialization – Wharton\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Entrepreneurship in Emerging Economies – Harvard\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Lean Startup & MVP Building\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Innovation and Entrepreneurship\"}, {\"platform\":\"Startup India\",\"course\":\"GOI Free Startup Program\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Y Combinator\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/ycombinator\"}, {\"title\":\"TED Talks – Business\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/TEDtalksDirector\"}, {\"title\":\"Startup India\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@startupindia\"}, {\"title\":\"Stanford eCorner\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/ecorner\"}, {\"title\":\"Alex Hormozi\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@AlexHormozi\"}]', '[\"https://startupindia.gov.in\", \"https://www.bplans.com\", \"https://www.entrepreneur.com\", \"https://www.liveplan.com\", \"https://www.bizplan.com\", \"https://www.yourstory.com\", \"https://www.f6s.com\", \"https://angel.co\"]', 'Entrepreneurship students may launch startups or join incubators, accelerators, venture capital firms, or startup consultancy roles. Colleges also place students in innovation teams of large firms like Razorpay, Amazon, Sequoia, Flipkart Labs, 91Springboard, etc.', 'Startup Founder, Business Planning Analyst, Incubation Manager, Entrepreneur in Residence (EIR), Innovation Consultant, VC/PE Analyst, Startup Coach, Startup Consultant', 'High opportunity due to startup culture growth, government support, and digital business rise. Strong placement support in startup ecosystems and accelerator networks.', '{\"founder\":\"₹0 – Profit based\", \"analyst\":\"₹4 – ₹10 LPA\", \"program_manager\":\"₹8 – ₹15 LPA\", \"vc_analyst\":\"₹12 – ₹25 LPA\", \"funded_ceo\":\"₹15 – ₹50+ LPA\"}', 'Startup India Yatra, Atal Incubation Centers, NSRCEL IIMB, CIIE IIMA, T-Hub, Techstars, Y Combinator Startup School, Internships at accelerators, MSME projects, IIM E-Cells, EDI India, Invest India programs.', 'Intern → Incubated Founder → Revenue Stage Entrepreneur → Funded CEO → Startup Mentor / Angel Investor / VC', 'Startup India Certificate, Coursera Wharton Certificate – Business Model Canvas, edX Harvard Entrepreneurship, Google for Startups, NPTEL Innovation, EDI India Incubation, AWS Activate, Microsoft for Startups, Meta Boost'),
('Commerce', 'Entrepreneurship', 'Pitch Deck Creation', '[\"IIM Ahmedabad\", \"ISB Hyderabad\", \"XLRI Jamshedpur\", \"SP Jain Mumbai\", \"Entrepreneurship Development Institute of India (EDI), Gandhinagar\", \"NMIMS Mumbai\", \"Ashoka University\", \"FLAME University\", \"BITS Pilani\", \"Christ University\"]', 'New Venture Planning, Business Communication & Pitching, Startup Finance, Entrepreneurial Strategy, Design Thinking, Product-Market Fit, Valuation & Fundraising, Marketing for Startups, MVP Development, Investor Relations', '[\"Pitch Anything – Oren Klaff\", \"The Art of Startup Fundraising – Alejandro Cremades\", \"Slide:ology – Nancy Duarte\", \"The Startup Pitch Deck Guide – PitchEnvy\", \"The Lean Startup – Eric Ries\", \"Presentation Zen – Garr Reynolds\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Y Combinator\",\"course\":\"Startup School\"}, {\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Presentation Skills – University of Colorado\"}, {\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Pitching to Investors\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Complete Pitch Deck Masterclass\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Entrepreneurship Pitching – IIMBx\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Slidebean\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@Slidebean\"}, {\"title\":\"Startup India\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@startupindia\"}, {\"title\":\"Y Combinator\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/ycombinator\"}, {\"title\":\"Sequoia India\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@SequoiaIndiaSEA\"}, {\"title\":\"Alex Hormozi\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@AlexHormozi\"}]', '[\"https://pitchdeckhunt.com\", \"https://slidebean.com\", \"https://pitch.com\", \"https://www.beautiful.ai\", \"https://startupindia.gov.in\", \"https://www.bplans.com\", \"https://www.ycombinator.com/library\"]', 'Opportunities in incubators, accelerators, startup programs, and innovation teams. Roles include pitch consultants, strategy interns, and investor relations leads in companies like Sequoia, NSRCEL, CIIE, Techstars, etc.', 'Startup Founder, Investor Pitch Consultant, Fundraising Associate, Deck Designer, Business Development Associate, VC Analyst, Program Manager – Incubators', 'Strong demand in the startup ecosystem for founders and presentation specialists. Increasing use of deck-based communication in early-stage fundraising and growth strategy.', '{\"consultant\":\"₹4 – ₹7 LPA\", \"associate\":\"₹6 – ₹12 LPA\", \"vc_analyst\":\"₹10 – ₹20 LPA\", \"ceo\":\"₹25 – ₹60+ LPA\", \"freelance_deck\":\"₹1,000 – ₹25,000 per project\"}', 'Startup India Yatra, Y Combinator School Projects, NSRCEL (IIMB), CIIE (IIM Ahmedabad), Sequoia Spark Fellowship, Internshala Startup Internships, Techstars Fellowship, Springboard Accelerators', 'Intern → Pitch Consultant → Fundraising Lead → Startup Founder / Co-Founder → Accelerator Mentor / Investor', 'Startup India Certificate, Y Combinator Startup School, Coursera – Presentation Skills, LinkedIn Learning – Pitching, Slidebean Certification, Google Launchpad, AWS Activate, Microsoft for Startups');
INSERT INTO `career_recommendation` (`field`, `domain`, `technical_skill`, `best_colleges`, `core_subjects`, `recommended_books`, `online_courses`, `youtube_channels`, `websites`, `placement_info`, `job_roles`, `job_status`, `salary_info`, `training_internship`, `career_path`, `certifications`) VALUES
('Commerce', 'Entrepreneurship', 'Market Research', '[\"IIM Ahmedabad\", \"ISB Hyderabad\", \"XLRI Jamshedpur\", \"SP Jain Institute of Management and Research\", \"Entrepreneurship Development Institute of India (EDI), Gandhinagar\", \"NMIMS Mumbai\", \"Ashoka University\", \"FLAME University\", \"Christ University\", \"SIBM Pune\"]', 'Marketing Research Techniques, Consumer Behavior, Business Statistics, Business Analytics, Market Segmentation, Competitive Strategy, Product & Pricing Research, Data Visualization, Innovation Management, Business Communication', '[\"Marketing Research – Naresh K. Malhotra\", \"Blue Ocean Strategy – Kim & Mauborgne\", \"Quantitative Research Methods – C. William Emory\", \"Lean Analytics – Croll & Yoskovitz\", \"The Startup Owner’s Manual – Steve Blank\", \"The Mom Test – Rob Fitzpatrick\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Market Research Specialization – UC Davis\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Market Research and Consumer Behavior – IE Business School\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Marketing Research & Data Analysis\"}, {\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Consumer Insight & Analytics\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Marketing Analytics\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Neil Patel\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@neilpatel\"}, {\"title\":\"Google for Startups\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/GoogleStartups\"}, {\"title\":\"Slidebean\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@Slidebean\"}, {\"title\":\"Valuetainment\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/c/Valuetainment\"}, {\"title\":\"Stanford eCorner\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/ecorner\"}]', '[\"https://www.statista.com\", \"https://www.similarweb.com\", \"https://www.google.com/trends\", \"https://www.semrush.com\", \"https://www.yourstory.com\", \"https://www.surveymonkey.com\", \"https://startupindia.gov.in\", \"https://www.mintel.com\"]', 'Placements in market research agencies, innovation labs, startup accelerators, strategy teams, and digital marketing consultancies. Companies like NielsenIQ, EY, Razorpay, Accenture, and RedSeer actively hire.', 'Market Research Analyst, Customer Insight Specialist, Competitive Intelligence Analyst, Startup Research Lead, Product Strategy Associate, Business Development Analyst, Innovation Strategist', 'Rapid growth in demand for validated research, competitive insights, and data-driven startup strategies. High utility in pre-funding, market entry, and business planning phases.', '{\"entry\":\"₹4 – ₹7 LPA\", \"mid\":\"₹8 – ₹15 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹18 – ₹30+ LPA\", \"founder\":\"Variable based on venture success\"}', 'Startup India Internship Portal, Atal Incubation Centers, NSRCEL (IIM Bangalore), CIIE (IIM Ahmedabad), Springboard, Internshala Market Research Roles, LinkedIn Startup Internships', 'Intern → Research Analyst → Insight Lead → Strategy Head / Co-Founder → Angel Investor / VC Analyst', 'Coursera – Market Research, edX – IE Business School, Udemy – Market Research Masterclass, LinkedIn Learning – Consumer Analytics, NPTEL – Marketing Analytics, Startup India Certificate, Google Trends & Analytics (Unofficial)'),
('Commerce', 'Supply Chain Management', 'SAP SCM', '[\"NITIE (IIM Mumbai)\", \"IIM Udaipur\", \"IIFT Delhi\", \"SP Jain Mumbai\", \"Amity Business School\", \"Symbiosis Institute of Operations Management\", \"IMT Ghaziabad\", \"Chandigarh University\", \"Christ University\", \"NMIMS Mumbai\"]', 'Logistics & Distribution Management, Supply Chain Analytics, Procurement & Vendor Management, Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP), Inventory & Warehouse Management, Operations Strategy, SAP ERP Modules – MM, SD, PP, Business Process Integration, Transportation & Freight Management', '[\"Supply Chain Management – Sunil Chopra\", \"Logistics & SCM – Martin Christopher\", \"SAP SCM – Functional Guide\", \"ERP Demystified – Alexis Leon\", \"Production and Operations Management – S.N. Chary\", \"Essentials of Supply Chain Management – Michael Hugos\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Supply Chain Management Specialization – Rutgers\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"SAP SCM, SAP MM, SAP SD – Beginner to Advanced\"}, {\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Logistics & Inventory Essentials\"}, {\"platform\":\"SAP Learning Hub\",\"course\":\"SCM Modules\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Operations & Supply Chain Management\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Michael Management SAP\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/user/michaelmanagement\"}, {\"title\":\"Simplilearn SCM\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@simplilearn\"}, {\"title\":\"Edureka Logistics\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@edurekaIN\"}, {\"title\":\"The Supply Chain Academy\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@thesupplychainacademy\"}, {\"title\":\"Zarantech SAP Training\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@ZaranTechSAPTraining\"}]', '[\"https://learning.sap.com\", \"https://www.michaelmanagement.com\", \"https://www.scmdojo.com\", \"https://www.edx.org\", \"https://supplychaindigital.com\", \"https://www.supplychainbrain.com\", \"https://www.sap.com\"]', 'Recruiters include Deloitte, PwC, Capgemini, Infosys, SAP Labs, Amazon, Flipkart, Nestlé, Maersk, Adani Logistics. Roles span SAP consulting, SCM analysis, ERP implementation, and vendor management.', 'SAP SCM Consultant, Logistics Manager, Procurement Analyst, Supply Chain Planner, Operations Analyst, Inventory Controller, SAP MM / SD Functional Consultant', 'High demand in FMCG, IT consulting, logistics, manufacturing, and e-commerce sectors. SAP-certified professionals see global placement and salary growth.', '{\"entry\":\"₹4 – ₹7 LPA\", \"mid\":\"₹8 – ₹15 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹18 – ₹30+ LPA\", \"freelance\":\"₹800 – ₹5000/hour\"}', 'SAP Learning Hub Internships, Amazon & Flipkart SCM roles, Internships at Nestlé, Tata Steel, Maersk, Unilever, NPTEL industry partners, Michael Management Practice Labs', 'SAP Intern → SAP Functional Consultant → SCM Analyst → Program Manager / Implementation Lead → SAP Architect / Director of Operations', 'SAP Certified Application Associate – S/4HANA SCM, Michael Management SAP SCM Certification, Udemy – SAP SD/MM/SCM Masterclasses, LinkedIn SAP Essentials, APICS CPIM/CSCP, NPTEL Logistics, SCMDOJO Practitioner Certificate'),
('Commerce', 'Supply Chain Management', 'Inventory Tools', '[\"NITIE (IIM Mumbai)\", \"IIM Udaipur\", \"IIFT Delhi\", \"SP Jain Mumbai\", \"Symbiosis Institute of Operations Management\", \"Amity University\", \"Chandigarh University\", \"Christ University\", \"NMIMS Mumbai\", \"Lovely Professional University\"]', 'Inventory & Warehouse Management, ERP & SCM Integration, Logistics & Transportation, Materials Management, Demand Planning & Forecasting, Purchasing & Procurement, Supply Chain Analytics, Inventory Auditing, Safety Stock & EOQ, Lean Inventory / JIT', '[\"Inventory Management Explained – David J. Piasecki\", \"Supply Chain Management – Sunil Chopra\", \"Materials Management – Prem Vrat\", \"The Everything Store – Brad Stone\", \"Logistics & Supply Chain Management – Martin Christopher\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Inventory Management & Logistics – Rutgers\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Inventory Management in SAP / Zoho / QuickBooks\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Operations & Supply Chain – IIMBx\"}, {\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"Inventory Fundamentals\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Inventory & SCM – IIT Madras\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Simplilearn – SCM & Inventory\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@simplilearn\"}, {\"title\":\"Edureka – Inventory Basics\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@edurekaIN\"}, {\"title\":\"Inventory Management School\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@InventoryManagementSchool\"}, {\"title\":\"Zarantech SAP MM\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@ZaranTechSAPTraining\"}, {\"title\":\"Tally Education India\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@tallyeducationindia\"}]', '[\"https://zoho.com/inventory\", \"https://inflowinventory.com\", \"https://tallysolutions.com\", \"https://inventoryops.com\", \"https://scmdojo.com\", \"https://sap.com\"]', 'Placements available in e-commerce, logistics, retail, and manufacturing companies like Amazon, Flipkart, Nestlé, Maersk, SAP Labs, Tata Steel, Blue Dart. Key roles include inventory analysis, ERP execution, and warehouse operations.', 'Inventory Analyst, Warehouse Manager, Procurement Executive, Materials Planner, Inventory Controller, SAP MM Consultant, Demand Planning Associate', 'Very high demand across e-commerce, FMCG, logistics, manufacturing, and retail sectors. Core to digital warehouse systems, supply planning, and ERP implementations.', '{\"entry\":\"₹3.5 – ₹6.5 LPA\", \"mid\":\"₹7 – ₹12 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹14 – ₹25 LPA\", \"consultant\":\"₹20 – ₹40+ LPA\"}', 'Zoho Inventory Internships, SAP MM Online Labs, Amazon Ops Internship, Flipkart Supply Chain Training, Delhivery & Blue Dart Logistics Programs, Tata Steel / HUL Graduate Trainee Programs, Internshala & LinkedIn roles', 'Inventory Intern → Analyst → Warehouse Supervisor → ERP Consultant / Inventory Manager → Supply Chain Director', 'SAP Certified Associate – MM/SCM, Zoho Inventory Certificate, Coursera – Inventory Planning, Udemy – SAP/Zoho Inventory, APICS CPIM, NPTEL – Warehouse Management, Lean Six Sigma – Inventory Optimization'),
('Commerce', 'Supply Chain Management', 'Logistics Software', '[\"NITIE (IIM Mumbai)\", \"IIM Udaipur\", \"IIFT Delhi\", \"SP Jain Mumbai\", \"SIOM Nashik\", \"NMIMS Mumbai\", \"Chandigarh University\", \"Christ University\", \"LPU\", \"Amity University\"]', 'Transportation & Logistics Management, Logistics Network Design, Freight Forwarding & Customs, ERP & TMS Systems, Procurement and Sourcing, Global Supply Chain Strategy, Digital Logistics, Last Mile Delivery, Import/Export Logistics, Logistics Data Analytics', '[\"Logistics Management & Strategy – Alan Harrison\", \"Supply Chain Logistics Management – Donald Bowersox\", \"Transportation: A Global Supply Chain Perspective – John Coyle\", \"The Everything Store – Brad Stone\", \"SAP TM Book: Transportation Management – Bernd Lauterbach\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Supply Chain Logistics – Rutgers\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Logistics Management – MITx\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\",\"course\":\"Oracle SCM / SAP TM / Freight Software\"}, {\"platform\":\"LinkedIn Learning\",\"course\":\"eCommerce Logistics & SCM\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Logistics & Supply Chain Optimization\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Simplilearn – SCM\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@simplilearn\"}, {\"title\":\"Edureka – Supply Chain\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@edurekaIN\"}, {\"title\":\"Logistics Basics\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@logisticsbasics\"}, {\"title\":\"FarEye Logistics\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@FarEyeChannel\"}, {\"title\":\"Locus Logistics\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@Locuslogistics\"}]', '[\"https://oracle.com/scm\", \"https://sap.com/products/scm/tm.html\", \"https://loginextsolutions.com\", \"https://freightpop.com\", \"https://cargo-wise.com\", \"https://shiprocket.in\", \"https://scmdojo.com\"]', 'Companies like Amazon, Flipkart, Maersk, SAP Labs, Delhivery, Blue Dart, DHL, Oracle, and Rivigo hire for logistics software roles. Key placement areas include TMS, SCM automation, and fleet management systems.', 'Logistics Software Analyst, Transportation Manager, ERP SCM Executive, Supply Chain Automation Consultant, Logistics Network Planner, TMS/WMS Consultant, Freight Operations Lead', 'High demand across logistics, e-commerce, manufacturing, and 3PL sectors. Logistics tech professionals are essential in digitization, automation, and last-mile delivery processes.', '{\"entry\":\"₹3.5 – ₹6.5 LPA\", \"mid\":\"₹7 – ₹12 LPA\", \"senior\":\"₹15 – ₹25+ LPA\", \"specialist\":\"₹30+ LPA\"}', 'Amazon Logistics Internship, SAP SCM Labs, Oracle SCM Trainee Program, Flipkart Delivery Tech Intern, Internshala Logistics Software Roles, FarEye & Shiprocket Summer Internships', 'Logistics Intern → SCM Analyst → TMS Consultant → Logistics Automation Engineer → ERP Logistics Manager → Head of Digital Logistics', 'SAP Certified – Transportation Management (TM), Oracle SCM Cloud Certification, Coursera – Logistics Specialization, Udemy – SAP TM & Oracle SCM, Lean Six Sigma Green Belt (Logistics), NPTEL – SCM Optimization, LSC Certified – India'),
('Medical', 'MBBS / BDS / Nursing', 'Patient Monitoring Systems', '[\"AIIMS Delhi\", \"Christian Medical College Vellore\", \"AFMC Pune\", \"JIPMER Puducherry\", \"Kasturba Medical College Manipal\", \"KGMU Lucknow\", \"MAMC Delhi\", \"SRM Institute of Medical Sciences\", \"Jamia Hamdard\", \"Amrita Institute of Medical Sciences\"]', 'Human Anatomy & Physiology, Pathology, Pharmacology, Microbiology, Medical Equipment Handling & Safety, Intensive Care Nursing, Bioinformatics, Biomedical Instrumentation, Patient Care Procedures, Digital Documentation (EHR/EMR)', '[\"Textbook of Medical Physiology – Guyton & Hall\", \"Fundamentals of Nursing – Potter & Perry\", \"Clinical Nursing Skills and Techniques – Taylor\", \"Introduction to Biomedical Equipment Technology – Carr & Brown\", \"Biomedical Instrumentation and Measurements – Leslie Cromwell\", \"ICU Equipment Manual – GE/Philips Guides\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"NPTEL\",\"course\":\"Biomedical Instrumentation\"}, {\"platform\":\"Coursera\",\"course\":\"Monitoring Patients in ICU – Yale University\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\",\"course\":\"Telemedicine and Monitoring\"}, {\"platform\":\"Medvarsity\",\"course\":\"Critical Care & ICU Equipment\"}, {\"platform\":\"Allied Health Academy\",\"course\":\"ICU Monitoring Certification\"}]', '[{\"title\":\"Medicosis Perfectionalis\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@medicosisperfectionalis\"}, {\"title\":\"Geeky Medics\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@geekymedics\"}, {\"title\":\"ICU Advantage\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@ICUAdvantage\"}, {\"title\":\"Nursing Exam Guide\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@nursingexamguide\"}, {\"title\":\"BMET Channel\",\"link\":\"https://www.youtube.com/@bmetchannel\"}]', '[\"https://nursingworld.org\", \"https://medvarsity.com\", \"https://gehealthcare.com\", \"https://philips.com/healthcare\", \"https://nptel.ac.in\", \"https://aiims.edu\"]', 'Top recruiters include Apollo Hospitals, AIIMS, Fortis, Max, Aster DM, and medical device companies like Philips, GE, Mindray. Common roles involve ICU patient monitoring, critical care nursing, and biomedical equipment operation.', 'ICU Nurse, ER Nurse, Medical Officer, Biomedical Technician, Clinical Equipment Operator, Patient Monitoring Device Trainer, Hospital IT Integration Officer', 'High demand in hospitals, ICUs, telemedicine setups, and healthcare tech companies. Growing importance after COVID-19 in both public and private healthcare sectors.', '{\"fresher_nurse\":\"₹2.5 – ₹4.5 LPA\", \"fresher_mbbs\":\"₹6 – ₹10 LPA\", \"experienced_nurse\":\"₹5 – ₹8 LPA\", \"biomedical_specialist\":\"₹8 – ₹12 LPA\", \"device_sales_trainer\":\"₹10 – ₹20+ LPA\"}', 'ICU Rotations during MBBS/Nursing, Biomedical internships with GE/Mindray/Philips, ICU & Emergency Certification via Medvarsity, Internshala Healthcare Device Training', 'Clinical Internship → ICU Nurse / House Surgeon → Biomedical Specialist → Equipment Trainer → ICU Supervisor / Consultant', 'Basic Life Support (BLS) & ACLS – AHA, ICU Nursing Certificate – Medvarsity, BMET Certification, Coursera – ICU Monitoring, NPTEL – Biomedical Instrumentation, GE/Philips Monitor Training, Healthcare EHR/EMR Certification'),
('Medical', 'MBBS / BDS / Nursing', 'EMR Software (Electronic Medical Records)', '[\"AIIMS Delhi\", \"CMC Vellore\", \"AFMC Pune\", \"Maulana Azad Medical College\", \"KMC Manipal\", \"KGMU Lucknow\", \"JIPMER Puducherry\", \"BHU Varanasi\", \"Sri Ramachandra Medical College\", \"St. John\'s Medical College Bangalore\"]', '[\"Human Anatomy & Physiology\", \"Biochemistry\", \"Pathology\", \"Pharmacology\", \"Microbiology\", \"Forensic Medicine\", \"Community Medicine\", \"Surgery\", \"Obstetrics and Gynaecology\", \"Medicine and Allied Sciences\"]', '[\"Gray’s Anatomy for Students\", \"Robbins & Cotran Pathologic Basis of Disease\", \"Lippincott Illustrated Reviews\", \"Shafer\'s Textbook of Oral Pathology\", \"Textbook of Dental Anatomy\", \"Fundamentals of Nursing\", \"Brunner and Suddarth’s Textbook of Medical-Surgical Nursing\"]', '[\"NPTEL – Clinical Research & Public Health\", \"Coursera – Anatomy Specialization\", \"edX – Essential Human Biology\", \"Medvarsity – EMR and Healthcare IT Courses\"]', '[\"Armando Hasudungan - https://www.youtube.com/user/armandohasudungan\", \"Dr. Najeeb Lectures - https://www.youtube.com/user/doctornajeeblectures\", \"Kenhub - https://www.youtube.com/user/kenhubcom\", \"Marrow - https://www.youtube.com/@MarrowIndia\", \"Osmosis - https://www.youtube.com/user/OsmosisMed\"]', '[\"https://www.mciindia.org\", \"https://www.nhp.gov.in\", \"https://www.medindia.net\", \"https://www.merilacademy.com\", \"https://emedicine.medscape.com\"]', 'Top institutes provide placement through internships, government schemes, hospital affiliations, and campus recruitment by corporate hospitals.', '[\"Resident Doctor\", \"Medical Officer\", \"Junior Doctor\", \"Dental Surgeon\", \"Hospital Consultant\", \"Staff Nurse\", \"ICU Nurse\", \"Home Care Nurse\", \"EMR Specialist\"]', 'High demand across public and private hospitals, clinical research, and healthcare IT sectors. Opportunities growing due to digital healthcare expansion.', 'Starting: ₹20,000–₹80,000/month; Mid-level: ₹50,000–₹1.2L; Experienced: ₹1.5L–₹3.5L+ depending on specialization and location.', 'Internships through CRRI, government hospitals, ICMR, WHO, private hospital observerships, and EMR training centers.', 'MBBS → MD/MS → DM/MCh → Specialist; BDS → MDS → Specialist Dentist; Nursing → MSc Nursing → Admin or Educator; EMR → Consultant → HealthTech Manager', '[\"EMR/EHR System Certification\", \"BLS/ACLS\", \"Clinical Data Management\", \"Hospital Management\", \"Health Informatics Certification\"]'),
('Medical', 'Pharmacy', 'Drug Dispensing Tools', '[\"NIPER Mohali\", \"Jamia Hamdard University\", \"Manipal College of Pharmaceutical Sciences\", \"Institute of Chemical Technology Mumbai\", \"Banasthali Vidyapith\", \"BITS Pilani\", \"JSS College of Pharmacy\", \"Poona College of Pharmacy\", \"DIPSAR\", \"Amrita School of Pharmacy\"]', '[\"Pharmaceutical Chemistry\", \"Pharmacology\", \"Pharmacognosy\", \"Pharmaceutics\", \"Clinical Pharmacy\", \"Hospital and Community Pharmacy\", \"Biopharmaceutics\", \"Pharmaceutical Analysis\", \"Pharmaceutical Jurisprudence\", \"Drug Regulatory Affairs\"]', '[\"Remington: The Science and Practice of Pharmacy\", \"Lippincott’s Illustrated Reviews: Pharmacology\", \"Aulton’s Pharmaceutics\", \"Essentials of Medical Pharmacology – K.D. Tripathi\", \"Textbook of Pharmaceutical Chemistry – Jayashree Ghosh\"]', '[\"SWAYAM – Pharmaceutical and Drug Discovery\", \"Coursera – Drug Commercialization and Development\", \"Medvarsity – Clinical Pharmacology and Pharmacovigilance\", \"edX – Prescription Drug Regulation, Cost & Access\"]', '[\"Pharma Knowledge Academy - https://www.youtube.com/@PharmaKnowledgeAcademy\", \"Pharma Tutorials - https://www.youtube.com/@pharmatutorials\", \"GPAT Academy - https://www.youtube.com/@GPATAcademy\", \"Pharmacology Mnemonics - https://www.youtube.com/@pharmacologymnemonics\", \"GPAT Discussion Center - https://www.youtube.com/@GPATDiscussionCenter\"]', '[\"https://pharmacopoeia.gov.in\", \"https://pharmatutor.org\", \"https://fda.gov\", \"https://cdsco.gov.in\", \"https://medlineplus.gov\"]', 'Top colleges provide training and campus placements with pharma companies like Cipla, Sun Pharma, Dr. Reddy’s; GPAT-qualified students get scholarships; strong internship programs in hospitals and industries.', '[\"Clinical Pharmacist\", \"Drug Safety Associate\", \"Medical Writer\", \"Production Executive\", \"QA/QC Analyst\", \"Regulatory Affairs Associate\"]', 'Growing demand in India and abroad for licensed pharmacists, regulatory affairs, pharma R&D, and hospital-based roles.', 'Starting: ₹18,000–₹40,000/month; Mid-level: ₹50,000–₹80,000; Experienced: ₹1L–₹1.5L+ depending on role and industry.', 'Internships at Cipla, Sun Pharma, Lupin, Apollo Hospital; training through pharma labs, retail chains, hospital pharmacies; industry visits in 3rd/4th year.', 'D.Pharm → B.Pharm → M.Pharm/Pharm.D → Regulatory or R&D Roles; or Hospital Pharmacist → Clinical Specialist → Head Pharmacist → Educator', '[\"Pharmacovigilance Training\", \"Clinical Research Certification\", \"GMP Certification\", \"Regulatory Affairs Certification\", \"Drug Safety & Compliance Training\"]'),
('Medical', 'Pharmacy', 'Pharma Software', '[\"NIPER Mohali\", \"Jamia Hamdard\", \"BITS Pilani – Pharmacy Division\", \"Manipal College of Pharmaceutical Sciences\", \"Institute of Chemical Technology Mumbai\", \"JSS College of Pharmacy\", \"Poona College of Pharmacy\", \"DIPSAR\", \"Banasthali Vidyapith\", \"Amrita School of Pharmacy\"]', '[\"Pharmaceutical Chemistry\", \"Pharmacology\", \"Pharmaceutics\", \"Pharmacognosy\", \"Biopharmaceutics & Pharmacokinetics\", \"Hospital & Clinical Pharmacy\", \"Computer Applications in Pharmacy\", \"Pharmaceutical Management\", \"Pharmaceutical Regulatory Affairs\"]', '[\"Remington: The Science and Practice of Pharmacy\", \"Lippincott\'s Illustrated Reviews: Pharmacology\", \"Pharmaceutical Management – Jogdand\", \"Essentials of Medical Pharmacology – K.D. Tripathi\", \"Computer Applications in Pharmacy – R. M. Mehta\"]', '[\"SWAYAM – Pharmaceutical Formulations & Drug Design\", \"Coursera – Introduction to Pharmacy Informatics\", \"Medvarsity – Healthcare Software Training, GMP Compliance\", \"edX – Data Science in Healthcare\"]', '[\"Pharma Knowledge Academy - https://www.youtube.com/@PharmaKnowledgeAcademy\", \"GPAT Discussion Center - https://www.youtube.com/@GPATDiscussionCenter\", \"Pharma Tutorials - https://www.youtube.com/@pharmatutorials\", \"Dr. Najeeb Lectures - https://www.youtube.com/user/doctornajeeblectures\", \"Pharma Pathshala - https://www.youtube.com/@pharmapathshala\"]', '[\"https://pharmatutor.org\", \"https://cdsco.gov.in\", \"https://pharmacopoeia.gov.in\", \"https://medlineplus.gov\", \"https://fda.gov\"]', 'Top pharmacy colleges have placement tie-ups with pharma companies like Cipla, Sun Pharma, Dr. Reddy\'s, and also roles in Health IT firms for pharma software specialists and data analysts.', '[\"Pharma Software Specialist\", \"Inventory Pharmacist\", \"Healthcare Analyst\", \"QA Executive\", \"Pharmacy Automation Consultant\", \"Clinical Data Coordinator\"]', 'Demand is growing in hospital systems, pharmacy chains, pharmaceutical companies, and government sectors due to digitization in pharma and healthcare.', 'Starting: ₹18,000–₹30,000/month; Mid-level: ₹50,000–₹80,000; Experienced: ₹90,000–₹1.5L depending on specialization and industry.', 'Internships in Cipla, Sun Pharma, and Apollo for software tools and QA/QC; Training in Health IT companies; Online pharma ERP training through platforms like Medvarsity or Udemy.', 'D.Pharm/B.Pharm → QA/QC Executive → Software Implementation Officer → Regulatory Analyst → Pharma Software Systems Manager OR Pharmacy Graduate → Clinical Software Specialist → EMR Analyst → Health Informatics Consultant', '[\"GMP & GLP Certification\", \"Pharmacovigilance Certification\", \"Pharma ERP/Inventory Software Training\", \"Healthcare Analytics\", \"Regulatory Affairs Certification\"]'),
('Medical', 'Physiotherapy', 'Therapy Equipment', '[\"Manipal College of Health Professions\", \"SRM Institute of Science and Technology\", \"Christian Medical College Vellore\", \"Jamia Hamdard University\", \"NIMS University Jaipur\", \"Dr. D.Y. Patil College of Physiotherapy Pune\", \"MUHS Nashik\", \"Amity Institute of Physiotherapy\", \"K.J. Somaiya College of Physiotherapy\", \"Seth GSMC & KEM Hospital Mumbai\"]', '[\"Anatomy & Physiology\", \"Biomechanics & Kinesiology\", \"Electrotherapy\", \"Exercise Therapy\", \"Physiotherapy in Orthopedics, Neurology, Cardiology\", \"Rehabilitation Sciences\", \"Research Methodology\", \"Pathology & Pharmacology\"]', '[\"Principles and Practice of Therapeutic Massage – Joseph W. Schmid\", \"Textbook of Electrotherapy – Jagmohan Singh\", \"Therapeutic Exercise – Carolyn Kisner\", \"Essentials of Physiotherapy – Jayant Joshi\", \"Orthopedic Physical Assessment – David J. Magee\"]', '[\"SWAYAM – Physical Therapy & Rehabilitation\", \"Coursera – Managing Chronic Pain and Recovery\", \"edX – Exercise Prescription for Disease\", \"Udemy – Electrotherapy and Manual Therapy Courses\"]', '[\"Physiotutors - https://www.youtube.com/@Physiotutors\", \"Clinical Physio - https://www.youtube.com/@ClinicalPhysio\", \"Physiotherapy with Vishal - https://www.youtube.com/@physiotherapywithvishal\", \"Healthcare Evolution - https://www.youtube.com/@HealthcareEvolution\", \"Movement Solution - https://www.youtube.com/@MovementSolution\"]', '[\"https://www.physiopedia.com\", \"https://www.indianjpain.org\", \"https://www.wcpt.org\", \"https://www.nhp.gov.in\", \"https://rehabpub.com\"]', 'Top colleges provide placement in hospitals, rehab centers, sports clinics, and home health setups. Institutes like Manipal, SRM, and CMC offer strong internship and hospital tie-up programs.', '[\"Clinical Physiotherapist\", \"Rehab Specialist\", \"Sports Physio\", \"Pediatric/Neuro PT\", \"Ergonomics Consultant\", \"Fitness/Rehab Coach\"]', 'High and growing demand in hospitals, sports, home care, and telehealth sectors across urban and semi-urban regions.', 'Starting: ₹20,000–₹35,000/month; Mid-level: ₹50,000–₹80,000; Experienced: ₹1L–₹2L+ depending on specialization and sector.', 'Mandatory 6–12 months of internship in final year; practical training at Apollo, Fortis, CMC, Manipal Hospital, sports rehab centers, and workshops in electrotherapy & movement-based rehab.', 'BPT → MPT (Specialization) → Senior Physio → Rehab Head/Sports Physio Lead OR BPT → Homecare Startup/Clinic Owner → Clinical Trainer/Educator', '[\"Dry Needling Certification\", \"Manual Therapy Certification\", \"Taping and Bracing Techniques\", \"IASTM & Cupping Therapy\", \"Sports Physiotherapy Certification\"]'),
('Medical', 'Physiotherapy', 'Rehabilitation Tools', '[\"Manipal College of Health Professions\", \"SRM Institute of Science and Technology\", \"Christian Medical College Vellore\", \"Jamia Hamdard\", \"Dr. D.Y. Patil College of Physiotherapy\", \"Amity Institute of Physiotherapy\", \"Seth GSMC & KEM Hospital\", \"RGUHS Karnataka\", \"NIMS University\", \"K.J. Somaiya College of Physiotherapy\"]', '[\"Biomechanics & Kinesiology\", \"Rehabilitation Techniques\", \"Assistive Device Training\", \"Electrotherapy\", \"Orthopedics and Neurological Physiotherapy\", \"Occupational Therapy & ADL Training\", \"Motor Control & Motor Learning\", \"Prosthetics & Orthotics\"]', '[\"Physical Rehabilitation – Susan B. O\'Sullivan & Thomas J. Schmitz\", \"Orthotics and Prosthetics in Rehabilitation – Michelle M. Lusardi\", \"Therapeutic Exercise – Carolyn Kisner\", \"Rehabilitation Techniques for Sports Medicine – Prentice\", \"Neurological Rehabilitation – Darcy Ann Umphred\"]', '[\"SWAYAM – Rehabilitation Therapy Programs\", \"Coursera – Introduction to Neurorehabilitation\", \"edX – Physical Activity & Health\", \"Udemy – Neuroplasticity & Stroke Rehab Tools\"]', '[\"Physiotutors - https://www.youtube.com/@Physiotutors\", \"Rehab Science - https://www.youtube.com/@RehabScience\", \"Clinical Physio - https://www.youtube.com/@ClinicalPhysio\", \"Bob & Brad - https://www.youtube.com/@BobandBrad\", \"Physiotherapy with Vishal - https://www.youtube.com/@physiotherapywithvishal\"]', '[\"https://www.physiopedia.com\", \"https://rehabpub.com\", \"https://www.wcpt.org\", \"https://www.nhp.gov.in\", \"https://www.abledata.acl.gov\"]', 'Colleges like Manipal, SRM, and CMC offer clinical exposure via attached rehab centers. Placement offered in hospitals, neuro-rehab units, disability centers, and assistive tech companies.', '[\"Rehab Physiotherapist\", \"Neuro/Ortho/Pediatric Therapist\", \"Assistive Tech Consultant\", \"Rehab Center Coordinator\", \"Disability Support Worker\"]', 'High demand in rehabilitation hospitals, assistive tech R&D, special education and therapy centers, and NGOs serving people with disabilities.', 'Starting: ₹20,000–₹35,000/month; Mid-level: ₹50,000–₹80,000; Experienced: ₹1L–₹2L depending on specialization, certifications, and role.', 'Internships in pediatric, neuro, and geriatric rehab centers; Training on robotic tools, smart wheelchairs, assistive ADL tech in institutes like NIMHANS, Mobility India, and AIIMS.', 'BPT → MPT in Rehab/Neuro → Specialist → Rehab Center Director OR BPT → Assistive Tech Specialist → R&D / HealthTech Consultant', '[\"Gait & Balance Certification\", \"Neuro Rehab Robotics\", \"Assistive Technology Specialist (ATS)\", \"Dry Needling & Manual Therapy\", \"Rehabilitation Counseling\"]'),
('Medical', 'Public Health', 'Data Analysis (Epi Info)', '[\"AIIMS New Delhi\", \"TISS Mumbai\", \"PGIMER Chandigarh\", \"Indian Institute of Public Health (IIPH)\", \"JIPMER Puducherry\", \"PHFI\", \"Manipal School of Public Health\", \"IIHMR Jaipur\", \"Amity Institute of Public Health\", \"KLE University Belgaum\"]', '[\"Epidemiology\", \"Biostatistics\", \"Public Health Informatics\", \"Health Systems & Policy\", \"Environmental & Occupational Health\", \"Health Economics\", \"Research Methodology\", \"Program Monitoring & Evaluation\", \"Communicable & Non-Communicable Diseases\"]', '[\"Epidemiology – Leon Gordis\", \"Essentials of Biostatistics – Lisa M. Sullivan\", \"Introduction to Public Health – Mary-Jane Schneider\", \"Principles of Epidemiology – CDC Manual\", \"Applied Epidemiology – Ross C. Brownson\"]', '[\"Coursera – Epidemiology: The Basic Science of Public Health\", \"SWAYAM – Public Health & Health Promotion\", \"edX – Data Analysis for Life Sciences\", \"WHO Health Academy – Outbreak Surveillance\", \"CDC Epi Info Training\"]', '[\"CDC - https://www.youtube.com/user/CDCStreamingHealth\", \"OpenWHO - https://www.youtube.com/@openWHO\", \"Dr. Hess - https://www.youtube.com/@drhess\", \"Epidemiology Made Easy - https://www.youtube.com/@epidemiologymadeeasy\", \"MedCram - https://www.youtube.com/@medcram\"]', '[\"https://www.cdc.gov/epiinfo\", \"https://openwho.org\", \"https://www.phfi.org\", \"https://www.who.int\", \"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc\"]', 'Institutes like AIIMS, PHFI, and IIPH have placement tie-ups with WHO, UNICEF, state health missions, and NGOs. Field training and fellowships often included with MPH programs.', '[\"Epidemiologist\", \"Public Health Analyst\", \"Health Data Officer\", \"Surveillance Coordinator\", \"Health Program Evaluator\", \"Field Investigator\"]', 'Strong and growing demand in disease surveillance, outbreak analysis, national health programs, and international development organizations.', 'Starting: ₹25,000–₹40,000/month; Mid-level: ₹60,000–₹1.2L; Experienced: ₹1.5L–₹2L+ based on project and org (WHO/UN/Research).', 'Internships with ICMR, WHO India, and public health research institutes; real-world data collection, survey work, and Epi Info-based analysis in field projects and NHM programs.', 'BPH/MPH → Analyst → Surveillance Officer → Program Manager → Regional/Global Health Lead OR MPH → Researcher → Epidemiologist → Policy Advisor → Health Director', '[\"Epi Info Training (CDC)\", \"SPSS/R/STATA Data Analysis\", \"Monitoring & Evaluation Certificate\", \"WHO OpenWHO Global Health Courses\", \"PM4PH – Project Management for Public Health\"]'),
('Medical', 'Public Health', 'SPSS (Statistical Package for the Social Sciences)', '[\"AIIMS New Delhi\", \"TISS Mumbai\", \"Indian Institute of Public Health (IIPH)\", \"PGIMER Chandigarh\", \"Manipal School of Public Health\", \"JIPMER Puducherry\", \"IIHMR University Jaipur\", \"PHFI\", \"Amity Institute of Public Health\", \"KLE University Belgaum\"]', '[\"Biostatistics\", \"Epidemiology\", \"Health Informatics\", \"Public Health Research Methods\", \"Health Survey Design & Analysis\", \"Data Management in Health Systems\", \"Monitoring & Evaluation\", \"Environmental and Occupational Health\"]', '[\"Biostatistics – Wayne W. Daniel\", \"Essentials of Biostatistics – Lisa Sullivan\", \"Public Health Research Methods – Greg Guest\", \"SPSS Survival Manual – Julie Pallant\", \"Applied Multivariate Statistics – James Stevens\"]', '[\"Coursera – Data Analysis in Public Health\", \"SWAYAM – Biostatistics and Epidemiology\", \"edX – Statistical Thinking for Public Health\", \"Udemy – SPSS for Beginners & Advanced\", \"WHO – Health Data Analysis\"]', '[\"Statistics Learning Centre - https://www.youtube.com/@statisticslearningcentre\", \"Dr. Yusuf SPSS - https://www.youtube.com/@drmuhammadyusuf\", \"Johns Hopkins SPH - https://www.youtube.com/@JohnsHopkinsSPH\", \"OpenWHO - https://www.youtube.com/@openWHO\", \"MedCram - https://www.youtube.com/@medcram\"]', '[\"https://www.ibm.com/products/spss-statistics\", \"https://openwho.org\", \"https://www.phfi.org\", \"https://www.cdc.gov\", \"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc\"]', 'Top institutions provide internships and job placements in NHM, UNICEF, WHO, ICMR, and academic health research projects. Practical training in SPSS and health data management is often integrated into coursework.', '[\"Health Data Analyst\", \"Public Health Researcher\", \"Epidemiologist\", \"Biostatistician\", \"Program Monitoring Officer\"]', 'SPSS skills are in strong demand in data-centric public health roles, particularly in monitoring, research, policy evaluation, and impact analysis across global health sectors.', 'Starting: ₹30,000–₹45,000/month; Mid-level: ₹70,000–₹1.5L; Experienced: ₹1.8L–₹2L+ in international or national health programs.', 'Internships available at PHFI, ICMR, IIHMR, WHO India, and State Health Departments. Involves data entry, SPSS analysis, survey analytics, and M&E dashboard reporting.', 'BPH/MPH → Data Analyst → Program Manager → Biostatistics/Surveillance Lead OR MPH → Research Officer → Technical Expert → Public Health Director', '[\"IBM SPSS Certification\", \"Monitoring & Evaluation for Public Health\", \"Epidemiology Certification – WHO/Johns Hopkins\", \"Biostatistics & R for Public Health\", \"Advanced Data Analytics in Healthcare\"]'),
('Medical', 'Lab Technology', 'Microscopy', '[\"AIIMS New Delhi\", \"PGIMER Chandigarh\", \"JIPMER Puducherry\", \"Manipal College of Health Professions\", \"CMC Vellore\", \"Amrita Vishwa Vidyapeetham\", \"SRM IST\", \"St. John’s Medical College\", \"Jamia Hamdard\", \"Kasturba Medical College Manipal\"]', '[\"Medical Microbiology\", \"Histopathology\", \"Cytology & Hematology\", \"Clinical Biochemistry\", \"Instrumentation in Lab Technology\", \"Parasitology & Mycology\", \"Quality Assurance & Laboratory Management\", \"Molecular Biology Techniques\"]', '[\"Medical Laboratory Technology – Ramnik Sood\", \"Microscopy and Microtechnique – R.G. Carter\", \"Textbook of Medical Laboratory Technology – Praful Godkar\", \"Clinical Microbiology Made Ridiculously Simple – Mark Gladwin\", \"Basic Histology – Junqueira\"]', '[\"Coursera – Fundamentals of Immunology and Microscopy\", \"edX – Cell Biology & Microscopy\", \"SWAYAM – Medical Laboratory Techniques\", \"Udemy – Basics of Microscopy & Histotechniques\", \"WHO – Lab Quality Management System\"]', '[\"Armando Hasudungan - https://www.youtube.com/@armandohasudungan\", \"Osmosis - https://www.youtube.com/@osmosis\", \"MicroscopyU - https://www.youtube.com/@MicroscopyU\", \"The Histology Guide - https://www.youtube.com/@thehistologyguide\", \"Lab Technician Classes - https://www.youtube.com/@labtechnicianclasses\"]', '[\"https://www.labtestsonline.org\", \"https://www.microscopyu.com\", \"https://openwho.org\", \"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc\", \"https://www.scribd.com/document/483395657/MLT-Notes\"]', 'Placement in hospital labs, research institutions, and private diagnostic labs. Top colleges like AIIMS, Manipal, and CMC Vellore offer direct placement or referrals to reputed labs and R&D centers.', '[\"Lab Technician\", \"Histology Assistant\", \"Path Lab Analyst\", \"Cytotechnologist\", \"Research Lab Assistant\", \"QA/QC Technician\"]', 'High demand in hospitals, diagnostics, pathology labs, pharmaceutical research centers, and clinical trial organizations.', 'Starting: ₹18,000–₹28,000/month; Mid-level: ₹40,000–₹70,000/month; Senior: ₹80,000–₹1.5L/month in R&D or management roles.', 'Internship in hospital/diagnostic labs during final year; training in microscopy, staining, imaging; opportunities in ICMR, NABL labs, private centers like SRL, Thyrocare, and Lal PathLabs.', 'DMLT/BSc MLT → Lab Technician → Senior Technologist → Lab Supervisor → Lab Manager → R&D Specialist / Clinical Research Lead', '[\"Diploma in Medical Laboratory Technology (DMLT)\", \"Certificate in Microscopy Techniques\", \"WHO Quality Lab Practices\", \"Histopathology Lab Certification\", \"NABL & ISO 15189 Lab Standards\"]'),
('Medical', 'Lab Technology', 'Blood Analysis Tools', '[\"AIIMS New Delhi\", \"PGIMER Chandigarh\", \"CMC Vellore\", \"JIPMER Puducherry\", \"Manipal College of Health Professions\", \"Amrita Institute of Medical Sciences\", \"St. John’s Medical College Bengaluru\", \"SRM IST\", \"Kasturba Medical College Manipal\", \"Jamia Hamdard New Delhi\"]', '[\"Hematology\", \"Clinical Biochemistry\", \"Immunohematology & Blood Banking\", \"Pathophysiology\", \"Instrumentation in Lab Technology\", \"Phlebotomy Techniques\", \"Serology and Coagulation Studies\", \"Quality Control & Lab Ethics\"]', '[\"Textbook of Medical Laboratory Technology – Praful Godkar\", \"Medical Laboratory Technology – Ramnik Sood\", \"Hematology: Clinical Principles and Applications – Rodak\", \"Basic Medical Laboratory Techniques – Barbara Estridge\", \"Clinical Hematology Atlas – Bernadette Rodak\"]', '[\"Coursera – Clinical Hematology: University of Minnesota\", \"edX – Essential Human Biology: Blood and Blood Analysis\", \"Udemy – Blood Tests & Diagnostics Simplified\", \"SWAYAM – Medical Lab Assistant Course\", \"WHO – Laboratory Quality Management Systems\"]', '[\"Lab Technician Classes - https://www.youtube.com/@labtechnicianclasses\", \"Armando Hasudungan - https://www.youtube.com/@armandohasudungan\", \"Osmosis - https://www.youtube.com/@osmosis\", \"Blood Bank Guy - https://www.youtube.com/@BloodBankGuy\", \"AIIMS Lab Tutorials - https://www.youtube.com/@AIIMSLab\"]', '[\"https://labtestsonline.org\", \"https://openwho.org\", \"https://microscopyu.com\", \"https://ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc\", \"https://who.int/health-topics/blood-products\"]', 'Top institutes provide clinical lab and blood bank internships; placements through diagnostic labs like SRL, Dr. Lal PathLabs, Apollo, Thyrocare; Govt hospitals through NHM recruitment.', '[\"Hematology Lab Technician\", \"Blood Bank Technologist\", \"Clinical Lab Scientist\", \"Phlebotomist\", \"Diagnostic Technician\"]', 'Consistently high demand in pathology labs, blood banks, and diagnostic centers across India, especially in Tier-1 & 2 cities. Certification in blood banking adds significant value.', 'Starting: ₹18,000–₹28,000/month; Mid-level: ₹45,000–₹70,000/month; Senior roles: ₹80,000–₹1.5L/month in research or hospital management settings.', 'Internships in hospital blood banks and diagnostic labs; includes hands-on experience with automated analyzers, phlebotomy, cross-matching, blood typing, and transfusion protocols.', 'DMLT/BSc MLT → Lab Technician → Blood Bank Technologist → Senior Technologist → Lab Supervisor → Diagnostic/R&D Specialist', '[\"Certificate in Hematology and Blood Banking\", \"DMLT/BSc MLT\", \"WHO Lab Quality Certification\", \"Phlebotomy Technician (CPT)\", \"NABL/ISO 15189 Standards Training\"]'),
('Medical', 'Radiology', 'MRI/CT Imaging Software', '[\"AIIMS New Delhi\", \"PGIMER Chandigarh\", \"JIPMER Puducherry\", \"CMC Vellore\", \"Amrita Institute of Medical Sciences\", \"Seth GS Medical College Mumbai\", \"Kasturba Medical College Manipal\", \"St. John’s Medical College Bengaluru\", \"KGMU Lucknow\", \"SRM Institute of Science & Technology\"]', '[\"Radiological Physics\", \"Anatomy & Physiology\", \"MRI Techniques\", \"CT Imaging\", \"Image Processing & Interpretation\", \"Radiation Protection\", \"Contrast Media Techniques\", \"Equipment Maintenance & QA\", \"Medical Ethics\"]', '[\"Textbook of Radiology and Imaging – David Sutton\", \"Fundamentals of Radiology – Lucy Frank Squire\", \"Computed Tomography – Euclid Seeram\", \"MRI Made Easy – Govind Chavhan\", \"Essentials of Radiologic Science – Robert Fosbinder\"]', '[\"Coursera – Fundamentals of MRI (University of Queensland)\", \"edX – Medical Imaging (MIT/Harvard)\", \"Udemy – CT/MRI Scan Interpretation\", \"WHO – Radiation Safety Training\", \"Radiopaedia – Radiology Courses\"]', '[\"Radiology Masterclass - https://www.youtube.com/@radiologymasterclass\", \"Dr. Najeeb Lectures - https://www.youtube.com/@DoctorNajeeb\", \"Radiopaedia - https://www.youtube.com/@Radiopaedia\", \"CTisus - https://www.youtube.com/@CTisus\", \"MRI Online - https://www.youtube.com/@mrionline\"]', '[\"https://www.radiopaedia.org\", \"https://www.ctisus.com\", \"https://openwho.org\", \"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\", \"https://www.myesr.org\"]', 'Top institutes provide internships and job placements in hospitals and diagnostic centers. Companies like Siemens, GE Healthcare, and Philips recruit trained imaging professionals.', '[\"MRI Technologist\", \"CT Scan Operator\", \"Radiographer\", \"Diagnostic Imaging Specialist\", \"PACS/RIS Operator\", \"Application Specialist (OEM)\"]', 'Growing demand for diagnostic professionals in hospitals, teleradiology firms, and medical equipment companies. High demand in urban and semi-urban centers.', 'Starting: ₹25,000–₹40,000/month; Mid-level: ₹60,000–₹1L/month; Senior: ₹1L–₹1.5L/month; OEM/International: ₹1.2L–₹2L/month.', 'Internships with hospitals and imaging labs for hands-on training in MRI/CT image acquisition, software interface, DICOM export, calibration. Companies like GE and Philips also offer short internships or field exposure.', 'Diploma/BSc in Radiology → MRI/CT Technician → Senior Technologist → Imaging Department Head OR Application Specialist → Clinical Applications Manager → Imaging Consultant', '[\"CT/MRI Technician Certification\", \"Radiation Safety Officer (BARC)\", \"PACS & DICOM Training\", \"International MRI/CT Certification (ARRT/ESR)\", \"Advanced Imaging Fellowship (AIIMS/ESR)\"]'),
('Medical', 'Radiology', 'PACS (Picture Archiving and Communication System)', '[\"AIIMS New Delhi\", \"PGIMER Chandigarh\", \"CMC Vellore\", \"JIPMER Puducherry\", \"Kasturba Medical College Manipal\", \"Amrita Institute of Medical Sciences\", \"SRM Institute of Science & Technology\", \"St. John’s Medical College Bengaluru\", \"KGMU Lucknow\", \"Apollo Radiology International\"]', '[\"Radiological Physics\", \"Imaging Modalities\", \"PACS & DICOM Standards\", \"Radiology Workflow\", \"Medical Informatics\", \"Networking & Server Configuration\", \"RIS/HIS Concepts\", \"Data Security & Storage\"]', '[\"PACS and Imaging Informatics – H. K. Huang\", \"Introduction to PACS Systems – Katherine Andriole\", \"Digital Radiography and PACS – Christi Carter\", \"Essentials of Radiologic Science – Robert Fosbinder\", \"DICOM Structured Reporting – David Clunie\"]', '[\"Coursera – Imaging Informatics & PACS Fundamentals\", \"edX – Health Informatics & Medical IT\", \"Udemy – PACS Administrator Training\", \"Radiopaedia – PACS Tutorials\", \"WHO – Health Data Management\"]', '[\"Radiopaedia - https://www.youtube.com/@Radiopaedia\", \"HIMSS Learning - https://www.youtube.com/@HIMSS\", \"Doctor Najeeb - https://www.youtube.com/@DoctorNajeeb\", \"CTisus - https://www.youtube.com/@CTisus\", \"Radiology Nation - https://www.youtube.com/@radiologynation\"]', '[\"https://radiopaedia.org\", \"https://dicomlibrary.com\", \"https://openwho.org\", \"https://myesr.org\", \"https://pacsadmin.org\"]', 'Leading colleges provide PACS exposure during training; placement opportunities exist with hospitals, diagnostic labs, and healthcare IT vendors such as GE, Philips, and Telerad Tech.', '[\"PACS Administrator\", \"Imaging Informatics Specialist\", \"Radiology IT Coordinator\", \"Application Support Executive\", \"Tele-radiology Support Specialist\"]', 'Increasing demand in hospitals, teleradiology services, and healthcare IT for managing radiology image data securely and efficiently.', 'Starting: ₹30,000–₹45,000/month; Mid-level: ₹70,000–₹1.2L/month; Senior roles: ₹1L–₹2L/month in large hospitals or with international imaging firms.', 'Internships in radiology departments with hands-on PACS systems like GE Centricity and Philips IntelliSpace; experience in DICOM networking, RIS integration, and image workflow.', 'Diploma/BSc Radiology → PACS Technician → PACS Administrator → Imaging Informatics Manager → Healthcare IT Lead', '[\"Certified PACS Associate (CPAS)\", \"Health Informatics Certification (HIMSS/NIIT)\", \"PACS Administrator (Udemy/Telerad Tech)\", \"DICOM Masterclass (Radiopaedia)\", \"RSNA Imaging Informatics Training\"]'),
('Medical', 'Ayurveda / Homeopathy', 'Herbal Extraction Tools', '[\"Banaras Hindu University (BHU), Varanasi\", \"National Institute of Ayurveda, Jaipur\", \"Gujarat Ayurved University, Jamnagar\", \"Dr. D.Y. Patil College of Ayurved, Pune\", \"Tilak Ayurved Mahavidyalaya, Pune\", \"National Institute of Homeopathy, Kolkata\", \"Govt Homoeopathic Medical College, Bangalore\", \"SKH Medical College, Kerala\", \"State Ayurvedic College and Hospital, Lucknow\", \"Bastyr University (International)\"]', '[\"Ayurvedic Pharmacognosy\", \"Dravyaguna Vigyan\", \"Herbal Pharmaceutics\", \"Materia Medica\", \"Phytochemistry\", \"Pharmacological Techniques\", \"Standardization of Herbal Drugs\", \"Ayurvedic Formulations\"]', '[\"Ayurvedic Pharmacopoeia of India\", \"Textbook of Dravyaguna Vigyan – Dr. Gyanendra Pandey\", \"Pharmacognosy – Kokate & Trease\", \"Materia Medica – William Boericke\", \"Herbal Drug Technology – A.K. Gupta\", \"Fundamentals of Pharmacognosy – Heinrich, Barnes\"]', '[\"SWAYAM – Ayurveda Fundamentals\", \"Coursera – Medicinal Plants by University of Minnesota\", \"Udemy – Herbal Extraction & Plant-Based Medicine\", \"AYUSH e-learning Portal\", \"CCRAS Herbal Skill Courses\"]', '[\"Ministry of AYUSH – https://www.youtube.com/@moayush\", \"BHU Ayurveda – https://www.youtube.com/@BHU-Ayurveda\", \"Dr. Pooja’s Ayurveda – https://www.youtube.com/@DrPoojaAyurveda\", \"HomeoAyurvedam – https://www.youtube.com/@HomeoAyurvedam\", \"Easy Ayurveda – https://www.youtube.com/@EasyAyurveda\"]', '[\"https://ayush.gov.in\", \"https://nmpb.nic.in\", \"https://ccras.nic.in\", \"https://easyayurveda.com\", \"https://dravyagun.com\"]', 'Colleges offer placements through industry tie-ups with companies like Dabur, Patanjali, Himalaya, Baidyanath. PSC/AYUSH-based recruitment also available in public sectors.', '[\"Herbal Extraction Technician\", \"Ayurvedic Product Developer\", \"Homeopathic Compounder\", \"Pharmacognosy Assistant\", \"Quality Analyst (Herbal)\", \"R&D Associate (Herbal Medicines)\"]', 'High demand in herbal and natural medicine industries, growing wellness and nutraceutical sectors, export-oriented units, and government AYUSH initiatives.', 'Starting: ₹15,000–₹25,000/month; Mid-level: ₹35,000–₹50,000/month; Senior R&D/Pharma roles: ₹60,000–₹1.5L/month.', 'Internships at Dabur, Patanjali, Himalaya, CCRAS labs, and field projects with NMPB; hands-on experience in Soxhlet, cold press, and herbal oil extraction.', 'Diploma/BAMS/BHMS → Junior Technician → Product Developer → R&D/Pharma QA → Ayurveda Pharmacist or Herbal Industry Consultant', '[\"AYUSH Herbal Processing Certification\", \"GMP/GLP for Herbal Industry\", \"Cert. in Medicinal Plant Cultivation\", \"Diploma in Clinical Research with Ayurveda\", \"Postgraduate Diploma in Herbal Formulation\"]');
INSERT INTO `career_recommendation` (`field`, `domain`, `technical_skill`, `best_colleges`, `core_subjects`, `recommended_books`, `online_courses`, `youtube_channels`, `websites`, `placement_info`, `job_roles`, `job_status`, `salary_info`, `training_internship`, `career_path`, `certifications`) VALUES
('Medical', 'Ayurveda / Homeopathy', 'Case Recording', '[\"Banaras Hindu University (BHU), Varanasi\", \"National Institute of Ayurveda, Jaipur\", \"Gujarat Ayurved University, Jamnagar\", \"National Institute of Homeopathy, Kolkata\", \"Dr. D.Y. Patil Ayurved College, Pune\", \"Government Homeopathic Medical College, Bangalore\", \"Tilak Ayurved Mahavidyalaya, Pune\", \"SKH Medical College, Kerala\", \"State Ayurvedic College & Hospital, Lucknow\", \"JB Roy State Ayurvedic Medical College, Kolkata\"]', '[\"Ayurvedic Pathology\", \"Clinical Case Taking\", \"Homeopathic Methodology\", \"Nidan Panchak\", \"Miasmatic Classification\", \"Medical Ethics\", \"Patient Assessment\"]', '[\"Rog Nidana Evam Vikriti Vigyan – Dr. C. R. Karnick\", \"Principles of Ayurvedic Diagnosis – Vasant Lad\", \"Case Taking & Repertory – Dr. S.R. Phatak\", \"Homeopathic Clinical Repertory – Robin Murphy\", \"Organon of Medicine – Samuel Hahnemann\", \"Textbook of Homeopathic Case Taking – P. Sankaran\"]', '[\"SWAYAM – Ayurvedic Diagnostics\", \"NIOS – Homeopathy Clinical Courses\", \"Udemy – Clinical Documentation\", \"Ayurveda Gurukulam – Case Analysis\", \"CCRAS eCourses\"]', '[\"Easy Ayurveda – https://www.youtube.com/@EasyAyurveda\", \"Dr. Pooja’s Ayurveda – https://www.youtube.com/@DrPoojaAyurveda\", \"BHU Ayurveda – https://www.youtube.com/@BHU-Ayurveda\", \"Dr. Nikunj Trivedi – https://www.youtube.com/@DrNikunjTrivedi\", \"Homeopathy 360 – https://www.youtube.com/@Homeopathy360\"]', '[\"https://ayush.gov.in\", \"https://easyayurveda.com\", \"https://homeobook.com\", \"https://ccras.nic.in\", \"https://homoeopathy360.com\"]', 'Placements available through college internships in AYUSH hospitals, government clinics, and private wellness centers. EMR-based roles also open in digital health platforms.', '[\"Clinical Assistant\", \"Ayurvedic Consultant\", \"Homeopathic Consultant\", \"EMR Executive\", \"Case Documentation Analyst\", \"Health Counselor\"]', 'Case recording skills are in demand in clinics, hospitals, digital EMR setups, and teleconsultation platforms. Also valued in research documentation and wellness centers.', 'Starting: ₹10,000–₹18,000/month; Mid-level: ₹25,000–₹40,000/month; Senior/Private Practice: ₹60,000–₹1L+/month depending on setup and expertise.', 'Internships at AYUSH hospitals with clinical case writing exposure, EMR documentation, and participation in real-time consultations. Optional workshops at NIH, CCRAS.', 'Diploma/BAMS/BHMS → Clinical Intern → Health Assistant → Case Analyst → Senior Consultant → Independent Practitioner or Case Reviewer', '[\"EMR Documentation Certification\", \"AYUSH Case Taking Workshop\", \"Repertory & Case Analysis (CCRH/CCRAS)\", \"Certificate in Classical Ayurveda Case Management\", \"WHO Clinical Counseling Certificate\"]'),
('Medical', 'Veterinary Science', 'Animal Care Equipment', '[\"Indian Veterinary Research Institute (IVRI), Bareilly\", \"Tamil Nadu Veterinary and Animal Sciences University (TANUVAS)\", \"Guru Angad Dev Veterinary and Animal Sciences University (GADVASU), Ludhiana\", \"Karnataka Veterinary, Animal & Fisheries Sciences University, Bidar\", \"College of Veterinary Science, Assam Agricultural University\", \"Bombay Veterinary College, Mumbai\", \"Nagpur Veterinary College\", \"Veterinary College and Research Institute, Namakkal\", \"College of Veterinary Science, Hyderabad\", \"Kerala Veterinary and Animal Sciences University\"]', '[\"Veterinary Anatomy\", \"Animal Surgery\", \"Veterinary Pharmacology\", \"Diagnostic Imaging\", \"Animal Reproduction\", \"Livestock Production\", \"Animal Nutrition\", \"Clinical Medicine\"]', '[\"Textbook of Veterinary Anatomy – Dyce\", \"Veterinary Surgery – S.K. Uppal\", \"Veterinary Clinical Practices – G.R. Pathak\", \"Large Animal Diagnostic Imaging – Donald Thrall\", \"Veterinary Equipment and Instruments – Kathleen Freeman\", \"Merck Veterinary Manual\"]', '[\"Coursera – Animal Health & Welfare\", \"SWAYAM – Veterinary Science\", \"eVetPortal – Equipment Handling Courses\", \"IVRI E-learning\", \"Skill India – Veterinary Technician Courses\"]', '[\"IVRI – https://www.youtube.com/@IVRIIndia\", \"Vet Visit – https://www.youtube.com/@vetvisit\", \"VetHustle – https://www.youtube.com/@VetHustle\", \"Dr. Nilesh Parmar – https://www.youtube.com/@nileshparmarvet\", \"Vet Talks India – https://www.youtube.com/@VetTalksIndia\"]', '[\"https://ivri.nic.in\", \"https://kvasu.ac.in\", \"https://vethelplineindia.co.in\", \"https://merckvetmanual.com\", \"https://gadvasu.in\"]', 'Placement support offered by colleges; common recruiters include government vet departments, pharma firms, animal hospitals, and livestock health centers.', '[\"Veterinary Technician\", \"Animal Diagnostic Assistant\", \"Veterinary Officer\", \"Livestock Inspector\", \"Animal Surgery Assistant\"]', 'Opportunities available in both private and government sectors; growth in demand due to increasing animal welfare awareness, dairy industry, and pet healthcare.', 'Starting: ₹20,000–₹30,000/month; After 5+ years: ₹50,000–₹80,000/month; Government Veterinary Officers: ₹1L+/month depending on role and location.', 'Internships during final year in hospitals, diagnostic labs, and farms. Training in equipment handling, diagnostics, and emergency care is mandatory.', 'B.V.Sc → Junior Assistant → Veterinary Officer → Senior Veterinary Surgeon → Consultant / Director in Animal Health Services', '[\"Certificate in Animal Health Worker\", \"Veterinary Surgical Equipment Training – IVRI\", \"Certification in Animal Diagnostics – eVetPortal\", \"Diploma in Animal Care\", \"Coursera – Vet Equipment Handling\"]'),
('Medical', 'Veterinary Science', 'Lab Analysis Tools', '[\"Indian Veterinary Research Institute (IVRI), Bareilly\", \"Tamil Nadu Veterinary and Animal Sciences University (TANUVAS)\", \"Karnataka Veterinary, Animal & Fisheries Sciences University, Bidar\", \"Guru Angad Dev Veterinary and Animal Sciences University (GADVASU), Ludhiana\", \"College of Veterinary Science, Hyderabad\", \"Bombay Veterinary College, Mumbai\", \"College of Veterinary Science, Assam Agricultural University\", \"Nagpur Veterinary College\", \"Veterinary College and Research Institute, Namakkal\", \"Kerala Veterinary and Animal Sciences University (KVASU)\"]', '[\"Veterinary Pathology\", \"Veterinary Microbiology\", \"Veterinary Parasitology\", \"Clinical Biochemistry\", \"Veterinary Public Health\", \"Laboratory Diagnostics\", \"Immunology\", \"Zoonotic Diseases\"]', '[\"Veterinary Clinical Pathology – Ramesh Gupta\", \"Textbook of Veterinary Microbiology – Quinn et al.\", \"Laboratory Manual of Veterinary Microbiology – Thirunavukkarasu\", \"Veterinary Biochemistry – Kaneko\", \"Manual of Diagnostic Tests and Vaccines – OIE\", \"Merck Veterinary Manual\"]', '[\"SWAYAM – Veterinary Pathology & Diagnostics\", \"Coursera – Veterinary Public Health\", \"IVRI E-learning Portal\", \"Skill India – Veterinary Lab Technician\", \"edX – Microbiological Lab Skills\"]', '[\"IVRI – https://www.youtube.com/@IVRIIndia\", \"Vet Visit – https://www.youtube.com/@vetvisit\", \"Vet Talks India – https://www.youtube.com/@VetTalksIndia\", \"Vet Med Academy – https://www.youtube.com/@VetMedAcademy\", \"Animalia Pathology – https://www.youtube.com/@AnimaliaPathology\"]', '[\"https://ivri.nic.in\", \"https://kvasu.ac.in\", \"https://merckvetmanual.com\", \"https://oie.int\", \"https://vethelplineindia.co.in\"]', 'Placements include internships and lab assistantships in public and private diagnostic labs, food safety units, and animal research institutions. Major hiring by govt diagnostic centers and pharma companies.', '[\"Veterinary Lab Technician\", \"Clinical Pathology Assistant\", \"Animal Diagnostic Officer\", \"Microbiology Analyst\", \"Zoonotic Surveillance Specialist\"]', 'Growing demand in public health labs, food safety, diagnostic startups, animal pharma, and zoonotic disease surveillance programs.', 'Starting: ₹18,000–₹25,000/month; Experienced: ₹40,000–₹70,000/month; Government/Lead roles: ₹1L+/month depending on qualifications and responsibilities.', 'Final-year internships mandatory; training includes blood tests, fecal exam, ELISA, PCR, and use of spectrophotometers and biochemistry analyzers. Offered at IVRI, TANUVAS, and regional diagnostic labs.', 'B.V.Sc → Lab Assistant → Veterinary Diagnostic Officer → Lead Pathologist → Zoonotic Disease Surveillance Officer / Lab Director', '[\"Veterinary Lab Technician Certificate – Skill India\", \"CCRAS Animal Diagnostics Workshop\", \"ISO 17025 Lab Quality Certification\", \"PCR & Molecular Diagnostics – IVRI\", \"OIE Disease Surveillance Training\"]'),
('Design', 'Fashion Design', 'Adobe Illustrator', '[\"National Institute of Fashion Technology (NIFT)\", \"National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad\", \"Pearl Academy\", \"Symbiosis Institute of Design, Pune\", \"Amity School of Fashion Technology\", \"MIT Institute of Design, Pune\", \"Footwear Design and Development Institute (FDDI)\", \"JD Institute of Fashion Technology\", \"INIFD – International Institute of Fashion Design\", \"Srishti Institute of Art, Design & Technology, Bangalore\"]', '[\"Fashion Illustration\", \"Apparel Construction\", \"Textile Science\", \"Computer-Aided Fashion Design (CAFD)\", \"Fashion History\", \"Pattern Making\", \"Draping\", \"Adobe Suite Tools\"]', '[\"Adobe Illustrator for Fashion Design – Susan Lazear\", \"Fashion Flats and Technical Drawing – Bina Abling\", \"Digital Fashion Illustration with Adobe Illustrator – Kevin Tallon\", \"Patternmaking for Fashion Design – Helen Joseph-Armstrong\", \"Textiles: Concepts and Principles – Virginia Hencken Elsasser\"]', '[\"Coursera – Fashion Design and CAD by Parsons\", \"Skillshare – Fashion Flats in Adobe Illustrator\", \"Udemy – Adobe Illustrator for Fashion Design\", \"SWAYAM – Fashion Technology\", \"Domestika – Digital Fashion Sketching\"]', '[\"Zoe Hong – https://www.youtube.com/@zoehongteaches\", \"Justine Leconte – https://www.youtube.com/@JustineLeconte\", \"Fashtory – https://www.youtube.com/@fashtory\", \"NIFT – https://www.youtube.com/@NIFTIndia\", \"Fashion Design Sketching – https://www.youtube.com/@fashiondesignsketching\"]', '[\"https://nift.ac.in\", \"https://nid.edu\", \"https://vogue.in\", \"https://wgsn.com\", \"https://behance.net\"]', 'Top recruiters include H&M, Aditya Birla Group, Raymond, Zara India, and more. Internships and placements supported by most institutes. Freelance and startup culture is also growing.', '[\"Fashion Illustrator\", \"CAD Designer\", \"Print Designer\", \"Apparel Designer\", \"Fashion Merchandiser\"]', 'Demand is rising across e-commerce, retail, and fashion-tech platforms. Strong freelance and startup ecosystem.', 'Starting: ₹20,000–₹30,000/month; Mid-level: ₹50,000–₹80,000/month; Experienced/Lead roles: ₹1L+/month based on portfolio and brand association.', 'Internships typically held in 3rd or 4th year with major apparel brands and export houses. Students trained in Illustrator, Photoshop, and real-client tech pack creation.', 'Diploma/Degree → Assistant Designer → CAD/Print Designer → Senior Designer → Fashion Director or Brand Founder', '[\"Adobe Certified Professional – Illustrator\", \"Certificate in Digital Fashion Design – Domestika/Udemy\", \"Fashion Illustration Certification – NIFT/Skillshare\", \"AI in Fashion Design – Coursera\", \"Textile Design Specialization – SWAYAM\"]'),
('Design', 'Fashion Design', 'Pattern Making', '[\"National Institute of Fashion Technology (NIFT)\", \"National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad\", \"Pearl Academy\", \"Symbiosis Institute of Design\", \"Footwear Design and Development Institute (FDDI)\", \"MIT Institute of Design\", \"Amity School of Fashion Technology\", \"Srishti Institute of Art, Design & Technology\", \"JD Institute of Fashion Technology\", \"INIFD – International Institute of Fashion Design\"]', '[\"Garment Construction\", \"Draping Techniques\", \"Pattern Drafting\", \"Textile Science\", \"Computer-Aided Pattern Making\", \"Fashion Illustration\", \"Garment Manufacturing Process\"]', '[\"Patternmaking for Fashion Design – Helen Joseph-Armstrong\", \"Metric Pattern Cutting – Winifred Aldrich\", \"Draping for Fashion Design – Hilde Jaffe & Nurie Relis\", \"The Art of Fashion Draping – Connie Amaden-Crawford\", \"Patternmaking Made Easy – Connie Amaden-Crawford\"]', '[\"Coursera – Pattern Making by Parsons or UAL\", \"Udemy – Complete Guide to Pattern Making\", \"Skillshare – Garment Construction & Draping\", \"TUKAcad Online Pattern Training\", \"SWAYAM – Indian Fashion Design Courses\"]', '[\"Zoe Hong – https://www.youtube.com/@zoehongteaches\", \"Fashion Sewing Blog TV – https://www.youtube.com/@fashionsewingblogtv\", \"NIFT India – https://www.youtube.com/@NIFTIndia\", \"Made to Sew – https://www.youtube.com/@madetosew\", \"Professor Pincushion – https://www.youtube.com/@ProfessorPincushion\"]', '[\"https://nift.ac.in\", \"https://nid.edu\", \"https://tukatech.com\", \"https://burdastyle.com\", \"https://vogue.in\"]', 'Internships and placements available with top brands, apparel manufacturing units, and design houses. Most colleges offer placement support and industrial training projects.', '[\"Pattern Master\", \"CAD Pattern Designer\", \"Garment Technologist\", \"Sample Development Executive\", \"Fashion Designer (Tech Pack Focus)\"]', 'Growing demand across design studios, export houses, and production units due to digital transformation in pattern making and tech-pack development.', 'Starting: ₹20,000–₹30,000/month; Mid-level: ₹50,000–₹80,000/month; Senior roles: ₹1L+/month depending on experience and client portfolio.', 'Internships during 3rd/4th year with fashion brands, garment factories, or independent pattern studios. Training includes flat patterning, draping, CAD tools like TUKAcad and CLO3D.', 'Fashion Student → Assistant Pattern Maker → CAD Pattern Designer → Senior Pattern Master → Technical Head / Production Lead', '[\"TUKAcad Pattern Making Certificate\", \"CLO 3D Pattern Simulation Certification\", \"Gerber CAD Pattern Design Certificate\", \"NIFT Continuing Education – Pattern Making\", \"Certificate in Fashion Draping – Domestika/Udemy\"]'),
('Design', 'Graphic Design', 'Photoshop', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad\", \"MIT Institute of Design, Pune\", \"Symbiosis Institute of Design, Pune\", \"National Institute of Fashion Technology (NIFT)\", \"Pearl Academy\", \"Srishti Institute of Art, Design & Technology\", \"Amity School of Fine Arts\", \"Arena Animation\", \"MAAC – Maya Academy of Advanced Cinematics\", \"Lovely Professional University (LPU)\"]', '[\"Fundamentals of Design\", \"Typography\", \"Branding and Visual Identity\", \"Digital Illustration\", \"Layout & Composition\", \"UI/UX Basics\", \"Color Theory\", \"Adobe Creative Suite\"]', '[\"Adobe Photoshop Classroom in a Book – Conrad Chavez\", \"Digital Design Essentials – Rajesh Lal\", \"Thinking with Type – Ellen Lupton\", \"Graphic Design School – David Dabner\", \"Logo Modernism – Jens Müller\"]', '[\"Udemy – Photoshop Masterclass for Graphic Design\", \"Coursera – Graphic Design by CalArts\", \"Skillshare – Photoshop for Beginners to Advanced\", \"LinkedIn Learning – Photoshop CC Training Series\", \"Domestika – Photoshop for Designers\"]', '[\"PiXimperfect – https://www.youtube.com/@PiXimperfect\", \"GFXMentor – https://www.youtube.com/@GFXMentor\", \"Adobe Photoshop – https://www.youtube.com/@Photoshop\", \"The Futur – https://www.youtube.com/@thefutur\", \"Tutvid – https://www.youtube.com/@tutvid\"]', '[\"https://www.adobe.com/in/products/photoshop\", \"https://www.behance.net\", \"https://dribbble.com\", \"https://www.creativebloq.com\", \"https://99designs.in\"]', 'Graphic design graduates are recruited by media agencies, digital marketing firms, branding studios, and publishing houses. Freelance and remote work are widely available and growing.', '[\"Graphic Designer\", \"Creative Designer\", \"Visual Designer\", \"UI/UX Designer\", \"Branding Specialist\", \"Social Media Designer\", \"Freelance Illustrator\"]', 'High demand in digital marketing, advertising, and content creation. Freelance design and social media content work is especially trending.', 'Starting: ₹18,000–₹30,000/month; Mid-level: ₹50,000–₹80,000/month; With strong portfolio or freelance clients: ₹1L+/month.', 'Internships with design studios, digital marketing companies, or advertising agencies. Students typically work on live projects, brand identity design, and marketing content using Photoshop.', 'Design Intern → Junior Graphic Designer → Visual Designer → Senior Designer / Art Director → Creative Head / Design Consultant', '[\"Adobe Certified Professional – Photoshop\", \"Graphic Design Specialization – Coursera\", \"Photoshop CC Certification – Udemy/Domestika\", \"Motion Graphics with Photoshop – Skillshare\", \"Digital Portfolio Development – LinkedIn Learning\"]'),
('Design', 'Graphic Design', 'Illustrator', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID)\", \"MIT Institute of Design\", \"Symbiosis Institute of Design\", \"Srishti Institute of Art, Design & Technology\", \"Pearl Academy\", \"Amity School of Fine Arts\", \"Unitedworld Institute of Design\", \"Lovely Professional University\", \"Arena Animation\", \"MAAC – Maya Academy of Advanced Cinematics\"]', '[\"Visual Communication\", \"Typography\", \"Adobe Illustrator Tools\", \"Color Theory & Branding\", \"Print Design vs Digital Media\", \"UI/UX Basics\", \"Illustration & Storyboarding\"]', '[\"Adobe Illustrator Classroom in a Book – Brian Wood\", \"Vector Basic Training – Von Glitschka\", \"Thinking with Type – Ellen Lupton\", \"Logo Design Love – David Airey\", \"The Elements of Graphic Design – Alex W. White\"]', '[\"Coursera – Graphic Design by CalArts\", \"Udemy – Illustrator CC Masterclass\", \"Skillshare – Vector Illustration with Illustrator\", \"Domestika – Branding & Logos with Illustrator\", \"LinkedIn Learning – Illustrator CC Essential Training\"]', '[\"GFXMentor – https://www.youtube.com/@GFXMentor\", \"Satori Graphics – https://www.youtube.com/@SatoriGraphics\", \"Yes I\'m a Designer – https://www.youtube.com/@yesimadesigner\", \"Envato Tuts+ – https://www.youtube.com/@tutsplus\", \"The Futur – https://www.youtube.com/@thefutur\"]', '[\"https://www.adobe.com/in/products/illustrator\", \"https://www.behance.net\", \"https://dribbble.com\", \"https://vectornator.io\", \"https://99designs.in\"]', 'Colleges provide internship support and campus placements with ad agencies, product companies, and media houses. Portfolio and project work play a major role in hiring.', '[\"Graphic Designer\", \"Illustrator\", \"Visual Designer\", \"UI Designer\", \"Packaging Designer\", \"Freelance Logo Designer\"]', 'High demand in e-commerce, branding, advertising, and freelance marketplaces. Illustrator remains one of the most requested tools for print and digital design.', 'Starting: ₹20,000–₹35,000/month; Experienced: ₹60,000–₹90,000/month; Freelance/Remote: ₹1L+/month depending on project size.', 'Internships at branding studios, creative agencies, or freelance mentorships. Interns typically handle logo creation, social media graphics, and client design briefs using Illustrator.', 'Student → Junior Graphic Designer → Visual Illustrator → Senior Designer → Creative Director → Studio Owner / Consultant', '[\"Adobe Certified Professional – Illustrator\", \"Logo & Brand Identity Design – Coursera/Skillshare\", \"Illustration for Design – Domestika\", \"Motion Graphics with Illustrator – Skillshare\", \"Design Systems with Illustrator – Figma Integration\"]'),
('Design', 'Graphic Design', 'Canva', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID)\", \"MIT Institute of Design\", \"Symbiosis Institute of Design\", \"Pearl Academy\", \"Srishti Manipal Institute\", \"Unitedworld Institute of Design\", \"Amity School of Fine Arts\", \"Lovely Professional University\", \"Arena Animation\", \"INIFD / JD Institute\"]', '[\"Design Principles\", \"Typography\", \"Color Theory\", \"Visual Hierarchy\", \"Brand Identity\", \"Layout & Composition\", \"Social Media Marketing\", \"Content Creation & Storytelling\"]', '[\"Don\'t Make Me Think – Steve Krug\", \"The Non-Designer\'s Design Book – Robin Williams\", \"Designing Brand Identity – Alina Wheeler\", \"Visual Grammar – Christian Leborg\", \"Show Your Work – Austin Kleon\"]', '[\"Coursera – Canva for Beginners\", \"Udemy – Canva Master Course for Beginners\", \"Skillshare – Social Media Design with Canva\", \"HubSpot Academy – Canva Content Marketing\", \"Canva Design School – Official Tutorials\"]', '[\"Canva – https://www.youtube.com/@Canva\", \"Design with Canva – https://www.youtube.com/@designwithcanva\", \"Think School – https://www.youtube.com/@ThinkSchool\", \"Create with Canva – https://www.youtube.com/@CreateWithCanva\", \"The Futur – https://www.youtube.com/@thefutur\"]', '[\"https://www.canva.com/learn\", \"https://www.creativebloq.com\", \"https://www.udemy.com\", \"https://www.skillshare.com\", \"https://www.behance.net\"]', 'Design colleges offer limited direct Canva placements, but students find internship and freelancing opportunities using Canva portfolios. Small agencies and marketing teams value Canva skills.', '[\"Canva Designer\", \"Visual Content Creator\", \"Social Media Designer\", \"Presentation Designer\", \"Freelance Canva Expert\"]', 'Canva skills are in high demand in startups, content creation, influencer marketing, and remote freelance projects. Particularly strong for social media and branding.', 'Starting: ₹15,000–₹25,000/month; With experience: ₹35,000–₹60,000/month; Freelancers can earn ₹50,000+/month based on projects and clients.', 'Internships available in digital marketing agencies, influencer teams, content studios, and education platforms. Canva is used for real-world design like Instagram posts, presentations, and brand kits.', 'Student → Canva Intern → Junior Visual Designer → Social Media Designer → Creative Lead / Brand Strategist', '[\"Canva Design School Certificate\", \"Udemy – Canva Mastery Certificate\", \"Coursera – Canva Projects\", \"HubSpot – Content Marketing Certificate\", \"LinkedIn Learning – Canva for Business\"]'),
('Design', 'Interior Design', 'AutoCAD', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID)\", \"CEPT University\", \"MIT Institute of Design\", \"Pearl Academy\", \"Srishti Manipal Institute\", \"Amity School of Design\", \"SPA Delhi\", \"Lovely Professional University\", \"JD Institute\", \"Unitedworld Institute of Design\"]', '[\"Architectural Drawing\", \"Space Planning\", \"Materials & Finishes\", \"Building Services\", \"Lighting & Acoustics\", \"AutoCAD\", \"Sustainable Design\", \"Interior Design History\"]', '[\"Interior Design Illustrated – Francis D.K. Ching\", \"Time-Saver Standards – Joseph DeChiara\", \"AutoCAD for Interior Design – Beverly Kirkpatrick\", \"Interior Design Reference Manual – David Kent Ballast\", \"Interior Design Materials – Lisa Godsey\"]', '[\"Udemy – AutoCAD for Interior Design\", \"Coursera – Making Architecture\", \"LinkedIn Learning – AutoCAD for Interior Designers\", \"Skillshare – AutoCAD Essentials\", \"NPTEL – Interior Design Basics\"]', '[\"House of B – https://www.youtube.com/@HouseofB\", \"Interior Design CAD – https://www.youtube.com/@interiordesigncad\", \"HomeLane – https://www.youtube.com/@HomelaneIndia\", \"AutoCAD India – https://www.youtube.com/@autocadindia\", \"The Futur – https://www.youtube.com/@thefutur\"]', '[\"https://www.autodesk.in/products/autocad\", \"https://www.houzz.in\", \"https://www.archdaily.com\", \"https://www.designboom.com\", \"https://www.nid.edu\"]', 'Colleges offer placements through interior consultancies and architecture firms. Strong portfolios and CAD drafting ability are key for selection.', '[\"Interior Designer\", \"CAD Drafter\", \"Space Planner\", \"3D Visualizer\", \"Modular Kitchen Designer\", \"Freelance Consultant\"]', 'High demand in real estate, renovation, modular kitchen, interior décor startups. AutoCAD remains essential for 2D/3D layout design.', 'Starting: ₹20,000–₹35,000/month; With experience: ₹50,000–₹80,000+/month; Freelancers may earn ₹10,000–₹1L+ per project.', 'Internships with architecture firms, interior studios (Livspace, Homelane). Work includes site layout, CAD drawing, fixture planning, and client presentations.', 'Student → Intern → Junior Designer → AutoCAD Drafter → Interior Designer → Project Manager → Creative Director / Studio Owner', '[\"AutoCAD Certified Professional – Autodesk\", \"Interior Design CAD – Udemy/Skillshare\", \"Sustainable Interior Design – Coursera\", \"Advanced Drafting – LinkedIn Learning\", \"SketchUp + AutoCAD – Domestika\"]'),
('Design', 'Interior Design', 'SketchUp', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID)\", \"CEPT University\", \"MIT Institute of Design\", \"Pearl Academy\", \"Srishti Manipal Institute\", \"School of Planning and Architecture (SPA), Delhi\", \"Amity School of Design\", \"Lovely Professional University\", \"Unitedworld Institute of Design\", \"JD Institute of Fashion Technology\"]', '[\"Space Planning\", \"3D Modeling & Visualization\", \"Interior Materials\", \"Lighting & Acoustics\", \"SketchUp\", \"Sustainable Design\", \"Furniture & Fixture Design\", \"Interior Detailing\"]', '[\"Interior Design Illustrated – Francis D.K. Ching\", \"SketchUp for Interior Design – Lydia Sloan Cline\", \"Residential Interior Design – Maureen Mitton\", \"Architectural Rendering with SketchUp – Daniel Tal\", \"Design Drawing – Francis D.K. Ching\"]', '[\"Udemy – SketchUp for Interior Design\", \"LinkedIn Learning – SketchUp Pro for Interior Design\", \"Skillshare – 3D Interior Design with SketchUp\", \"Coursera – 3D Model Creation\", \"SketchUp Campus – Official Tutorials\"]', '[\"SketchUp School – https://www.youtube.com/@SketchUpSchool\", \"Show It Better – https://www.youtube.com/@showitbetter\", \"SketchUp – https://www.youtube.com/@SketchUp\", \"Designer Hacks – https://www.youtube.com/@DesignerHacks\", \"Interior Design Academy – https://www.youtube.com/@interiordesignacademy\"]', '[\"https://learn.sketchup.com\", \"https://www.designconnected.com\", \"https://3dwarehouse.sketchup.com\", \"https://www.cgtrader.com\", \"https://archdaily.com\"]', 'Design schools place students in architecture and interior firms, real estate developers, and visualization studios. SketchUp expertise enhances shortlisting for roles involving 3D layout presentation.', '[\"3D Interior Designer\", \"SketchUp Specialist\", \"Interior Visualizer\", \"Interior Consultant\", \"Freelance 3D Modeler\", \"Set & Event Designer\"]', 'High demand across real estate, architectural, and modular interior design firms. Clients seek realistic previews, and SketchUp delivers efficient 3D solutions.', 'Starting: ₹20,000–₹35,000/month; Mid-Level: ₹50,000–₹80,000/month; Freelance: ₹5,000–₹50,000+ per project depending on scope.', 'Internships in design studios (e.g., Homelane, Livspace, Morphogenesis) focus on real projects where SketchUp is used for modeling spaces, layouts, and presentations with rendering plugins like V-Ray or Enscape.', 'Student → Modeling Intern → 3D Interior Designer → SketchUp Specialist → Senior Visualizer → Design Lead / Studio Owner', '[\"SketchUp Pro Certification – Trimble\", \"SketchUp Interior Design – Udemy\", \"V-Ray for SketchUp Certificate – Chaos Group\", \"Enscape for SketchUp – Rendering Training\", \"Domestika – Advanced 3D Interiors with SketchUp\"]'),
('Design', 'Interior Design', '3DS Max', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID)\", \"CEPT University\", \"MIT Institute of Design\", \"Pearl Academy\", \"Srishti Manipal Institute\", \"School of Planning and Architecture (SPA), Delhi\", \"Lovely Professional University\", \"Amity University\", \"Unitedworld Institute of Design\", \"JD Institute of Fashion Technology\"]', '[\"Interior Design Studio\", \"3D Visualization & Modeling\", \"Lighting & Rendering\", \"CAD + 3DS Max Integration\", \"Space Planning\", \"Interior Material Finishes\", \"Animation Walkthrough\", \"Building Construction Detailing\"]', '[\"3ds Max 2022 Fundamentals – Ascent\", \"Interior Design Illustrated – Francis D.K. Ching\", \"3D Rendering in AutoCAD and 3ds Max – Brian Smith\", \"Architectural Rendering with 3ds Max and V-Ray – Roger Cusson\", \"SketchUp to 3DS Max to V-Ray Workflow – Jamie Cardoso\"]', '[\"Udemy – 3DS Max + V-Ray Interior Design\", \"LinkedIn Learning – 3DS Max for Interior Visualization\", \"Skillshare – 3DS Max for Beginners\", \"Coursera – 3D Visualization Techniques\", \"Pluralsight – 3DS Max Interior Courses\"]', '[\"3DS Max Tutorials – https://www.youtube.com/@3dsMaxOfficial\", \"Free 3D Tutorials – https://www.youtube.com/@free3dtutorials\", \"Blackhart Films – https://www.youtube.com/@BlackhartFilms\", \"Arch Viz Artist – https://www.youtube.com/@archvizartist\", \"Easy Render – https://www.youtube.com/@easyrender\"]', '[\"https://www.autodesk.in/products/3ds-max\", \"https://www.evermotion.org\", \"https://cgarchitect.com\", \"https://www.behance.net\", \"https://www.cgtrader.com\"]', 'Design institutions offer placement through architecture firms, real estate developers, and rendering agencies. 3DS Max proficiency, especially with V-Ray or Enscape, boosts placement potential.', '[\"Interior 3D Visualizer\", \"3DS Max Specialist\", \"Interior Rendering Artist\", \"Architectural Animator\", \"Freelance Rendering Consultant\", \"V-Ray/3DS Max Trainer\"]', 'Strong demand in real estate visualization and interior firms for photorealistic modeling. Candidates with high-end walkthrough portfolios are in high demand.', 'Starting: ₹25,000–₹40,000/month; 3–5 years: ₹60,000–₹1.2L+/month; Freelancers earn ₹5,000–₹1L+ per project depending on complexity.', 'Internships in firms like Morphogenesis, Livspace, The KariGhars, FHD Group. Work includes photorealistic rendering, animation, material application, and lighting simulation.', 'Student → Intern → 3D Visualizer → 3DS Max Specialist → Senior Rendering Artist → Creative Lead → Visualization Studio Owner', '[\"Autodesk Certified Professional – 3DS Max\", \"V-Ray for 3DS Max – Chaos Group\", \"CGI Visualization Masterclass – Udemy\", \"Advanced Rendering – Pluralsight\", \"Interior Rendering – Domestika\"]'),
