Arena, and Whistling Woods offer campus placements. Companies hiring include Technicolor, Red Chillies VFX, Hotstar, Netflix, and digital agencies. High demand for AE professionals in content creation and EdTech.', 'Motion Graphic Designer,Video Editor & Animator,Compositing Artist,VFX Artist,2D Animator,Content Creator/YouTuber', 'High demand across advertising, EdTech, gaming, OTT platforms, social media, YouTube, and digital marketing', 'Entry: ₹2.5–5 LPA, Mid-level: ₹6–9 LPA, Senior: ₹10–18+ LPA, Freelance: ₹1,000 – ₹10,000+ per project', 'Internship providers include ad agencies, post-production studios, animation houses, EdTech firms, and platforms like Internshala, LinkedIn, Fiverr. Tools: AE, Premiere Pro, Photoshop, Illustrator, Cinema 4D.', 'Student → Junior Motion Designer → Motion Graphics Artist → VFX Designer → Senior Animator → Creative Director or Freelancer → YouTube Educator → Studio Owner', 'Adobe Certified Professional (After Effects), School of Motion Certifications, Domestika Certificates, Arena/MAAC Diplomas, LinkedIn Skill Badges, Motion Design School Certifications'),
('Design', 'Animation & VFX', 'Maya', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad\", \"Whistling Woods International, Mumbai\", \"MAAC (Maya Academy of Advanced Cinematics)\", \"Arena Animation\", \"Zee Institute of Creative Art (ZICA)\", \"MIT Institute of Design, Pune\", \"Srishti Manipal Institute of Art, Design & Technology\", \"Lovely Professional University, Punjab\", \"Frameboxx Animation & Visual Effects Institute\", \"NSHM Knowledge Campus, Kolkata\"]', 'Principles of 3D Animation,Character Design and Development,3D Modeling & Texturing,Rigging and Skinning,Lighting & Rendering,Dynamics (Particles, Hair, Cloth),Compositing & Post-production,Camera Tracking,Portfolio Development', '[\"Introducing Autodesk Maya 2022 - Dariush Derakhshani\", \"The Art of 3D Computer Animation and Effects - Isaac Kerlow\", \"Stop Staring - Jason Osipa\", \"Digital Lighting and Rendering - Jeremy Birn\", \"Character Animation with Maya - J. Cubberly & M. Oshita\"]', '[\"LinkedIn Learning - Maya Essential Training\", \"Udemy - Autodesk Maya 3D Animation & Modeling\", \"Coursera - 3D Animation by University of London\", \"Pluralsight - Maya VFX, Rigging, and Modeling Courses\", \"CG Spectrum - Diploma in 3D Modeling with Maya\", \"Gnomon Workshop - Maya Training\"]', '[\"Mike Hermes - https://www.youtube.com/user/banimation2000\", \"Academic Phoenix Plus - https://www.youtube.com/c/AcademicPhoenixPlus\", \"CG Geek - https://www.youtube.com/c/Blenderfan93\", \"Game Dev Academy - https://www.youtube.com/@GameDevAcademy\", \"Simply Maya - https://www.youtube.com/@SimplyMaya\", \"Arrimus 3D - https://www.youtube.com/@Arrimus3D\", \"FlippedNormals - https://www.youtube.com/c/FlippedNormals\"]', '[\"https://www.autodesk.com/products/maya\", \"https://www.pluralsight.com\", \"https://www.cgsociety.org\", \"https://forums.autodesk.com\", \"https://www.3dtotal.com\", \"https://www.artstation.com\"]', 'Top institutes like MAAC, Arena, Whistling Woods, and Srishti offer placement opportunities. Companies hiring Maya artists include Technicolor, DNEG, Red Chillies VFX, Prime Focus, Ubisoft, and Netflix Studios.', '3D Animator,Character Modeler,Rigging Artist,VFX Artist,Lighting Artist,Environment Artist,Technical Animator,Game Asset Designer', 'High demand in film production, game development, TV commercials, AR/VR, and freelancing', 'Entry: ₹3–5.5 LPA, Mid-level: ₹6–10 LPA, Senior: ₹12–20+ LPA, Freelance: ₹2,000–₹25,000+ per project', 'Internship opportunities with studios like Green Gold Animation, Red Chillies VFX, Byju’s, and Paperboat Studios. Duration: 3–6 months. Platforms: Internshala, LinkedIn, MAAC/Arena tie-ups.', 'Student → 3D Generalist/Junior Animator → Rigging/Modeling Specialist → VFX Artist → Art Lead → Technical Director → Creative Head ↘ Freelancer → Studio Owner → Mentor / Trainer', 'Autodesk Certified Maya Professional,Arena / MAAC Diploma Certificate,Coursera Verified Certificates,LinkedIn Learning Course Certificates,Pluralsight Skill IQ,Gnomon Workshop Completion Certificates'),
('Design', 'UI/UX Design', 'Figma', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad\", \"IDC School of Design, IIT Bombay\", \"MIT Institute of Design, Pune\", \"Srishti Manipal Institute of Art, Design & Technology\", \"UPES School of Design, Dehradun\", \"ISDI School of Design and Innovation, Mumbai\", \"Pearl Academy, Delhi/Mumbai\", \"World University of Design (WUD), Haryana\", \"IIIT Hyderabad – Human-Centered Design Lab\", \"Chitkara University – UI/UX & Interaction Design\"]', 'Design Thinking,Human-Computer Interaction (HCI),Visual Design Principles,UX Research & Usability Testing,Interaction Design,Information Architecture,Responsive Web & App Design,Typography & Color Theory,Prototyping Tools', '[\"Don\'t Make Me Think - Steve Krug\", \"The Design of Everyday Things - Don Norman\", \"Hooked - Nir Eyal\", \"100 Things Every Designer Needs to Know About People - Susan Weinschenk\", \"Refactoring UI - Adam Wathan & Steve Schoger\"]', '[\"Coursera - UI/UX Design Specialization (University of Michigan)\", \"Google UX Certificate - Coursera\", \"Udemy - Figma UI/UX Design Essentials\", \"Interaction Design Foundation - UX Courses\", \"LinkedIn Learning - UX Research, Figma for Designers\", \"Dribbble Learn - Design Systems & Case Studies\"]', '[\"Flux Academy - https://www.youtube.com/c/FluxAcademy\", \"DesignCourse - https://www.youtube.com/c/DesignCourse\", \"Jesse Showalter - https://www.youtube.com/c/JesseShowalter\", \"Kevin Powell - https://www.youtube.com/kepowob\", \"CharliMarieTV - https://www.youtube.com/c/CharliMarieTV\", \"Laith Wallace - https://www.youtube.com/c/LaithWallace\", \"Mizko - https://www.youtube.com/c/Mizko\"]', '[\"https://www.figma.com/learn\", \"https://www.interaction-design.org\", \"https://uxdesign.cc\", \"https://www.behance.net\", \"https://dribbble.com\", \"https://uxplanet.org\"]', 'Colleges like NID, MITID, ISDI, and Pearl have dedicated placement cells. Top recruiters include Google, Microsoft, Infosys, TCS, Swiggy, Ola, Razorpay, Flipkart, Paytm, and agencies like Lollypop, Fractal Ink, YUJ Designs.', 'UI/UX Designer,Product Designer,UX Researcher,UX Writer,UX Analyst,Interaction Designer,Design System Manager', 'Very high demand in tech startups, FinTech, EdTech, health apps, global SaaS companies, and freelance marketplaces', 'Entry: ₹4–7 LPA, Mid-level: ₹8–15 LPA, Senior: ₹18–30+ LPA, Freelancers: ₹1,000–₹5,000+ per screen or project', 'Internship providers include startups, UX design studios, EdTech companies. Apply via Internshala, LinkedIn, AngelList. Tools used: Figma, XD, Miro, Maze. Duration: 2–6 months.', 'Student → UI/UX Intern → Junior Designer → UI/UX Designer → Product Designer → Senior Designer → UX Lead → Design Director ↘ Freelancer → Consultant → UX Strategist', 'Google UX Design Certificate,Coursera Verified Certificate,Adobe XD Certified Expert,Interaction Design Foundation Badge,Figma Community Certificates,LinkedIn Learning UX/UI Certificates,Dribbble Certified Designer'),
('Design', 'UI/UX Design', 'Wireframing', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad\", \"IDC, IIT Bombay\", \"Srishti Manipal Institute of Art, Design & Technology\", \"MIT Institute of Design, Pune\", \"UPES School of Design, Dehradun\", \"ISDI School of Design & Innovation, Mumbai\", \"Pearl Academy, Delhi/Mumbai\", \"World University of Design, Haryana\", \"Chitkara University – UX Program\", \"DSK International School of Design\"]', 'Design Thinking,UX Research & Personas,Interaction Design,Usability Principles,Human-Computer Interaction (HCI),Information Architecture,Wireframing & Low/Mid-Fidelity Prototyping,Heuristic Evaluation,UI Design Principles', '[\"About Face - Alan Cooper\", \"Don\'t Make Me Think - Steve Krug\", \"Sketching User Experiences - Bill Buxton\", \"The UX Book - Rex Hartson\", \"UX for Beginners - Joel Marsh\"]', '[\"Coursera - Google UX Design Certificate\", \"Udemy - Wireframing with Figma, Balsamiq & Sketch\", \"LinkedIn Learning - Learning Wireframing & UX Documentation\", \"Interaction Design Foundation - Wireframing for UX Designers\", \"Skillshare - Rapid Wireframing in Figma/Balsamiq\"]', '[\"AJ&Smart - https://www.youtube.com/c/AJSmart\", \"Flux Academy - https://www.youtube.com/c/FluxAcademy\", \"Jesse Showalter - https://www.youtube.com/c/JesseShowalter\", \"CharliMarieTV - https://www.youtube.com/c/CharliMarieTV\", \"Laith Wallace - https://www.youtube.com/c/LaithWallace\", \"Mizko - https://www.youtube.com/c/Mizko\"]', '[\"https://balsamiq.com\", \"https://www.figma.com\", \"https://www.adaptivepath.org\", \"https://uxdesign.cc\", \"https://www.interaction-design.org\"]', 'Top UI/UX colleges such as NID, ISDI, and Srishti offer strong placement support. Companies hiring wireframing-skilled designers include Google, Microsoft, Razorpay, CRED, Swiggy, and Lollypop Studio.', 'UX Designer,Wireframing Specialist,UI/UX Intern,Interaction Designer,Product Experience Designer', 'In-demand across startups, SaaS platforms, EdTech, FinTech, and remote freelance marketplaces', 'Entry: ₹3.5–6.5 LPA, Mid-level: ₹7–12 LPA, Senior: ₹14–22+ LPA, Freelance: ₹1,000–₹5,000+ per wireframe flow', 'Internships available with UX design studios, tech startups, and digital agencies. Apply via Internshala, AngelList, LinkedIn. Duration: 2–6 months. Tools: Figma, Balsamiq, XD.', 'Student → UX Intern → UX Designer → Wireframe/Prototype Specialist → Product Designer → Senior Designer → UX Architect → UX Director ↘ Freelancer → Design Consultant', 'Google UX Design Certificate,Interaction Design Foundation – Wireframing Course,LinkedIn Learning UX & Wireframing Certificate,Balsamiq Wireframing Bootcamp,Adobe Certified Professional (XD),Design Thinking Certifications'),
('Design', 'Photography', 'Lightroom', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad\", \"Jawaharlal Nehru Architecture and Fine Arts University (JNAFAU), Hyderabad\", \"Delhi College of Photography\", \"Sir JJ School of Applied Art, Mumbai\", \"Symbiosis School of Photography, Pune\", \"Asian Academy of Film and Television (AAFT), Noida\", \"National Institute of Photography, Mumbai\", \"Raffles Millennium International, Bangalore\", \"NICC International College of Design, Bangalore\", \"Fergusson College, Pune\"]', 'History & Evolution of Photography,Composition & Aesthetics,Digital Image Processing,Camera Handling & Exposure Techniques,Post-Processing (Lightroom & Photoshop),Lighting (Natural & Studio),Color Theory,Storytelling Through Images,Portfolio Development', '[\"Understanding Exposure - Bryan Peterson\", \"The Digital Photography Book - Scott Kelby\", \"Light, Science and Magic - Fil Hunter\", \"Adobe Lightroom Classic Classroom in a Book - Rafael Concepcion\", \"The Photographer\'s Eye - Michael Freeman\"]', '[\"Udemy - Adobe Lightroom Masterclass\", \"Coursera - Photography Basics & Beyond (University of Michigan)\", \"Domestika - Professional Photo Retouching in Lightroom\", \"LinkedIn Learning - Lightroom CC for Photographers\", \"CreativeLive - Lightroom Editing Essentials\", \"Skillshare - Lightroom Workflow for Photographers\"]', '[\"Peter McKinnon - https://www.youtube.com/c/PeterMcKinnon\", \"Mango Street - https://www.youtube.com/c/MangoStreet\", \"Jessica Kobeissi - https://www.youtube.com/c/JessicaKobeissi\", \"The Art of Photography - https://www.youtube.com/c/theartofphotography\", \"Jamie Windsor - https://www.youtube.com/c/JamieWindsor\", \"Signature Edits - https://www.youtube.com/c/SignatureEdits\", \"Adobe Lightroom - https://www.youtube.com/user/AdobeLightroom\"]', '[\"https://www.adobe.com/products/photoshop-lightroom\", \"https://www.digitalphotomentor.com\", \"https://www.lightstalking.com\", \"https://fstoppers.com\", \"https://500px.com\", \"https://www.photoblog.com\"]', 'Photography colleges offer limited structured placements. However, students get connected to media houses, fashion studios, and event companies. Freelancing and internships are critical to career building.', 'Photographer,Photo Retoucher,Visual Content Creator,Lightroom Editor,Event/Portrait Photographer,Travel/Documentary Photographer', 'Steady demand in wedding, fashion, product photography, content marketing, and freelancing', 'Entry: ₹2.5–4.5 LPA, Mid-level: ₹5–10 LPA, Senior: ₹12–18+ LPA, Freelance: ₹5,000–₹1,00,000 per shoot', 'Internships with studios, media companies, and events. Roles include editing, lighting assistant, second shooter. Duration: 1–3 months. Platforms: Internshala, Indeed, networking.', 'Student → Assistant Photographer → Independent Photographer → Studio Owner → Creative Director → Photo Educator ↘ Lightroom Specialist → Visual Content Consultant', 'Adobe Certified Professional – Lightroom,Coursera Photography Certificate (Michigan),Udemy Lightroom Masterclass Certificate,Domestika Lightroom Editing Certificate,CreativeLive Workshop Certificate,Canon/Nikon Academy Workshop Certificate');
INSERT INTO `career_recommendation` (`field`, `domain`, `technical_skill`, `best_colleges`, `core_subjects`, `recommended_books`, `online_courses`, `youtube_channels`, `websites`, `placement_info`, `job_roles`, `job_status`, `salary_info`, `training_internship`, `career_path`, `certifications`) VALUES
('Design', 'Photography', 'DSLR Handling', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad\", \"Delhi College of Photography\", \"Light & Life Academy, Ooty\", \"Sir JJ School of Applied Art, Mumbai\", \"Symbiosis School of Photography, Pune\", \"Asian Academy of Film & Television (AAFT), Noida\", \"Seamedu School of Pro-Expressionism, Pune/Bangalore\", \"Jawaharlal Nehru Architecture and Fine Arts University (JNAFAU), Hyderabad\", \"National Institute of Photography, Mumbai\", \"Sri Aurobindo Centre for Arts and Communication (SACAC), Delhi\"]', 'Basics of DSLR Photography,Exposure Triangle (Aperture, Shutter Speed, ISO),Color Theory & White Balance,Studio & Natural Lighting,Photography Genres (Fashion, Wildlife, Portrait, Product),Image Composition & Framing,Post-Processing (Lightroom/Photoshop),Photography Ethics & Visual Storytelling,DSLR Video Basics', '[\"Understanding Exposure - Bryan Peterson\", \"The Photographer\'s Eye - Michael Freeman\", \"Digital Photography Complete Course - DK\", \"The Digital Photography Book - Scott Kelby\", \"DSLR Photography for Beginners - Brian Black\"]', '[\"Udemy - DSLR Photography for Beginners\", \"Coursera - Photography Basics & Beyond (University of Michigan)\", \"Domestika - Digital Photography for Beginners\", \"LinkedIn Learning - Learning DSLR Photography\", \"Skillshare - Fundamentals of DSLR Shooting\", \"Canon Edge - DSLR Tutorials (Canon India)\"]', '[\"Tony & Chelsea Northrup - https://www.youtube.com/user/VistaClues\", \"Peter McKinnon - https://www.youtube.com/c/PeterMcKinnon\", \"FroKnowsPhoto - https://www.youtube.com/user/JaredPolin\", \"Mango Street - https://www.youtube.com/c/MangoStreet\", \"Jessica Kobeissi - https://www.youtube.com/c/JessicaKobeissi\", \"Saurav Sinha - https://www.youtube.com/c/SauravSinhaPhotography\", \"DSLR Video Shooter - https://www.youtube.com/c/DSLRVideoShooter\"]', '[\"https://www.cambridgeincolour.com\", \"https://www.digital-photography-school.com\", \"https://fstoppers.com\", \"https://www.adorama.com/alc\", \"https://photographycourse.net\", \"https://www.canonedge.in\"]', 'Top colleges like NID and Symbiosis connect students with media firms, fashion shoots, and film studios. Structured placements are limited, but high freelance and project-based opportunity exists.', 'DSLR Photographer,Assistant Photographer,Videographer,Photography Trainer,Event Coverage Specialist,Freelance Photojournalist', 'High demand in event photography, ecommerce shoots, fashion campaigns, journalism, and creative content marketing', 'Entry: ₹2–4.5 LPA, Mid-level: ₹5–10 LPA, Senior: ₹12–20+ LPA, Freelance: ₹5,000–₹50,000+ per event/project', 'Internships available in photography studios, film production houses, wedding/event companies, and ecommerce content teams. Apply via Internshala, LinkedIn, and Canon/Nikon India workshops.', 'Student → Assistant Photographer → DSLR Photographer → Independent Freelancer → Studio Owner → Cinematographer → Visual Director ↘ DSLR Videographer → Commercial Campaign Shooter', 'Canon/Nikon Academy DSLR Certificate,Adobe Certified Lightroom Expert,Coursera Photography Certificate (Michigan),Udemy DSLR Photography Certification,Domestika DSLR Courses,Skillshare Lightroom + DSLR Essentials'),
('Design', 'Photography', 'Editing Tools', '[\"National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad\", \"Delhi College of Photography\", \"Light & Life Academy, Ooty\", \"Sir JJ School of Applied Art, Mumbai\", \"Symbiosis School of Photography, Pune\", \"Asian Academy of Film & Television (AAFT), Noida\", \"Seamedu School of Pro-Expressionism, Pune/Bangalore\", \"National Institute of Photography, Mumbai\", \"Sri Aurobindo Centre for Arts & Communication (SACAC), Delhi\", \"NICC International College of Design, Bangalore\"]', 'Photo Composition & Visual Storytelling,Image Post-Processing Techniques,Color Theory in Photography,Studio & Outdoor Lighting,Digital Workflow Management,RAW Processing Tools,Creative Photo Manipulation,Editing for Print vs Web,Portfolio & Branding', '[\"Photoshop for Photographers - Martin Evening\", \"The Adobe Photoshop Lightroom Book - Scott Kelby\", \"Mastering Photoshop for Photographers - Katrin Eismann\", \"The Digital Negative - Jeff Schewe\", \"Creative Black and White - Harold Davis\"]', '[\"Udemy - Mastering Photo Editing with Lightroom & Photoshop\", \"Coursera - Digital Photography & Editing (University of Michigan)\", \"Domestika - Photoshop Editing for Photographers\", \"Skillshare - Lightroom and Photoshop Workflow for Creatives\", \"LinkedIn Learning - Advanced Editing for Photographers\", \"CreativeLive - Photoshop Week & Retouching 101\"]', '[\"Phlearn - https://www.youtube.com/c/Phlearn\", \"Peter McKinnon - https://www.youtube.com/c/PeterMcKinnon\", \"Piximperfect - https://www.youtube.com/c/PiXimperfect\", \"Signature Edits - https://www.youtube.com/c/SignatureEdits\", \"Mango Street - https://www.youtube.com/c/MangoStreet\", \"Jamie Windsor - https://www.youtube.com/c/JamieWindsor\"]', '[\"https://www.adobe.com/\", \"https://fstoppers.com/\", \"https://www.lightroomqueen.com/\", \"https://www.dpreview.com/\", \"https://skylum.com/luminar\", \"https://www.captureone.com/\"]', 'Top colleges provide connections with post-production studios, magazines, and freelance platforms. Structured placement is limited, but experienced editors are in demand for creative, e-commerce, and wedding sectors.', 'Photo Editor,Retoucher,Visual Content Designer,Freelance Editor,Lightroom Specialist,Image Correction Expert', 'Consistently high demand across e-commerce, wedding/event, fashion, and media domains. Strong freelance and remote work opportunities.', 'Entry: ₹2.5–5 LPA, Mid-level: ₹5–9 LPA, Senior: ₹10–18+ LPA, Freelancers: ₹500–₹5,000 per project or ₹10K–₹1L/month', 'Internships available with post-production agencies, wedding editing services, media houses. Roles include RAW processing, color correction, masking, retouching. Tools: Lightroom, Photoshop, Luminar.', 'Student → Editing Intern → Junior Editor → Photo Retoucher → Senior Editor → Creative Director → Post-production Lead ↘ Freelancer → Online Tutor → Editing Agency Owner', 'Adobe Certified Professional – Photoshop & Lightroom,Coursera Digital Photography & Editing Certificate (Michigan),Phlearn PRO Retouching Certificate'),
('Design', 'Film Making', 'Adobe Premiere Pro', '[\"Film and Television Institute of India (FTII), Pune\", \"Satyajit Ray Film and Television Institute (SRFTI), Kolkata\", \"Whistling Woods International, Mumbai\", \"AAFT (Asian Academy of Film & Television), Noida\", \"National Institute of Design (NID), Ahmedabad\", \"Xavier Institute of Communications (XIC), Mumbai\", \"Ramesh Sippy Academy of Cinema and Entertainment, Mumbai\", \"L V Prasad Film and TV Academy, Chennai\", \"Seamedu School of Pro-Expressionism, Pune\", \"Mumbai University - Department of Film & Television\"]', 'Fundamentals of Film Editing,Narrative Structure & Storytelling,Audio for Video,Color Theory & Grading,Editing Aesthetics,Post-Production Workflow,Visual Effects Basics,Script to Screen Techniques,Premiere Pro + After Effects Integration', '[\"In the Blink of an Eye - Walter Murch\", \"The Technique of Film Editing - Karel Reisz\", \"Adobe Premiere Pro Classroom in a Book - Maxim Jago\", \"Film Editing: Great Cuts Every Filmmaker Should Know - Gael Chandler\", \"The Visual Story - Bruce Block\"]', '[\"Udemy - Adobe Premiere Pro CC Masterclass\", \"Coursera - Video Production & Editing Specialization\", \"LinkedIn Learning - Premiere Pro 2024 Essential Training\", \"Skillshare - Storytelling Through Editing\", \"Domestika - Video Editing Techniques with Premiere Pro\", \"Adobe Learn - Free Premiere Pro Tutorials\"]', '[\"Justin Odisho - https://www.youtube.com/c/JustinOdisho\", \"Premiere Gal - https://www.youtube.com/c/PremiereGal\", \"Peter McKinnon - https://www.youtube.com/c/PeterMcKinnon\", \"Cinecom.net - https://www.youtube.com/c/Cinecom\", \"Film Riot - https://www.youtube.com/c/filmriot\", \"Think Media - https://www.youtube.com/c/ThinkMediaTV\"]', '[\"https://helpx.adobe.com/premiere-pro/tutorials.html\", \"https://nofilmschool.com/\", \"https://motionarray.com/\", \"https://videocopilot.net/\", \"https://www.premiumbeat.com/blog\"]', 'FTII, Whistling Woods, Seamedu, and AAFT offer strong placement pipelines with production houses, OTT networks, ad agencies, and editing studios. Portfolios and projects are key.', 'Video Editor,Assistant Editor,Motion Graphics Designer,Post-Production Supervisor,Content Creator,Film Trailer Editor,Freelance Video Editor', 'High and growing demand in OTT platforms, YouTube channels, advertising, and digital media content. Freelance work is highly lucrative with a good portfolio.', 'Entry: ₹2.5–5 LPA, Mid-level: ₹5–10 LPA, Senior: ₹12–25+ LPA, Freelance: ₹3,000–₹50,000+ per project', 'Internships in production houses, YouTube channels, and media agencies. Common roles include assistant editor, sync artist, logger. Apply via Internshala, LinkedIn, or referrals.', 'Student → Assistant Editor → Video Editor → Senior Editor → Post-Production Lead → Creative Director ↘ Freelance Editor → Content Creator → Production Company Owner', 'Adobe Certified Professional – Premiere Pro,LinkedIn Learning Completion Certificate,Coursera Film Production Specialization (University of London),Udemy Premiere Pro Certificate,Domestika Creative Editing Certifications,YouTube Certified Creator'),
('Design', 'Film Making', 'Script Writing Tools', '[\"Film and Television Institute of India (FTII), Pune\", \"Satyajit Ray Film & Television Institute (SRFTI), Kolkata\", \"Whistling Woods International, Mumbai\", \"Asian Academy of Film & Television (AAFT), Noida\", \"Ramesh Sippy Academy of Cinema and Entertainment, Mumbai\", \"L V Prasad Film and TV Academy, Chennai\", \"Annapurna College of Film & Media, Hyderabad\", \"K R Narayanan National Institute of Visual Science and Arts, Kerala\", \"Seamedu School of Pro-Expressionism, Pune\", \"Mumbai University – Film Studies Division\"]', 'Screenwriting Fundamentals,Script Formatting & Editing,Structure & Narrative Arcs,Dialogue Writing,Character Arcs & Conflict,Genre Writing Techniques,Screenplay Software Training,Film Theory & Visual Storytelling,Adaptation Writing', '[\"Save the Cat! - Blake Snyder\", \"Story - Robert McKee\", \"The Anatomy of Story - John Truby\", \"Screenplay - Syd Field\", \"The Writer’s Journey - Christopher Vogler\"]', '[\"Coursera - Scriptwriting for Film and TV (Michigan State University)\", \"Udemy - Screenwriting Masterclass\", \"Skillshare - Screenwriting for Beginners\", \"MasterClass - Aaron Sorkin Teaches Screenwriting\", \"Domestika - Screenwriting Techniques\", \"FutureLearn - Introduction to Screenwriting\"]', '[\"Lessons from the Screenplay - https://www.youtube.com/c/LessonsfromtheScreenplay\", \"The Script Lab - https://www.youtube.com/c/TheScriptLab\", \"Film Courage - https://www.youtube.com/c/filmcourage\", \"Behind the Curtain - https://www.youtube.com/@BehindtheCurtainYT\", \"Just Write - https://www.youtube.com/c/JustWrite\", \"Now You See It - https://www.youtube.com/c/nowyouseeit\"]', '[\"https://www.finaldraft.com/\", \"https://www.celtx.com/\", \"https://www.studiobinder.com/\", \"https://www.scriptreaderpro.com/\", \"https://www.writersstore.com/\", \"https://nofilmschool.com/\"]', 'FTII, SRFTI, and Whistling Woods support student script pitches to studios. However, personal networking, writing samples, and screenplay competitions are more impactful than traditional placements.', 'Screenwriter,Script Supervisor,Dialogue Writer,Content Developer (Film/Web/TV),Script Analyst,Ghostwriter,Storyboard Writer', 'Moderate to High Demand. Especially strong in OTT platforms, web series, indie films, and advertising scripts. Freelance and ghostwriting opportunities growing rapidly.', 'Entry: ₹2 – ₹4.5 LPA, Mid-level: ₹5 – ₹10 LPA, Senior: ₹12 – ₹20+ LPA, Freelance Projects: ₹10K – ₹2L+ per script', 'Internships available with production houses, writers\' rooms, ad agencies, and OTT platforms. Roles include assistant scriptwriter, dialogue researcher, and scene breakdown assistant.', 'Student → Assistant Scriptwriter → Screenwriter → Head Writer → Showrunner → Creative Director ↘ Freelance Script Consultant → Story Editor → OTT Series Writer', 'Final Draft Certified Writer,Scriptwriting Certificate – Michigan State (Coursera),MasterClass – Aaron Sorkin’s Screenwriting Course,Domestika Screenwriting Certificate,ScreenCraft Fellowship Participation'),
('Design', 'Architecture', 'AutoCAD', '[\"School of Planning and Architecture (SPA), Delhi\", \"IIT Kharagpur\", \"IIT Roorkee\", \"CEPT University, Ahmedabad\", \"Sir JJ College of Architecture, Mumbai\", \"Chandigarh College of Architecture\", \"Manipal School of Architecture & Planning\", \"Jamia Millia Islamia, Delhi\", \"BMS College of Architecture, Bangalore\", \"R.V. College of Architecture, Bangalore\"]', 'Architectural Design,Building Materials & Construction,Structural Systems,Environmental Science in Architecture,History of Architecture,Building Services (MEP),Professional Practice,Urban & Rural Planning,AutoCAD, SketchUp, Revit', '[\"Architectural Drawing - David Dernie\", \"Form, Space & Order - Francis D.K. Ching\", \"AutoCAD for Architecture - Elise Moss\", \"Design Drawing - Francis D.K. Ching\", \"Building Construction Illustrated - Ching\"]', '[\"Udemy - AutoCAD 2D & 3D Masterclass for Architecture\", \"LinkedIn Learning - AutoCAD for Architecture Projects\", \"Coursera - Making Architecture (IE School of Architecture)\", \"Skillshare - Intro to AutoCAD for Designers\", \"NPTEL - Basics of Architecture & AutoCAD\", \"Autodesk Learn - Official Free Tutorials\"]', '[\"TheModmin - https://www.youtube.com/c/TheModmin\", \"Mughal Architecture - https://www.youtube.com/c/MughalArchitecture\", \"Design Charette - https://www.youtube.com/c/DesignCharette\", \"Autodesk Building Solutions - https://www.youtube.com/c/AutodeskBuildingSolutions\", \"Show It Better - https://www.youtube.com/c/ShowItBetter\", \"The B1M - https://www.youtube.com/c/TheB1M\"]', '[\"https://www.autodesk.com/education/free-software/autocad\", \"https://www.archdaily.com/\", \"https://www.architecturaldigest.in/\", \"https://www.designboom.com/architecture/\", \"https://nptel.ac.in/\", \"https://visualizingarchitecture.com/\"]', 'SPA, IITs, and CEPT have strong placement networks with architecture firms, real estate developers, and government departments. Portfolios and internships heavily influence job offers.', 'Junior Architect,AutoCAD Draftsman,Urban Planner,Interior Architect,BIM Coordinator,CAD Designer,Landscape Architect', 'Steady demand in urban planning, government projects, real estate, smart cities, and infrastructure. Specialized skills like BIM and sustainability increase job scope.', 'Entry: ₹3–6 LPA, Mid-level: ₹7–12 LPA, Senior: ₹15–25+ LPA, Freelance: ₹20K–₹2L per project', 'Internships typically during 4th/5th year with design studios, construction firms, urban design departments. Common roles: intern architect, site documenter, CAD drafter.', 'B.Arch. Student → Intern Architect → Junior Architect → Project Architect → Senior Architect ↘ Urban Planner / BIM Expert / Consultant → Studio Owner / Govt. Consultant / Faculty', 'Autodesk Certified Professional – AutoCAD,BIM Certification (Revit/Navisworks),LEED / GRIHA Green Building Certificate,Coursera Architectural Design Thinking (NUS),Photoshop & 3DS Max Rendering for Architects'),
