('Agriculture', 'Forestry', 'GIS (Geographic Information System)', 'Forest Research Institute (FRI) Dehradun, Indian Institute of Remote Sensing (IIRS) Dehradun, Indian Institute of Forest Management (IIFM) Bhopal, Tamil Nadu Agricultural University (TNAU) Coimbatore, Dr. Y.S. Parmar University of Horticulture and Forestry Solan, Birsa Agricultural University Ranchi, Kerala Agricultural University (KAU), Assam Agricultural University Jorhat, NERIST Arunachal Pradesh, GB Pant University Pantnagar', 'Principles of GIS, Remote Sensing & Image Interpretation, Forest Resource Mapping, Spatial Data Analysis, Forest Ecology and Inventory, Forest Fire and Biodiversity Mapping', 'Fundamentals of GIS – Michael N. DeMers, Introduction to GIS – Kang-Tsung Chang, Remote Sensing and GIS for Ecological Studies – S.K. Kushwaha, GIS for Environmental Management – Robert Scally, GIS and Science – Longley et al.', 'ISRO IIRS Free GIS & RS Courses, NPTEL Remote Sensing and GIS, Coursera GIS Specialization, edX Fundamentals of GIS, Udemy ArcGIS/QGIS, Skill India GIS Technician Course', 'IIRS Outreach, Geospatial World, GIS Simplified India, NPTEL India, GeoHub India, Forest Survey of India FSI', 'https://iirs.gov.in, https://fsi.nic.in, https://nptel.ac.in, https://bhuvan.nrsc.gov.in, https://geospatialworld.net, https://icfre.gov.in', 'Placement in government departments, FSI, ISRO, GIS companies, research roles in forest data and environmental impact. NGOs and global forestry projects also recruit actively.', 'Forest GIS Analyst, Remote Sensing Technician, Forest Mapping Consultant, Geospatial Data Scientist, Forest Carbon Mapping Expert, Conservation GIS Expert', 'High demand for climate monitoring, biodiversity tracking, carbon offset mapping, and forest GIS digitalization. Growing recruitment in both government and private sectors.', 'Entry: ₹30,000–50,000; Mid-level: ₹60,000–90,000; Senior: ₹1L–2L+; Freelance: ₹10k–₹1L+/project', 'ISRO-IIRS GIS Training, FRI Internships, FSI Forest Survey Projects, ESRI/RMSI/Cyient Internships, WWF Forest GIS Projects, Bhuvan NRSC Internship', 'GIS Intern → Forest GIS Analyst → Senior GIS Officer → RS-GIS Scientist → Project Lead/Consultant → Forest GIS Director', 'ISRO IIRS Certificate, NPTEL GIS Certification, ArcGIS/QGIS Certification, ICAR Forestry Data Mapping Certificate, WWF Forest Mapping Certificate, Skill India GIS Technician'),
('Agriculture', 'Fisheries', 'Aquaculture Tech', 'Central Institute of Fisheries Education (CIFE) Mumbai, Kerala University of Fisheries and Ocean Studies (KUFOS) Kochi, Tamil Nadu Dr. J. Jayalalithaa Fisheries University (TNJFU), College of Fisheries Mangalore, Dr. Balasaheb Sawant Konkan Krishi Vidyapeeth Maharashtra, Orissa University of Agriculture and Technology (OUAT), Assam Agricultural University College of Fisheries Raha, Central Institute of Brackishwater Aquaculture (CIBA) Chennai, ICAR-CMFRI, College of Fisheries Dholi Bihar', 'Aquaculture Systems & Engineering, Fish Nutrition & Feed Technology, Hatchery Techniques & Breeding, Aquatic Animal Health, Water Quality Management, Fisheries Extension & Economics, RAS Technology, Post-Harvest Technology', 'Aquaculture: Farming Aquatic Animals and Plants – John S. Lucas, Fish Nutrition – Ronald W. Hardy, Principles of Aquaculture – Robert R. Stickney, Aquaculture Engineering – Odd-Ivar Lekang, Aquatic Animal Health – G.V. Radhakrishnan', 'NPTEL Aquaculture & Marine Biotechnology, ICAR-CIFE eLearning, edX Aquaculture by Wageningen University, Coursera Sustainable Aquaculture, Skill India Fisheries & Aquaculture Courses, FutureLearn Aquatic Animal Health', 'ICAR CIFE Official, Fisheries India, AgriTech Guruji, Blue Revolution India, KUFOS Kerala Channel, Biofloc Farming - Aqua Diaries', 'https://icar.org.in, https://cife.edu.in, https://kufos.ac.in, https://nfdb.gov.in, https://ciba.res.in, https://skillindia.gov.in', 'Good placement support in institutes like CIFE, TNJFU, and KUFOS. Roles in hatcheries, aquafeed companies, RAS firms, and seafood export agencies.', 'Aquaculture Technician, Fish Farm Manager, Feed & Nutrition Specialist, Hatchery Supervisor, Aquatic Health Expert, RAS Engineer, Marine Biotechnologist, Quality Controller in Seafood Exports', 'High demand in sustainable aquaculture, shrimp farming, ornamental fishery, RAS systems, seafood exports. National and global projects available.', 'Entry: ₹25,000–45,000; Mid: ₹50,000–80,000; Senior: ₹1L–1.8L+; International: ₹2L–5L+', 'CIFE Internships, ICAR-CIBA and CMFRI projects, NFDB training, internships at shrimp hatcheries (Tamil Nadu, Gujarat), RAS-based fish farms, KUFOS summer programs', 'Intern → Assistant Aquaculture Manager → Farm/Feed Plant Manager → Project Consultant → Tech Head or Entrepreneur in Aquaculture', 'ISRO-IIRS Remote Sensing for Aquaculture, NFDB Biofloc & RAS Certification, CIFE Aquatic Animal Health Certificate, Skill India Aquaculture Tech Certificate, FAO eLearning in Biosecurity, HACCP Export Standards Certification');
INSERT INTO `career_recommendation` (`field`, `domain`, `technical_skill`, `best_colleges`, `core_subjects`, `recommended_books`, `online_courses`, `youtube_channels`, `websites`, `placement_info`, `job_roles`, `job_status`, `salary_info`, `training_internship`, `career_path`, `certifications`) VALUES
('Agriculture', 'Fisheries', 'GPS Tracking', '[\"Central Institute of Fisheries Education (CIFE), Mumbai\", \"Tamil Nadu Fisheries University (TNFU), Nagapattinam\", \"College of Fisheries, Mangalore (KVAFSU)\", \"Central Agricultural University (CAU), Imphal\", \"Assam Agricultural University, Jorhat\", \"West Bengal University of Animal & Fishery Sciences, Kolkata\", \"Dr. Balasaheb Sawant Konkan Krishi Vidyapeeth, Dapoli\", \"Orissa University of Agriculture and Technology (OUAT), Bhubaneswar\"]', '[\"Fisheries Biology & Ecology\", \"Aquaculture Systems & Techniques\", \"Fishery Resource Management\", \"Marine & Freshwater Ecosystems\", \"Geographic Information System (GIS) & Remote Sensing\", \"GPS Technology & Applications\", \"Data Analysis & Statistical Methods\", \"Environmental Monitoring\", \"Marine Engineering Basics\"]', '[\"Fisheries Management: A Manual for Managers, Scientists and Engineers by Carl J. Walters\", \"Principles of Aquaculture by Robert R. Stickney\", \"Geographic Information Systems and Science by Paul A. Longley\", \"Remote Sensing and GIS for Fisheries and Aquaculture by Subhajyoti Ray\", \"GPS Satellite Surveying by Alfred Leick\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\", \"course\":\"GIS and Remote Sensing Specialization\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\", \"course\":\"Introduction to GPS: Global Positioning System\"}, {\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\", \"course\":\"Aquaculture & Fisheries Science\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\", \"course\":\"Fisheries Science and Management\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Fisheries and Aquaculture Research & Education\"}, {\"name\":\"GIS & Remote Sensing Tutorials by Esri India\"}, {\"name\":\"Aquaculture Hub\"}, {\"name\":\"Fishery Survey of India\"}, {\"name\":\"National Institute of Ocean Technology (NIOT)\"}]', '[\"http://cife.edu.in/\", \"https://nfdb.gov.in/\", \"http://www.fao.org/fisheries/en/\", \"https://icar.org.in/\", \"https://www.gisdevelopment.net/\"]', 'Good placement opportunities from fisheries universities, especially in government departments, research institutes, and private aquaculture companies.', '[\"Fisheries Research Scientist\", \"GPS Data Analyst\", \"Aquaculture Farm Manager\", \"GIS Specialist\", \"Marine Environmental Consultant\", \"Fleet Operation Manager\", \"Policy Analyst in Fisheries Management\"]', 'Growing demand in government, private aquaculture, environmental organizations, and marine tech sectors.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2,50,000 - ₹4,00,000\", \"mid_level\":\"₹4,50,000 - ₹7,00,000\", \"experienced\":\"₹7,00,000 - ₹12,00,000+\"}', 'Internships available at ICAR Institutes, NFDB, and local fisheries departments with hands-on training in GPS monitoring and aquaculture management.', 'Entry-Level: Fisheries Technician / GPS Data Analyst → Mid-Level: Aquaculture Manager / GIS Specialist / Fisheries Scientist → Senior-Level: Project Manager / Research Lead / Policy Advisor', 'Certified GIS Professional (GISP), GPS and Remote Sensing Certification, Aquaculture Management Certification, Data Analysis & Visualization Certification'),
('Agriculture', 'Agribusiness', 'Farm ERP', '[\"National Institute of Agricultural Extension Management (MANAGE), Hyderabad\", \"Institute of Agribusiness Management, Bikaner\", \"Indian Agricultural Research Institute (IARI), New Delhi\", \"Punjab Agricultural University (PAU), Ludhiana\", \"Tamil Nadu Agricultural University (TNAU), Coimbatore\", \"University of Agricultural Sciences (UAS), Bangalore\", \"Indian Institute of Plantation Management (IIPM), Bangalore\", \"Narendra Deva University of Agriculture and Technology, Faizabad\"]', '[\"Principles of Agribusiness Management\", \"Agricultural Economics\", \"Farm Management & Production Economics\", \"Supply Chain and Logistics Management\", \"Information Technology in Agriculture\", \"ERP Systems and Software Tools\", \"Data Analytics & Business Intelligence\", \"Agricultural Marketing and Finance\", \"Precision Agriculture Technology\"]', '[\"Agribusiness Management by N. Lalitha\", \"Introduction to Agricultural Economics by P.A. Ray\", \"Farm Management by George W. Norton\", \"Enterprise Resource Planning by Alexis Leon\", \"Precision Agriculture Technology for Crop Farming by Qin Zhang\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\", \"course\":\"Agribusiness Management\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\", \"course\":\"Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) Fundamentals\"}, {\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\", \"course\":\"Data Analytics for Agriculture\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\", \"course\":\"Digital Agriculture\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Agribusiness Management Tutorials\"}, {\"name\":\"ERP Software Training India\"}, {\"name\":\"Precision Agriculture Channel\"}, {\"name\":\"Agricultural Economics by Giri Institute\"}, {\"name\":\"Krishi Jagran\"}]', '[\"https://www.manage.gov.in/\", \"https://apeda.gov.in/\", \"https://icar.org.in/\", \"https://agricoop.nic.in/\", \"https://www.agrostar.in/\"]', 'Good campus recruitment from agribusiness firms, agri-tech startups, and ERP solution providers.', '[\"Farm ERP Consultant\", \"Agribusiness Analyst\", \"Supply Chain Manager\", \"Agriculture Data Analyst\", \"Farm Operations Manager\", \"IT Specialist in Agriculture Sector\"]', 'Growing demand in agri-tech companies, ERP solution providers, agricultural cooperatives, and government agriculture departments.', '{\"starting\":\"₹3,00,000 - ₹5,00,000\", \"mid_level\":\"₹5,00,000 - ₹9,00,000\", \"experienced\":\"₹9,00,000 - ₹15,00,000+\"}', 'Internships available at MANAGE, agri-tech startups, and ERP firms like AgroStar, Tally for Agriculture with hands-on experience.', 'Entry-Level: Farm ERP Trainee / Agribusiness Analyst → Mid-Level: ERP Consultant / Supply Chain Manager / Data Analyst → Senior-Level: ERP Project Manager / Agribusiness Consultant / Strategic Planner', 'Certified ERP Consultant (SAP, Oracle, or others), Agribusiness Management Certification, Data Analytics & Business Intelligence certifications, Digital Agriculture & IoT Certifications'),
('Agriculture', 'Agribusiness', 'Inventory Tools', '[\"National Institute of Agricultural Extension Management (MANAGE), Hyderabad\", \"Institute of Agribusiness Management, Bikaner\", \"Indian Agricultural Research Institute (IARI), New Delhi\", \"Punjab Agricultural University (PAU), Ludhiana\", \"Tamil Nadu Agricultural University (TNAU), Coimbatore\", \"University of Agricultural Sciences (UAS), Bangalore\", \"Institute of Rural Management Anand (IRMA), Gujarat\", \"Xavier Institute of Management, Bhubaneswar (XIMB)\"]', '[\"Principles of Agribusiness Management\", \"Agricultural Supply Chain Management\", \"Inventory and Warehouse Management\", \"ERP Systems in Agriculture\", \"Data Analytics and Forecasting\", \"Logistics and Distribution Management\", \"Information Technology in Agriculture\", \"Financial Accounting and Control\"]', '[\"Inventory Management and Production Planning and Scheduling by Edward A. Silver\", \"Supply Chain Management: Strategy, Planning, and Operation by Sunil Chopra\", \"Agribusiness Management by N. Lalitha\", \"Enterprise Resource Planning by Alexis Leon\", \"Data Analytics for Supply Chain Management by Nada R. Sanders\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\", \"course\":\"Supply Chain Management\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\", \"course\":\"Inventory Management Fundamentals\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\", \"course\":\"ERP Fundamentals\"}, {\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\", \"course\":\"Agribusiness Management\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Supply Chain & Inventory Management Tutorials\"}, {\"name\":\"Agribusiness Management India\"}, {\"name\":\"ERP Software Training\"}, {\"name\":\"Logistics Management Channel\"}, {\"name\":\"Krishi Jagran\"}]', '[\"https://www.manage.gov.in/\", \"https://icar.org.in/\", \"https://apeda.gov.in/\", \"https://agricoop.nic.in/\", \"https://www.supplychaindigital.com/\"]', 'Good campus placement opportunities in agribusiness firms, FMCG, agri-tech startups, and logistics companies.', '[\"Inventory Manager\", \"Supply Chain Analyst\", \"ERP Consultant\", \"Warehouse Manager\", \"Logistics Coordinator\", \"Data Analyst in Agribusiness\"]', 'Growing demand in agribusiness companies, food processing firms, supply chain firms, retail chains, and e-commerce companies with agriculture focus.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2,50,000 - ₹4,50,000\", \"mid_level\":\"₹4,50,000 - ₹7,50,000\", \"experienced\":\"₹7,50,000 - ₹12,00,000+\"}', 'Internships at MANAGE, agribusiness firms, FMCG companies, logistics firms, and ERP vendors with practical training in inventory software and supply chain analytics.', 'Entry-Level: Inventory Executive / Supply Chain Assistant → Mid-Level: Inventory Manager / ERP Consultant / Supply Chain Analyst → Senior-Level: Supply Chain Director / Operations Head / Agribusiness Consultant', 'Certified Supply Chain Professional (CSCP), ERP Certification (SAP, Oracle, Tally), Data Analytics Certifications (Power BI, Tableau), Logistics & Warehouse Management Certifications'),
('Agriculture', 'Environmental Studies', 'EIA Tools', '[\"Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Bombay\", \"Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Kharagpur\", \"National Institute of Technology (NIT) Rourkela\", \"TERI School of Advanced Studies, New Delhi\", \"Jawaharlal Nehru University (JNU), New Delhi\", \"University of Delhi (DU)\", \"Indian Institute of Science (IISc), Bangalore\", \"Symbiosis Institute of Geoinformatics\"]', '[\"Environmental Impact Assessment\", \"Environmental Science & Ecology\", \"Environmental Laws and Regulations\", \"Geographic Information Systems (GIS) & Remote Sensing\", \"Pollution Control Technologies\", \"Environmental Monitoring & Modeling\", \"Risk Assessment and Management\", \"Sustainable Development\", \"Environmental Data Analysis\"]', '[\"Environmental Impact Assessment: A Practical Guide by Lawrence D. Canter\", \"Methods of Environmental Impact Assessment by Peter Morris and Riki Therivel\", \"Environmental Science: Principles and Practices by G. Tyler Miller\", \"GIS and Environmental Modeling by Michael F. Goodchild\", \"Environmental Pollution and Control by P. Aarne Vesilind\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\", \"course\":\"Environmental Impact Assessment\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\", \"course\":\"GIS and Remote Sensing for Environmental Applications\"}, {\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\", \"course\":\"Environmental Management & Sustainability\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\", \"course\":\"Environmental Law and Policy\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Environmental Science and Engineering Lectures (IIT Bombay)\"}, {\"name\":\"GIS and Remote Sensing Tutorials by Esri India\"}, {\"name\":\"Sustainability and Environmental Education\"}, {\"name\":\"Indian Institute of Remote Sensing (IIRS)\"}, {\"name\":\"Ministry of Environment, Forest and Climate Change (MoEFCC) India\"}]', '[\"https://moef.gov.in/\", \"https://cpcb.nic.in/\", \"https://www.neeri.res.in/\", \"https://iirs.gov.in/\", \"http://envfor.nic.in/envis\"]', 'Good opportunities in environmental consultancy firms, government agencies, research organizations, and NGOs.', '[\"EIA Consultant\", \"Environmental Analyst\", \"GIS Specialist\", \"Pollution Control Officer\", \"Environmental Compliance Manager\", \"Sustainability Analyst\"]', 'Steady and growing demand in government regulatory bodies, environmental consultancies, research & academia, NGOs, and corporate sustainability departments.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2,50,000 - ₹4,50,000\", \"mid_level\":\"₹4,50,000 - ₹8,00,000\", \"experienced\":\"₹8,00,000 - ₹15,00,000+\"}', 'Internships at MoEFCC, CPCB, NEERI, environmental NGOs, and private EIA consulting firms with hands-on experience in EIA project prep and GIS data analysis.', 'Entry-Level: Junior EIA Consultant / Environmental Technician → Mid-Level: Senior EIA Consultant / Environmental Analyst / GIS Specialist → Senior-Level: Project Manager / Environmental Compliance Manager / Sustainability Lead', 'Certified Environmental Impact Assessment Practitioner (CEIAP), GIS Professional Certification (GISP), Environmental Management System Auditor, Certified Sustainability Professional (CSP)'),
('Agriculture', 'Environmental Studies', 'Pollution Monitoring Devices', '[\"Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Bombay\", \"Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Delhi\", \"Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Kharagpur\", \"National Institute of Technology (NIT) Rourkela\", \"Indian Institute of Science (IISc), Bangalore\", \"TERI School of Advanced Studies, New Delhi\", \"Jawaharlal Nehru University (JNU), New Delhi\", \"Anna University, Chennai\"]', '[\"Environmental Chemistry & Toxicology\", \"Instrumentation & Analytical Techniques\", \"Air, Water & Soil Pollution Monitoring\", \"Environmental Microbiology\", \"Data Acquisition & Signal Processing\", \"Remote Sensing & GIS Applications\", \"Environmental Laws & Regulations\", \"Environmental Data Analysis & Modelling\"]', '[\"Environmental Instrumentation and Analysis by Roman Kline\", \"Air Quality Monitoring by Jayant Kumar Bhuyan\", \"Environmental Pollution and Control by P. Aarne Vesilind\", \"Instrumentation for Environmental Monitoring by S. M. Khopkar\", \"Handbook of Air Pollution Analysis by S. E. Bunch\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"NPTEL\", \"course\":\"Environmental Monitoring and Instrumentation\"}, {\"platform\":\"Coursera\", \"course\":\"Air Pollution – Monitoring, Modelling and Management\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\", \"course\":\"Environmental Instrumentation\"}, {\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\", \"course\":\"Remote Sensing and GIS\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Environmental Monitoring & Instrumentation Tutorials\"}, {\"name\":\"IIT Bombay Environmental Science Lectures\"}, {\"name\":\"Air Quality & Pollution Control\"}, {\"name\":\"Indian Institute of Remote Sensing (IIRS)\"}, {\"name\":\"Ministry of Environment, Forest and Climate Change (MoEFCC) India\"}]', '[\"https://cpcb.nic.in/\", \"https://moef.gov.in/\", \"https://www.neeri.res.in/\", \"https://iirs.gov.in/\", \"https://www.springer.com/journal/10661\"]', 'Good opportunities in environmental consultancy firms, government pollution control boards, research organizations, and environmental tech companies.', '[\"Pollution Monitoring Technician\", \"Environmental Instrumentation Specialist\", \"Data Analyst\", \"Environmental Consultant\", \"Regulatory Compliance Officer\", \"Field Engineer\"]', 'Steady demand in government agencies (CPCB, SPCBs), environmental monitoring firms, research labs, and industries with environmental compliance units.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2,50,000 - ₹4,00,000\", \"mid_level\":\"₹4,00,000 - ₹7,00,000\", \"experienced\":\"₹7,00,000 - ₹12,00,000+\"}', 'Internships at CPCB, NEERI, environmental labs, and private environmental tech firms with training on pollution monitoring instruments, data collection, and analysis.', 'Entry-Level: Pollution Monitoring Technician / Environmental Assistant → Mid-Level: Instrumentation Specialist / Environmental Consultant / Data Analyst → Senior-Level: Project Manager / Regulatory Compliance Manager / Environmental Technology Lead', 'Certified Environmental Instrumentation Specialist, Data Analysis & Visualization Certifications (Tableau, Power BI), Environmental Management System Auditor, Certification in Remote Sensing & GIS'),
('Hospitality', 'Hotel Management', 'PMS Software', '[\"Institute of Hotel Management (IHM), Mumbai\", \"Institute of Hotel Management (IHM), Delhi\", \"Welcomgroup Graduate School of Hotel Administration (WGSHA), Manipal\", \"IHM Bangalore\", \"IHM Hyderabad\", \"IHM Kolkata\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Dr. Ambedkar Institute of Hotel Management, Chennai\"]', '[\"Hospitality Management Fundamentals\", \"Hotel Operations Management\", \"Front Office and Reception Management\", \"Property Management Systems (PMS)\", \"Food and Beverage Management\", \"Hospitality Accounting and Billing\", \"Customer Service & CRM\", \"Hospitality IT Systems & Software\", \"Data Analytics in Hospitality\"]', '[\"Hotel Front Office Management by James A. Bardi\", \"Hospitality Information Technology by Peter O’Connor\", \"Hotel Management and Operations by Michael J. Boella and Alan Cook\", \"The Cornell School of Hotel Administration on Hospitality by Michael C. Sturman\", \"Property Management System: PMS Manuals and Guides\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\", \"course\":\"Hotel Management Fundamentals\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\", \"course\":\"Introduction to Hospitality and Tourism Management\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\", \"course\":\"PMS Software Training (Opera PMS, eZee FrontDesk)\"}, {\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\", \"course\":\"Hospitality Management\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Hotel Management Tutorials\"}, {\"name\":\"PMS Software Training Videos (Opera, eZee FrontDesk)\"}, {\"name\":\"Hospitality Insights\"}, {\"name\":\"Hotelier India\"}, {\"name\":\"IHCL Official Channel\"}]', '[\"https://www.ihmchennai.edu.in/\", \"https://nchm.nic.in/\", \"https://www.hotelmanagement.net/\", \"https://www.hospitalitynet.org/\", \"https://www.ezeeabsolute.com/\"]', 'Strong placement record with hotels, resorts, and hospitality chains.', '[\"Front Office Manager\", \"PMS Administrator\", \"Reservation Executive\", \"Revenue Manager\", \"Hospitality IT Support\", \"Hotel Operations Coordinator\"]', 'Growing demand in hotels, resorts, cruise lines, event management, corporate hospitality, and hospitality software providers.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2,00,000 - ₹4,00,000\", \"mid_level\":\"₹4,00,000 - ₹8,00,000\", \"experienced\":\"₹8,00,000 - ₹15,00,000+\"}', 'Internships at reputed hotels, hospitality chains, and PMS software firms like eZee, Oracle Hospitality with hands-on PMS experience.', 'Entry-Level: Front Desk Executive / PMS Operator → Mid-Level: Front Office Manager / PMS Administrator / Revenue Manager → Senior-Level: Hotel Operations Manager / Hospitality IT Manager / Regional Manager', 'Certified Hotel Administrator (CHA), PMS Software Certifications (Oracle Opera, eZee, MSI), CRM Certification, Hospitality Management Certification by NCHMCT'),
('Hospitality', 'Hotel Management', 'POS Systems (Point of Sale)', '[\"Institute of Hotel Management (IHM), Mumbai\", \"Institute of Hotel Management (IHM), Delhi\", \"Welcomgroup Graduate School of Hotel Administration (WGSHA), Manipal\", \"IHM Bangalore\", \"IHM Hyderabad\", \"IHM Kolkata\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Dr. Ambedkar Institute of Hotel Management, Chennai\"]', '[\"Hospitality Operations Management\", \"Front Office and Reception Management\", \"Food & Beverage Service Management\", \"Point of Sale (POS) System Operations\", \"Billing and Accounting\", \"Customer Relationship Management (CRM)\", \"Hospitality IT & Software Systems\", \"Data Analytics & Reporting\"]', '[\"Hospitality Management Accounting by Martin G. Jagels\", \"Point of Sale Systems and Operations (industry manuals)\", \"Hospitality Information Technology by Peter O’Connor\", \"Hotel Front Office Management by James A. Bardi\", \"The Cornell School of Hotel Administration on Hospitality by Michael C. Sturman\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\", \"course\":\"Hospitality Management Fundamentals\"}, {\"platform\":\"Udemy\", \"course\":\"POS Systems Training\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\", \"course\":\"Introduction to Hospitality and Tourism Management\"}, {\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\", \"course\":\"Hospitality Technology Management\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"POS System Tutorials\"}, {\"name\":\"Hotel Management Training\"}, {\"name\":\"Hospitality Insights\"}, {\"name\":\"IHM Mumbai Official Channel\"}, {\"name\":\"Hotelier India\"}]', '[\"https://nchm.nic.in/\", \"https://www.ihmchennai.edu.in/\", \"https://www.hospitalitynet.org/\", \"https://www.hotelmanagement.net/\", \"https://pos.toasttab.com/\"]', 'Good placement support through IHMs and hospitality institutes with top hotels, resorts, and restaurant chains.', '[\"POS Operator\", \"Billing Executive\", \"Front Office Associate\", \"Sales Coordinator\", \"Hospitality IT Support\"]', 'Steady demand in hotels, restaurants, cafes, event management, retail outlets, and hospitality software companies.', '{\"starting\":\"₹1,80,000 - ₹3,50,000\", \"mid_level\":\"₹3,50,000 - ₹6,00,000\", \"experienced\":\"₹6,00,000 - ₹10,00,000+\"}', 'Internships at hotels, restaurants, hospitality chains, and POS software providers with hands-on training in POS terminals and billing.', 'Entry-Level: POS Operator / Billing Executive → Mid-Level: Front Office Supervisor / Sales Coordinator / POS Manager → Senior-Level: Hospitality IT Manager / Operations Manager / Regional Manager', 'Certified POS Professional, Hospitality Management Certification by NCHMCT, CRM Certification, Customer Service and Sales Certifications'),
('Hospitality', 'Tourism Management', 'Tour Planning Tools', '[\"Indian Institute of Tourism and Travel Management (IITTM), Gwalior\", \"Institute of Hotel Management (IHM), Delhi\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Banaras Hindu University (BHU), Varanasi\", \"Tata Institute of Social Sciences (TISS), Mumbai\", \"Jawaharlal Nehru University (JNU), New Delhi\", \"Lovely Professional University (LPU), Punjab\", \"Kerala Institute of Tourism and Travel Studies (KITTS), Thiruvananthapuram\"]', '[\"Tourism Principles and Practices\", \"Tour Operations Management\", \"Travel Agency and Tour Guiding\", \"Destination Management\", \"Travel Technology and Planning Tools\", \"Tourism Marketing and Promotion\", \"Customer Relationship Management (CRM)\", \"Sustainable and Eco-tourism\", \"Geography and Cultural Studies\"]', '[\"Tourism Management by Stephen J. Page\", \"Introduction to Tourism and Hospitality in BC by Roy A. Cook\", \"Tour Operations Management by William F. Theobald\", \"Travel Agency and Tour Operations by Raghubalan and Smritee Raghubalan\", \"Sustainable Tourism: Business Development, Operations and Management by Carol Patterson\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\", \"course\":\"Tourism and Travel Management\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\", \"course\":\"Introduction to Sustainable Tourism\"}, {\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\", \"course\":\"Tour Planning and Management\"}, {\"platform\":\"NPTEL\", \"course\":\"Tourism and Hospitality Management\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Tourism Management Lectures\"}, {\"name\":\"Travel Tech & Tools Tutorials\"}, {\"name\":\"Indian Tourism Official Channel\"}, {\"name\":\"Sustainable Tourism Channel\"}, {\"name\":\"Travel & Hospitality Industry Insights\"}]', '[\"https://tourism.gov.in/\", \"https://www.iittm.ac.in/\", \"https://www.unwto.org/\", \"https://www.travefy.com/\", \"https://sustainabletourism.net/\"]', 'Good placement opportunities in travel agencies, tour operators, government tourism departments, and hospitality chains.', '[\"Tour Planner\", \"Travel Consultant\", \"Tour Coordinator\", \"Travel Operations Manager\", \"Itinerary Designer\", \"Tourism Marketing Executive\"]', 'Growing demand in travel agencies, airlines, hotels, resorts, government tourism boards, and online travel platforms.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2,00,000 - ₹4,50,000\", \"mid_level\":\"₹4,50,000 - ₹8,00,000\", \"experienced\":\"₹8,00,000 - ₹14,00,000+\"}', 'Internships with travel agencies, tourism departments, tour operators, and online travel portals with practical exposure to itinerary planning and tour management software.', 'Entry-Level: Travel Consultant / Tour Coordinator → Mid-Level: Tour Planner / Operations Manager / CRM Manager → Senior-Level: Tourism Manager / Business Development Manager / Regional Director', 'Certified Travel Associate (CTA), Certified Tour Professional (CTP), Certificate in Sustainable Tourism, CRM & Travel Technology Certifications'),
('Hospitality', 'Tourism Management', 'CRM (Customer Relationship Management)', '[\"Indian Institute of Tourism and Travel Management (IITTM), Gwalior\", \"Institute of Hotel Management (IHM), Delhi\", \"Christ University, Bangalore\", \"Tata Institute of Social Sciences (TISS), Mumbai\", \"Jawaharlal Nehru University (JNU), New Delhi\", \"Symbiosis Centre for Management Studies, Pune\", \"Amity University, Noida\", \"Lovely Professional University (LPU), Punjab\"]', '[\"Principles of Tourism Management\", \"Customer Relationship Management\", \"Marketing Management\", \"Sales and Distribution Management\", \"Tourism Information Systems\", \"Data Analytics for Tourism\", \"Digital Marketing & CRM Tools\", \"Hospitality & Tourism Operations\", \"Communication Skills\"]', '[\"Customer Relationship Management: Concepts and Technologies by Francis Buttle\", \"CRM at the Speed of Light by Paul Greenberg\", \"Tourism Marketing by Alastair M. Morrison\", \"Digital Marketing for Tourism and Hospitality by Roberta Minazzi\", \"Hospitality Marketing Management by Robert D. Reid & David C. Bojanic\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Coursera\", \"course\":\"Customer Relationship Management\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\", \"course\":\"Digital Marketing & CRM Tools\"}, {\"platform\":\"Salesforce Trailhead\", \"course\":\"Salesforce CRM Basics\"}, {\"platform\":\"FutureLearn\", \"course\":\"CRM for Hospitality & Tourism\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Salesforce CRM Tutorials\"}, {\"name\":\"Zoho CRM Training\"}, {\"name\":\"Digital Marketing & CRM Insights\"}, {\"name\":\"Tourism Management Lectures\"}, {\"name\":\"Hospitality CRM Best Practices\"}]', '[\"https://www.iittm.ac.in/\", \"https://nchm.nic.in/\", \"https://trailhead.salesforce.com/\", \"https://www.zoho.com/crm/\", \"https://www.hubspot.com/products/crm\"]', 'Good placement opportunities in travel agencies, tourism boards, hospitality firms, and CRM software providers.', '[\"CRM Analyst\", \"Customer Service Manager\", \"Digital Marketing Executive\", \"Sales Coordinator\", \"Tourism Marketing Specialist\"]', 'Growing demand in tourism & hospitality companies, travel agencies, CRM software firms, marketing agencies, and airlines.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2,00,000 - ₹4,50,000\", \"mid_level\":\"₹4,50,000 - ₹8,50,000\", \"experienced\":\"₹8,50,000 - ₹15,00,000+\"}', 'Internships with CRM firms, travel agencies, hospitality companies, and digital marketing agencies with practical CRM software experience.', 'Entry-Level: CRM Assistant / Marketing Coordinator → Mid-Level: CRM Analyst / Customer Service Manager / Digital Marketing Specialist → Senior-Level: CRM Manager / Sales Manager / Business Development Manager', 'Salesforce Certified Administrator, HubSpot CRM Certification, Digital Marketing Certification, Customer Experience Management Certification'),
('Hospitality', 'Travel & Airline Services', 'GDS (Amadeus, Galileo)', '[\"Institute of Hotel Management (IHM), Mumbai\", \"Indian Institute of Tourism and Travel Management (IITTM), Gwalior\", \"International Air Transport Association (IATA) Authorized Training Centers\", \"American Institute of Travel & Tourism (AITT), New Delhi\", \"Indira Gandhi Institute of Aeronautics (IGIA), Pune\", \"Frankfinn Institute of Air Hostess Training, Mumbai\", \"National Institute of Travel & Tourism Management (NITTM), Hyderabad\", \"Aptech Aviation Academy\"]', '[\"Fundamentals of Travel & Tourism\", \"Airline Ticketing & Reservation Systems\", \"Global Distribution Systems (GDS) – Amadeus, Galileo\", \"Airfare Construction & Pricing\", \"Passenger Handling & Customer Service\", \"Travel Documentation & Visa Procedures\", \"Travel Agency Operations\", \"Travel Technology & Software\", \"Aviation Law & Regulations\"]', '[\"Airline Reservation and Ticketing Systems by K. S. Gill\", \"Global Distribution Systems and Travel Agency Management by R. S. Malhotra\", \"Introduction to Air Transport Management by Lucy Budd & Stephen Ison\", \"Travel Agency Management by R. V. Deshpande\", \"International Air Transport by Peter Belobaba, Amedeo Odoni, & Cynthia Barnhart\"]', '[{\"platform\":\"Udemy\", \"course\":\"Amadeus GDS Training\"}, {\"platform\":\"Coursera\", \"course\":\"Global Distribution Systems\"}, {\"platform\":\"IATA\", \"course\":\"Travel and Tourism Courses\"}, {\"platform\":\"edX\", \"course\":\"Travel Technology\"}]', '[{\"name\":\"Amadeus GDS Training Tutorials\"}, {\"name\":\"Travel and Tourism Channel India\"}, {\"name\":\"IATA Training Videos\"}, {\"name\":\"Galileo GDS Tutorials\"}, {\"name\":\"Airline and Travel Booking Insights\"}]', '[\"https://amadeus.com/en/learning\", \"https://www.travelport.com/solutions/galileo\", \"https://www.iata.org/en/training/\", \"https://www.iittm.ac.in/\", \"https://www.travelport.com/\"]', 'Good placement in travel agencies, airlines, and GDS providers via institutes and aviation academies.', '[\"GDS Ticketing Agent\", \"Travel Consultant\", \"Airline Reservations Specialist\", \"Customer Service Executive\", \"Travel Operations Coordinator\"]', 'Steady demand in airlines, travel agencies, corporate travel, and airport services.', '{\"starting\":\"₹2,00,000 - ₹3,50,000\", \"mid_level\":\"₹3,50,000 - ₹6,50,000\", \"experienced\":\"₹6,50,000 - ₹12,00,000+\"}', 'Training with airlines, travel agencies, GDS providers, and airport customer service teams with hands-on Amadeus and Galileo software experience.', 'Entry-Level: GDS Ticketing Agent / Travel Consultant → Mid-Level: Airline Reservations Specialist / Customer Service Supervisor → Senior-Level: Travel Operations Manager / Corporate Travel Manager / GDS Trainer', 'IATA Foundation & Professional Certificates, Certified Amadeus Consultant, Galileo GDS Certification, Customer Service Excellence in Aviation');
